\h Jeremaia 
\toc3 JER 
\toc2 Jeremaia 
\toc1 God…®n Akam Inigha Izir Gumazim Jeremaian Ak…®nafarim 
\mt1 God…®n Akam Inigha Izir Gumazim // Jeremaian Ak…®nafarim 
\mt2 O 
\mt1 Jeremaia 
\imt1 Akar faragha zuim 
\ip Akam inigha izir gumazim Jeremaia Jerusalem…®n itima Babilonian Atrivim Nebukatnesar iza Judabagh as…®ghas…®ki. Jeremaian akar av…®riba a Judaba ko Israelia dughiar kam bagha ikiangs…®zir akaba me gan…®ngi. Eght…® gumazamiziba aseba ategh navibagh iraghan koght…®, God me gas…®ghasigham. Ez…® me Jeremaia m…®geir akaba baraghan aghua. Ez…® Jeremaian akar maba, God…®n akar d…®k…®r…®zim…®n gun me m…®gei, God g…®n Judabar apangkufigh men akuraght…®, me uamategh uan nguazim…®n izam. 
\ip Jeremaian ak…®nafarim akam inigha izir gumazir igharazibar ak…®nafariba mong men ighara. A kamak…®n, Jeremaia uab…® an eghaghanir av…®riba an aven iti. Jeremaia uab…® God…®n akam akunasa ifongezir puvat…®, a pura uan ifongiam ab…®ragha God…®n ifongiam…®n g…®n ghu. A dughiar av…®ribar navim osemegha uab…®ra uab…®n apangkufi. Egha a uan navir os…®mt…®zim modozir puvat…®. A guizbang…®ra an gun m…®kemez…®, an m…®g…®r…®g…®aba ak…®nafarir kam…®n iti. Jeremaia Judaba bar me gifonge, ez…® God Akar Gavgaviba a gan…®dima, an adar gun m…®k…®masa ifongezir puvat…®. Ez…® gumazamiziba an akam baraghan aghuagha a gas…®ghas…®ghasava amima, a me bagha pamten God m…®gei. 
\ip Jeremaian akar bar aghuir mam sapta 31:31-34…®n iti. Jeremaian akam kagh God uan gumazamiziba ko Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir Igiam damuamin akabar gun m…®gei. Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir Igiar kam, me dag…®am ko ak…®nafarimra an osirighan kogham. A gumazamizibar navir averiabar ik…®t…®, me uari an g…®n mang…®s…® bar ifuegham. E Iesus…®n g…®n zuir gumazamiziba, God…®n Duam…®n ingangarim…®n gara Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir Igiar kam g…®n…®ghn…®si. 
\c 1  
\ms1 God uan akam akunasa  // Jeremaian dia 
\mr (Sapta 1) 
\s1 Azenir God uan akam isa Jeremaia gan…®diba 
\p  
\v 1 Ak…®nafarir kam, Jeremaia m…®kemezir m…®g…®r…®g…®aba an iti. Jeremaia, a Hilkian otarim, a ofa gamir gumazir mam, a Benjamin…®n anabam…®n gumazim, egha Anatot…®n nguibam…®n iti.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 1:2 \xt 2 Atriviba 22:3--23:27; 2 Eghaghaniba 34:8--35:19\x*Ez…® Emon…®n otarim Josaia, a Judan kantrin atrivim…®n itima, an 13plan azenibar dughiam…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God, akar kaba isa Jeremaia gan…®ngi.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 1:3 \xt 2 Atriviba 23:36--24:7; 2 Atriviba 24:18--25:21; 2 Eghaghaniba 36:5-8; 36:11-21\x*Ez…® g…®n Josaian otarim Jehoiakim atrivim…®n itima, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ua akar av…®riba isa Jeremaia gan…®gav…®ra ikia ghua Josaian otarim Sedekaia atrivim…®n itir dughiam…®n, an namba 11plan azenim…®n tu. Ez…® azenir kam…®n namba 5 iak…®nim…®n, apaniba Jerusalem…®n gumazamiziba inigha ghua kantrin igharazim…®n kalabus…®n me ar…®ki. 
\s1 God, uan akam inigha izir ingangarim damuasa Jeremaian dia 
\p  
\v 4 K…® Jeremaia, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, kamagh…®n na m…®g…®a ghaze: 
\b  
\q1  
\v 5 \x - \xo 1:5 \xt Onger Akaba 139:15-16; Aisaia 49:1; 49:5\x*‚ÄúK…® t…®ghar n…®n amebam…®n navir averiam…®n aven n…®n ingaramin dughiam, 
\q2 k…® n…® g…®fogha, n…® ginabagha g…®fa. 
\q1 N…®n amebam t…®ghar n…® batamin dughiam…®n, 
\q2 k…® kantribar tong…®n akam inigha izir gumazim…®n ingangarim damuasa n…® am…®sefe, 
\q3 n…® na baghav…®ra ikiamin gumazim…®n ikiasa, k…® n…® am…®sevegha g…®fa.‚Äù 
