\p  
\v 6 \x - \xo 1:6 \xt 1 Atriviba 3:7\x*Ez…® k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akar kam baregha, kamagh…®n an akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúTi puvat…®gham. Ikiav…®ra Itir God, nan Ekiam, k…® gumazir bar igiam, egha k…® akam akunamin arazibagh fozir puvat…®.‚Äù  
\v 7 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, kamagh…®n na m…®gei: 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄúN…® kamagh…®n m…®k…®man mark…® suam, 
\q2 k…® gumazir bar igiam. 
\q1 Egh k…® gumazamizir manaba me bagh n…® amangam, 
\q2 n…® me bagh pura mang…®. 
\q1 Egh akar k…® bar n…® m…®kemeziba, 
\q2 n…® dar gun me m…®k…®m. 
\q1  
\v 8 K…® n…® ko ik…® egh n…®n akurvagham. 
\q2 Kamagh…®n, n…® men atiatingan mark…®. 
\q3 K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® n…® m…®kemegha g…®fa.‚Äù 
\b  
\p  
\v 9 Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God, uan dafarim isa nan akam gat…®gha, kamagh…®n m…®gei: 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄúN…® oragh. K…® dat…®r…®gh…®n uan akaba isa n…®n akam gar…®si, 
\q2 eght…® n…® dar gun m…®k…®mam. 
\q1  
\v 10 Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n dughiar kam…®n, k…® kantrin igharazir av…®ribar gumazamizibav k…®mamin gavgavim n…® gan…®di. 
\q2 Eght…® n…® biziba asiamin gavgavim, 
\q2 ko biziba ap…®rar…®ghamin gavgavim, 
\q2 ko bizibagh as…®ghas…®ghamin gavgavim, 
\q2 ko biziba d…®kab…®namin gavgavim, 
\q2 ko bizibar ingaramin gavgavim, 
\q2 ko biziba oparamin gavgavim, 
\q3 k…® bar da isa n…® gan…®di.‚Äù 
\s1 God bizir pumuning isa Jeremaian aka 
\p  
\v 11 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God g…®n kamagh…®n nan azara, ‚ÄúJeremaia, n…® tizim…®n gari?‚Äù Ez…® k…® a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® amon…®n temer aguam…®n gari.‚Äù  
\v 12 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, kamagh…®n na m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® deragha m…®gei. Kamagh…®n, k…® uab…® uan akam derav…®ram an gari. Eght…®, k…® m…®k…®mamin biziba guizbang…®ram otivam.‚Äù\f + \fr 1:12 \ft Hibrun akam, ‚ÄúAmon,‚Äù an akar otevir kam ko magh ghu, ‚ÄúN…® deragha gari.‚Äù\f* 
\p  
\v 13 Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God bizir igharazim nan akagha nan azara, ‚ÄúJeremaia, n…® tizim…®n gari?‚Äù Ez…® k…® a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® not…®n amadaghan gari m…®nem isiaghkua ikia, en amadaghan fuaghanadaghsava ami.‚Äù  
\v 14 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n na m…®gei, ‚ÄúBizir kam a kamak…®n: Bizir bar kurar mam not…®n amadaghan ikegh iz…®, en nguazir kam…®n gumazamiziba bar me gas…®ghas…®gham.  
\v 15 N…® gan! K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n n…® m…®gei, n…® deraghv…®ram oragh. K…® dat…®r…®gh…®n not…®n itir kantribar atrivibar diaght…®, me uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko izam. Eght…® atrivir kaba iz…® uan atrivir dabirabiba Jerusalem…®n tiar akabar borogh…®n dar afegham. Egh me nguibar ekiam aghuizir d…®vazir gavgaviba akararigham. Egh me uaghan Judan nguibar igharaziba kamagh…®ra dar amuam.  
\v 16 Nan gumazamiziba ak…®rim ragha na gasaragha, uari bagha marvir guabar ingarigha, dar damazim…®n dapaniba avia da bagha ofan mughuriar aghuiba zuibagh amua dar ziaba fe. Me kamagh…®n amua, bar arazir kuram gami. Kamagh…®n, k…® me is…® kot dat…®gham. 
\p  
\v 17 ‚ÄúEz…® Jeremaia, n…® uab…®ra uab…® ak…®righ d…®kavigh mang…® akar k…® n…® m…®kemeziba n…® dar gun me m…®k…®m. N…® men atiatingan mark…®, n…® atiatingt…® k…® n…® damight…®, n…® men damazibar bar atiatigham.  
\v 18 Jeremaia, n…® orakigh. K…® dat…®r…®gh…®n n…® gamiz…® n…® nguibam av…®nizir d…®vazir gavgavim…®n m…®n gavgavigha, mati ain…®n d…®penir ak…®nir guarim, ko d…®vazir me bras…®n ingarizim…®n m…®n gavgafi. Eght…® Judan atriviba ko, atrivim…®n ingangaribar faragha zuir gumazir dapaniba ko, ofa gamir gumaziba ko, nguazir kam…®n itir gumazamizir bar gavgaviba, me n…® d…®kab…®ragh n…® ab…®raghan kogham.  
\v 19 K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® m…®kemegha g…®fa, K…® uab…® n…® ko ik…® n…®n akurvagham. Eght…® gumazir kaba n…®n apanim…®n ik…®va, n…® d…®kab…®ragh n…® ab…®ns…® damuva avegham.‚Äù 
\c 2  
\ms1 Jeremaia God…®n akam Judaba ko Jerusalemia m…®k…®ri 
\mr (Sapta 2--25) 
\s1 Israelia dat…®r…®gh…®n  // Ikiav…®ra Itir God ataki 
\p  
\v 1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God na m…®g…®a ghaze: 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 ‚ÄúN…® Jerusalemia bagh mang…® nan akam…®n gun kamagh me m…®k…®m: 
\q1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God ghaze, ia bar faraghav…®ra nan gumazamizibar otivizir dughiam…®n, 
\q2 ia mati amizim igiamra pam…®n ikia uan pam gifongez…® mogh…®n, 
\q3 ia uari isa na ganigha na gifueghav…®ra iti. 
\q1 Egha ia na baghav…®ra ikia gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n nan g…®n zui, 
