\v 8 Ez…® nan ofa gamir gumaziba uaghan na g…®n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®. 
\q2 Ez…® Moses Osirizir Arazibagh fozir gumaziba, me uaghan na g…®fozir puvat…®. 
\q1 Ez…® ian atriviba, me ak…®rim ragha na gasara. 
\q2 Ez…® ian akam inigha izir gumazamiziba me asem, Bal, an ziam…®n gun m…®gei. 
