\v 12 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, 
\q1 ‚ÄòO overiam, n…® Israelian arazir kurar kam…®n gan…®va d…®gavir kuram damu. 
\q2 Egh n…® atiating navim ikuvigh mamagh…®ra ik…®. 
