\v 13 \x - \xo 2:13 \xt Aisaia 12:3; 65:11; Jeremaia 17:13\x*Nan gumazamiziba arazir kurar pumuning gami. 
\q2 K…® mati, d…®par aghuir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuim an…®dim me bagha fasfagha iri. 
