\v 12 \x - \xo 7:12-14 \xt Onger Akaba 78:60; Jeremaia 26:6\x*‚ÄúKamagh…®n, ia mang…® Silon nguibar k…® uan ziam fasa faragha inabazim…®n, k…® amizir bizibar ganigh. Nan gumazamiziba Israelia, me arazir kuram gami, kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® nguibar kam bar a gas…®ghas…®ki.\f + \fr 7:12 \ft Josuan dughiam…®n, Israelia Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Purirpenim Silon nguibam…®n anesara. (N…® Josua 18:1…®n an gan.) Ez…® ofa gamir gumazim Elin dughiam…®n, God…®n Purirpenim Silon iti. (N…® 1 Samuel 1-3…®n an gan.) Ez…® dughiar Filistiaba Israelia ab…®razir kam…®n me ti Silon nguibam gas…®ghas…®ki, ez…® g…®n nguibam pura ikiav…®ra iti. (N…® 1 Samuel 4…®n an gan.)\f* 
