\v 15 Egh ia Judaba, k…® Efraim…®n anabam…®n adarazi batoghez…® mogh…®n, ia batuegh ua ian ganan kogham.‚Äù\f + \fr 7:15 \ft Israelian akar kam, a fom…®ra not…®n amadaghan kantri Israel…®n adaraziv gei. N…® Jeremaia 3:7…®n ganigh.\f* 
