\v 18 \x - \xo 7:18 \xt Jeremaia 44:17-19\x*Men boriba dazibagh eghuva izima, afeziaba aviba ar…®si, ez…® amebaba bisketba tuasa plaua gami, kar aser amizir kam, Astarten me a bagha ofa gami, me a d…®bora ghaze, Overiam…®n Garir Atrivir Amizim. Egha me uaghan aser igharagha gariba bagha wain isa me bagha ofa gami. Me kamagh…®n amua paza na damuasava ami.  
