\v 23 \x - \xo 7:23 \xt Ua Me Ini 15:26; Ofa Gami 26:12; Aisaia 3:10\x*K…® kamagh…®n me m…®keme, ‚ÄòIa nan Akar Gavgavir k…® ia m…®geiba baragh deraghv…®ra dar g…®n mang…®t…®, k…® ian God…®n ik…®t…®, ia nan gumazamizibar m…®n ikiam. Eght…® biziba bar ian deragham.‚Äô  
