\v 34 \x - \xo 7:34 \xt Jeremaia 16:9; 25:10; Akar Mogomem 18:23\x*Eght…® gumazamiziba ua Judan nguibaba ko Jerusalem…®n tuavibar ikian kogham. K…® bizir kaba bar dar amight…®, da otivam, eght…® navir aghuim…®n arazim ko, agoroger arazim ko, poroghamir igiabar isar ekiaba, da bar g…®vagham. Eght…® kantrin kam…®n danganiba ikuvigh ikiam.‚Äù 
