\v 19 Ikiav…®ra Itir God na m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® mang…® nguibar ekiam…®n d…®vazim…®n tiar akar me kamagh…®n d…®borim, Gumazamizibar Tiarakam, n…® an borogh…®n tugh…®v ik…®. Kar Judan atrivibar nguibar ekiam…®n aven mang…®gh izegh gamir tiar akam. Egh n…® g…®n anetegh mang…® Jerusalem…®n tiar akar igharaziba uaghan bar dar borogh…®n tugh…®v ik…®.  
\v 20 Egh n…® gumazamiziba kamagh…®n me m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòIa Judan atriviba, ko Judan gumazamiziba, ko Jerusalemian tiar akar kam…®n mang…®gh izegh gamiba, ia deraghv…®ra kuariba arigh Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam baragh.  
\v 21 \x - \xo 17:21 \xt Nehemia 13:15-22\x*Ikiav…®ra Itir God, kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze: Ia deraghv…®ra uan ik…®r…®m…®rim bagh n…®ghn…®gh. Egh Ia Sabat…®n dughiam…®n biziba ater Jerusalem…®n aven mang…®s…®, tiar akar kabar aven mangan mark…®.  
\v 22 \x - \xo 17:22 \xt Ua Me Ini 20:8-10; God…®n Araziba 5:12-14\x*Egh ia uaghan Sabat…®n dughiam…®n, uan d…®penibar itir biziba ater daruan mark…®. Egh ingangaribar amuan mark…®. K…® ian inazir afeziabav kemez…® mogh…®n, ia Sabat…®n dughiam am…®seveght…®, a na baghv…®ra ik…®.  
\v 23 Ez…® ian ovaviba nan akam batuegha, nan g…®n zuir puvat…®gha, nan suren akar aghuiba baraghan aghua.  
\v 24 K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® ghaze: Ia nan akam barakigh! Ia Sabat…®n dughiam…®n biziba ater Jerusalem…®n aven izan mark…®. Ia Sabat…®n dughiam am…®seveght…® a nan dughiamra ik…®t…®, ia an ingangaritam bar a damuan mark…®. Ia nan akam…®n g…®n mang…®,  
\v 25 eght…® atriviba zurara Devit…®n ik…®zim…®n otivam, egh me Devit…®n ik…®zim…®n atrivir dabirabim dapiam. Eght…® atriviba uan gumazir aruaba ko, hoziabar apiagh, karisbar tuivigh Jerusalem…®n tiar akabar aven mang…® izegh damuam. Eght…® Judaba ko Jerusalemia tiar akar kabar mang…® izegh damuam. Egh dughiabar zurara gumazamiziba Jerusalem…®n ikiam.  
\v 26 Eght…® gumazamiziba Judan kantrin danganiba bar da ategh, uan ofaba inigh nan D…®penim…®n izam. Me Judan nguibar ekiaba ko, Jerusalem…®n borogh…®n itir nguibaba ko, Benjamin…®n anabam…®n nguazim ko, m…®ghs…®ar dozir aruem uaghiri nagh…®n itiba ko, m…®ghs…®aba itir danganir igharaziba ko, saut…®n amadaghan Negev iti nagh…®n, me danganir kaba bar da ategh, Jerusalem…®n izam. Me iz…®, as…®zir tue bar isia m…®gh…®rir ofaba ko, as…®zir igharazibar ofaba ko, witba tuer ofaba ko, mughuriar aghuim zuir ofaba ko, na m…®nabir ofaba, me da inigh na bagh Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n izam.  
\v 27 Egh ia nan akam…®n g…®n mangan aghuagh, Sabat…®n dughiam am…®seveght…® a nan dughiamra ikian kogh, ia biziba inigh Sabat…®n dughiam…®n Jerusalem…®n tiar akabar aven mang…®gh izegh damut…®, k…® tiar akar kaba avim dar at…®ght…® da isiam. Eght…® Jerusalem…®n itir d…®penir ekiaba bar isigham. Eght…® tav avir kam amungeghan kogham.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù 
\c 18  
\s1 God mati nguazir m…®nebar ingarir gumazim 
