\v 11 ‚ÄúJeremaia, n…® kamagh…®n Judaba ko Jerusalemia m…®k…®m, ‚ÄòK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® ghaze, ia oragh! Bizir kurar k…® ia damuamim, k…® anek…®righa g…®fa. K…® ivezir kuram ia dan…®ngasava ami. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia vaghvagh uan arazir kuraba ategh, uan dabirabiba ak…®righ arazir aghuibara g…®n mang…®.‚Äô  
\v 12 Eght…® gumazamiziba kamagh…®n n…®n akam ikaragham, ‚ÄòMark…® e aghua. E uari uan n…®ghn…®zibar g…®n mangasa ifonge. E bar mogh…®ra n…®n akam baraghan aghua, e uan navir averiar kurabar g…®n mangasa.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù 
