\v 18 Gumazamiziba kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúJeremaia guizbang…®ra akatam…®n m…®geir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n, e Jeremaia m…®soghs…® tuaviba buriam. E ghaze, Ofa gamir gumaziba suren akam akurir ingangarim atagh…®raghan kogham. Eght…® gumazir n…®ghn…®zir aghuim ko fofozir aghuiba itiba, me uan n…®ghn…®zim ko fofozir aghuim ateghan kogham. Eght…® akam inigha izir gumaziba God…®n akam e m…®k…®mv…®ra ikiam. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, e Jeremaia baraghan kogham. E a is…® kotiam dar…®gham.‚Äù 
