\v 19 Ez…® k…® Jeremaia, k…® kamagh…®n God ko m…®gei, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God, nan d…®mdiam barakigh. N…® nan apaniba m…®kemezir akam g…®n…®ghn…®gh.  
\v 20 Gumazitam arazir aghuim damut…®, gumaziba ti a ikaragh arazir kuram a dan…®ngam, o? Puvat…®. Eght…® gumazir kaba na gas…®ghasigham, me mati gumazim mozim gutui, eght…® as…®zim atamakuigh an mag…®r…®gham. N…®, arazir k…® fom…®ra amizim g…®n…®ghn…®gh. K…® n…®n borogh…®ra iza me bagha n…®n azangs…®gha ghaze, n…® uan an…®ngagharim ag…®vagh, gumazamizir kaba deraghv…®ra me damu.  
\v 21 Ez…® dat…®r…®k…®n, n…® men boribar amut…®, me dagheba puvat…®gh ar…®ghiregham. Egh apaniba ateght…®, me iz…® gumazitabav sueght…® me ar…®ghiregh. Eght…® gumazitaba ar…®mariar kurataba ini ar…®ghir…®. Eght…® gumazir igiaba m…®dorozim…®n ar…®ghir…®. Kamagh…®n, men amuiba boriba ko paba puvat…®gham.  
\v 22 Nan apaniba nan suiragh na gas…®ghas…®ghasa, mati as…®zim mozim…®n mag…®rasa mozim gutui, egha mati gumazim as…®zim…®n suighasa azuazim aguragha a m…®zua iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® zuam…®ra gumazir kuraba ameght…® me iz…® gumazir kaba ko m…®sogh, me gas…®ghas…®kigh, eght…® me bar puv…®ram atiating…®va, uan d…®penibar aven mongegh bar puv…®ram arangam.  
