\p  
\v 1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n na m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúJeremaia, n…® mang…®va nguazir m…®nebar ingarir gumazim da nguazir m…®netam givesegh. Egh m…®ner kam inigh mang…® gumazamizibar gumazir dapanir taba ko ofa gamir gumazibar dapanir taba inight…®, me n…® ko mang…®.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 19:2 \xt 2 Atriviba 23:10; Jeremaia 32:34-35\x*Egh ia mang…® Jerusalem…®n d…®vazim…®n tiar akar me kamagh…®n d…®borim, M…®neba B…®aghirezir Tiarakam, an borogh…®n mang…® Hinom…®n Danganir Zarim…®n otogh. Egh n…® kagh tugh nan akam akun suam,\f + \fr 19:2 \ft N…® Jeremaia 7:30-33…®n gan.\f* 
\v 3 ‚ÄòIa Judan atriviba ko Jerusalem…®n gumazamiziba, ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam baragh! K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, Israelian God, k…® guizbang…®ra m…®gei. K…® bizir bar kuram damight…®, a danganir kam…®n otivam. Eght…® gumazamizir bizir otivamin kam…®n akaba bareghamiba, me bar d…®gavir kuram damigham.  
\v 4 K…® kamagh…®n damuamin bizim…®n m…®ngarim, a kamak…®n, gumazamizir kaba ak…®rim ragha na gasaragha, aseba bagha ofan m…®gharir mughuriar aghuim zuibagh ami. Gumazamizir kaba, ko men ovaviba, ko Judan atriviba, me fom…®ra aser kabagh fozir puvat…®. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n, me aser kabar ziaba fe, egha arazir kam…®n me danganir kam gamima a nan damazim…®n bar m…®ze. Me uaghan pura gumazamizir arazir kurabagh amir puvat…®zir av…®ribav soghez…®, me ariaghirez…® men ghuziba danganir kam gire.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 19:5 \xt Ofa Gami 18:21\x*Egha me Jerusalem…®n asem Bal…®n ziam fasa danganibar ingarigha, uari uan boriba isa ofan bar isia m…®gh…®ribar m…®n, avim…®n da tua asem Bal bagha ofa gami. Arazir ia amizir kam a nan arazim puvat…®. K…® kamagh…®n arazir kam damuasa me m…®kemezir puvat…®. Bar puvat…®. Egha uaghan arazir kamagh garir tam k…® me dan…®ngasa n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®.  
\v 6 Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God ghaze, me g…®n ua danganir kam…®n ziam, Tofet o Hinom…®n Danganir Zarim a dar…®ghan kogham. Puvat…®. Me kamagh…®n danganir kam d…®ponam, Danganir Zarir Gumazir Av…®ribav Sozi Me Ariaghirim! 
\p  
\v 7 ‚Äú‚Äâ‚ÄòJudaba ko Jerusalemia danganir kam…®n bizir av…®ribar amuasa n…®ghn…®si, ez…® k…® men tuavim ap…®right…® me dar amighan kogham. Eght…® k…® apaniba ameght…®, me iz…® me m…®sueght…® me ar…®m…®ghiregham. Eght…® k…® kuaraziba ko as…®zir atiaba ameght…®, da iz…® men kuabar amegham.  
