\v 9 Apaniba Jerusalemia m…®soghs…®, iz…® men nguibar ekiam av…®nigham. Eght…® bizir kam an os…®mt…®zir bar ekiam Jerusalemia danight…®, dagheba bar men puvat…®gham. Eght…® gumazamiziba uari uan boribav sogh dar am…®va, egh uari uan namakabav sogh me amam.‚Äô\f + \fr 19:9 \ft Hibrun akam deragha m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®. Gumazamiziba ti igharaz daraziv sogh me amam, akar kamagh…®n amizim 2 Atriviba 6:26-29…®n iti. O me ti igharaz darazir kuabar m…®karzibar as…®zibar amam, mati Azirakam 2:20 ko 4:10…®n iti? E derav…®ra foghan kogham.\f* 
\p  
\v 10 ‚ÄúJeremaia, n…® akam akunt…® gumazamiziba n…® baragh n…®n gant…®, n…® nguazir m…®ner n…® suirazim n…® anem…®sarar…®kigh.  
\v 11 Egh kamagh…®n me m…®k…®m, ‚ÄòIkiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze: K…® Judan kantrin gumazamiziba ko Jerusalem…®n gumazamiziba bar, nguazir m…®nem am…®saraghar…®ghiz…® mogh…®n me m…®sararigham. Eght…® gumazitam uam anek…®righan kogham. Eght…® Tofet…®n danganim, Judabar matmat…®n m…®n otoght…®, men kuaba danganir kam bar a giz…®vagham.  
