\v 1-2 \x - \xo 21:1-2 \xt 2 Atriviba 25:1-11; 2 Eghaghaniba 36:17-21\x*Atrivim Sedekaia, gumazir pumuning Jeremaia bagha aning amada. Aning…®n ziamning, Malkian otarim Pasur, ko Masean otarim Sefanaia, an ofa gamir gumazir mam. Aning Jeremaia m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúBabilon…®n Atrivim Nebukatnesar, e ko m…®sosi. Ez…® n…® e bagh Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n azaraght…®, an en akuraghasa e ifonge. A ti e bagh mirakel…®n tam damigham, a fom…®ra en adarazi bagha amiz…® mok…®n. Eght…® a mirakel…®n kam Atrivim Nebukatnesar damight…® anetegh mangam.‚Äù Me m…®geima, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, m…®g…®r…®g…®am isa Jeremaia gan…®di. 
