\v 9 Eght…® gumazamizir nguibar ekiar kam…®n aven itiba, me ar…®m…®ghiregham. Apaniba iz…® me m…®sogham, eght…® tarazi dagheba men puvat…®ght…® me ar…®m…®ghiregham, eght…® tarazi ar…®mariar kuram me gas…®ghasight…®, me ar…®m…®ghiregham. Eght…® gumazamizir angam…®ra ikiasa ifongeziba, me nguibar ekiar kam ategh mang…® pura uari is…®, Babilonian d…®vazim…®n azenan ikia m…®soghasa garir darazi pura uari is…® me danigh, men g…®n mang…®, angam…®ra ik…® mati apaniba m…®dorozim gafiragha suirazir pura ingangarir gumazamizibar k…®nibar m…®n ikiam.  
\v 10 K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® guizbang…®ra m…®g…®a ghaze, K…® Jerusalem…®n nguibar ekiam gas…®ghas…®ghasa n…®ghnigha g…®fa. K…® ua deraghv…®ra a damuan aghua. K…® Babilon…®n atrivim…®n amamangat…®ght…®, a nguibar ekiar kam inigh uan m…®dorozir gumazibav kemeght…®, me a daboroght…®, a bar mogh…®ra isigh ikuvigh puvat…®gham.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù 
