\v 25 Egh k…® n…® is…® n…® gas…®ghas…®ghamin gumazibar anigam, kar n…® atiatir gumaziba. K…® Babilon…®n Atrivim Nebukatnesar uan Kaldian m…®dorozir gumaziba ko me m…®gei.  
