\p  
\v 1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa gumazir dapaniba, Iavzika! Ia bar ikuvigham. Ia nan gumazamiziba paza me gami. Ia sipsipbar gari gumazir kuraba, ia men ag…®nt…®gha me gas…®ghas…®zima me tintinibar zui.  
\v 2 Kamagh…®n, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Israelian God, k…® bighav…®ra gumazir dapanir nan gumazamizibagh ativiba me m…®g…®a ghaze, Ia nan sipsipba batogha men ag…®nt…®zi me tintinibar ara ghue. Ia deragha men gara me geghuvir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® ghaze, ia amizir arazir kurar kam, k…® deraghv…®ra an gan egh a ikarvagham.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 23:3 \xt Jeremaia 32:37; Esekiel 34:13\x*Gumazamizir k…® amangiz…® ghua kantrin igharazibar itiba, k…® ua men ikiav…®ra itir varazira aku iz…® me is…® men d…®vazim…®n aven me ar…®gham. Eght…® me borir av…®riba bat…®va bar av…®rasemegham.  
