\p  
\v 5 \x - \xo 23:5-6 \xt Jeremaia 33:14-16\x*‚ÄúK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, Dughiam iz…®t…®, k…® Atrivim Devit…®n adarazir tong…®n, gumazir aghui tam am…®sevegham. Eght…® a Temer Ghuzir Igiam temer dakam…®n otogha aghui mogh…®n ikiam. Gumazir kam atrivim…®n ik…®, n…®ghn…®zir aghuim ik…®, ingangarim damuam. Egh guiz…®n arazim…®n g…®n mang…® nguazir kam…®n gumazamiziba arazir aghuibar me damuam.  
\v 6 Eght…® an atrivim…®n ikiamin dughiam…®n, Israel…®n nguibam…®n itir darasi, me dabirabir aghuim ko navir am…®rizim…®n ikiam. Eght…® Judaba, God men akurvaght…®, me uam os…®mt…®ziba puvat…®gh derav…®ra ikiam. Eght…® me Jerusalem ziar kam a dar…®gh a d…®ponam, ‚ÄòIkiav…®ra Itir God, A Guiz…®n Arazir Aghuim…®n M…®ngarim.‚Äô 
