\v 16 Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim kamagh…®n Jerusalemia m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa God…®n akam inigha izir gumaziba m…®geir akaba baraghan mark…®. Me ia gifara ghaze ia deraghv…®ra ikiam. Me uan n…®ghn…®zibar aven irebabar m…®n garir bizibar gara ia m…®gei. K…® akar kaba me gan…®di puvat…®.  
\v 17 Gumazamizir nan akam baraghan aghuaziba, akam inigha izir gumazir kaba kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄòIa dabirabir aghuim ikiam.‚Äô Egha gumazamizir akaba batogha, uan n…®ghn…®zibar g…®n zuiba, akam inigha izir gumazir kaba, kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄòBizir kuram, ia bativan kogham.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù 
