\v 27 Me uari uan irebabar gun uarira uariv gei, egha me ghaze bizir kam gumazamizibar amut…®, me na g…®n amadagham, mati men inazir afeziaba fom…®ra na g…®n amadagha, asem Bal bagha tevibar p…®ra an ziam fe.  
