\p  
\v 33 Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n Jeremaia m…®keme, ‚ÄúGumazamiziba o, God…®n akam inigha izir gumaziba o, ofa gamir gumazitam, me ti iz…® kamagh…®n n…®n azangs…®gham, ‚ÄòIkiav…®ra Itir God, akar os…®mt…®zim ititam iti, o puvat…®?‚Äô Eght…® n…® a ikaragh nan akar kam…®n gun m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® akam ian iti. Iarara os…®mt…®zim na gat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® ia batuegham.‚Äô\f + \fr 23:33 \ft Me Hibrun akam…®n aven, akar kam, ‚Äúakam,‚Äù ko akar kam, ‚Äúos…®mt…®zim,‚Äù aning…®n arerem vorogh…®ra ghu. Akar kam…®n arerem, a m…®ngarir pumuning iti. Jerusalemia kamagh…®n a g…®n…®ghn…®gha d…®bovir akabar kamagh…®n a d…®bori, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam bar oseme.‚Äù\f* 
\v 34 Eght…® akam inigha izir gumazitam o, ofa gamir gumazitam o, gumazir k…®nitam, ti kamagh…®n m…®k…®mam, ‚ÄòIkiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam, bar oseme.‚Äô Eght…® k…® gumazir kam ikarvagh os…®mt…®zim a dan…®ng…®va, an adarazi sara os…®mt…®zim me dan…®ngam.  
\v 35 Ia uan namakaba ko aveghbuabav geir dughiam…®n, ia kamagh…®n m…®k…®m, ‚ÄòIkiav…®ra Itir God, manmagh…®n akam ikara?‚Äô o ‚ÄòIkiav…®ra Itir God, akar manam m…®keme?‚Äô  
\v 36 Eght…® ia ua kamagh…®n m…®k…®man mark…®, ‚ÄòIkiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam, a bar oseme.‚Äô Puvat…®. Ian akabara, os…®mt…®zim ia gan…®di. Ez…® ia uari nan akam adavadafi. K…® God…®n zurara ikia mamagh…®ra itim. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, k…® ian God.  
\v 37 Eght…® gumazitam akam inigha izir gumazitam…®n azangs…®ghs…®, a kamagh…®n m…®k…®m, ‚ÄòIkiav…®ra Itir God akar manam…®n n…® ikara?‚Äô o ‚ÄòIkiav…®ra Itir God manmagh…®ra m…®keme?‚Äô  
\v 38 Eght…® ia kamagh…®n m…®k…®mam, ‚ÄòIkiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam bar oseme,‚Äô k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® deraghav…®ra ia m…®gei. K…® akar kam…®n m…®k…®man ian anogoroke, ez…® ia nan akam batuegha ua m…®gei, ‚ÄòIkiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam bar oseme.‚Äô  
\v 39 Ez…® guizbang…®ra, k…® ia inigh ia asirafagh, ia akunight…® ia nan saghuiam…®n mang…®gham. K…® kamagh…®ra ia damuva, ia ko ian ovavibagh an…®ngizir nguibar ekiar kam, k…® uaghan a makunigham.  
\v 40 K…® ia damight…®, gumazir igharaziba d…®bovir akaba ia gas…®t…®, ia bar aghumsigham. Eght…® aghums…®zir kam ik…® mamagh…®ra ikiam, eght…® ia a g…®n amadaghan kogham.‚Äù 
\c 24  
\s1 K…® Jeremaia, k…® figh…®n temebar ov…®zibar gani 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 24:1 \xt 2 Atriviba 24:12-16; 2 Eghaghaniba 36:10\x*Babilon…®n Atrivim Nebukatnesar, Jerusalem ab…®ragha g…®vagha, Judaba inigha ua Babilon…®n ghu. A uaghan Atrivim Jehoiakim…®n otarim ini, otarir kam…®n ziar mam Jehoiakin, an ziar igharazim Jekonia. Egha a uaghan Judan gumazir ekiaba ko fofozir gumazir, bizir aghuibar ingariba ko ain…®n bizibar ingarir gumaziba sara inigha Jerusalem ataki. Ez…® bizir kabar g…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God bizir mam irebam…®n m…®n garir bizim…®n aven nan aka, ez…® an aven k…® ak…®rar pumuning…®n garima, figh…®n ov…®ziba ak…®rar kamning…®n iti. Ak…®rar kamning, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n tiar akam…®n borogh…®n iti.  
\v 2 Figh…®n ov…®zir faragha azenibar ania iti mogh…®n, ak…®rar mam figh…®n ov…®zir bar aghuiba an iti. Ez…® ak…®rar igharazim figh…®n ov…®zir bar kuraba an iti, ez…® gumazamiziba dar aman iburagham.  
\v 3 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n na m…®gei, ‚ÄúJeremaia, n…® bizir tizim…®n gari?‚Äù Ez…® k…® kamagh…®n a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® figh…®n ov…®zibar gari. Figh…®n aghuiba da bar dera, ez…® figh…®n kuraba, da bar ikufi, gumaziba dar aman iburagham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 4 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God akar mam na gan…®ngi. Akar kam kamak…®n:  
\v 5 ‚ÄúK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Israelian God, k…® ghaze, Judan gumazamizir k…® me batoghez…®, me ghua Kaldian nguazim…®n ghueziba, k…® men garima, me mati figh…®n ov…®zir aghuiba.  
\v 6 Ez…® k…® bar deraghv…®ra men gan…®va, deraghv…®ra me geghuvam. Egh ua me inigh nguazir kam…®n izam. K…® gavgavim me dan…®ng me ab…®nan kogham. K…® me akaragh me asian kogham.  
\v 7 Egh k…® men navir averiabar aven n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba me dan…®ngt…®, me kamagh…®n fogh suam, K…® uab…®, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God. Eght…® me ua na bagha iz…®va, na ko navir vam…®ran ikiam. Egh nan gumazamizibar otivight…®, k…® men God…®n ikiam. 
\p  
\v 8 ‚ÄúK…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® kamagh…®n m…®gei: K…® Atrivim Sedekaia uan gumazir dapaniba ko, Jerusalemian gumazamizir uan nguazim…®n ikiav…®ra itir varazira, ko gumazamizir Isip…®n ghueziba, k…® gumazamizir kaba paz…® me damigham, mati gumazim paza figh…®n ov…®zir kurar gumaziba daman iburazibagh ami.  
\v 9-10 Eght…® Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba, k…® Judan amizir biziba baregh, d…®gavir kuram damigh, egh bar atiatigham. Guizbang…®ra, k…® apaniba ameght…® me iz…® Judan gumazamizir ikiav…®ra itibav sueght…® me ar…®ghiregham, eght…® tarazi dagheba puvat…®gh ar…®ghiram, eght…® ar…®mariar kuram tarazigh as…®ghasight…® me ar…®m…®ghiram. K…® me batueght…® me tintinibar mangegham. Eght…® arazir kam…®n, k…® nguazir ia ko ian ovavibagh an…®ngizir kam…®n aven, k…® bar ia ag…®vagham. Eght…® kantrin igharazir kabar gumazamiziba, k…® Judaba batoghez…® me dar ghueziba, me paz…®v…®ra me damuva me d…®povam. Egh gumazamizir kaba uan apanibar atar akar kurabar me m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòIa Judaba ikuviz…® mogh…®n, ia ikuvigham.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù 
\c 25  
\s1 Atrivim Nebukatnesar Judabagh as…®ghas…®gham 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 25:1 \xt 2 Atriviba 24:1; 2 Eghaghaniba 36:5-7; Daniel 1:1-2\x*Ikiav…®ra Itir God Judabav k…®mamin akam iti, egha akar kam isa Jeremaia gan…®ngi. Dughiar kam…®n Josaian otarim Jehoiakim, a Judabar atrivim…®n itima, an namba 4…®n azenim oto. Ez…® Nebukatnesar Babilon…®n atrivim itima an namba 1…®n azenim oto.  
\v 2 Ez…® God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Jeremaia akar kam Judaba ko Jerusalemia m…®k…®ri. A kamagh…®n me m…®keme: 
\p  
\v 3 Emon…®n otarim Josaia, a Judabar atrivim…®n itima, an namba 13…®n azenim…®n, k…® Jeremaia Ikiav…®ra Itir God na gan…®ngizir akam akurav…®ra ikia iza namba 23…®n azenim g…®fa. Ez…® ia a baraghan aghua.  
\v 4 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ia bagha dughiar av…®ribar uan akam inigha izir gumaziba amadi, kar an ingangarir gumaziba. Ez…® ia uan kuariba ap…®righa men akaba baraghan aghua.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 25:5 \xt 2 Atriviba 17:13; Jeremaia 18:11\x*God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir kaba ghaze, ‚ÄúIa bar vaghvagh navibagh iragh, tuavir kurar ia g…®n zuim atakigh, egh arazir kurar ia amiba atakigh. Egh arazir kaba ateght…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God ia ateght…®, ia nguazir a ia ko ian ovavibagh an…®ngizir nguazim…®n deraghv…®ra ik…® mamagh…®ra ikiam.  
\v 6 Ia asebar g…®n mang…® egh dar ziaba f…®va dar ingangaribar amuan mark…®. Egh ia aser kabar marvir guabar ingar…®va, Ikiav…®ra Itir God damut…®, a ian an…®ngaghan mark…®. Ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam…®n g…®n mang…®t…®, a paz…® ia damighan kogham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 7 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® guizbang…®ra m…®gei, Nan akam inigha izir gumazim nan akar kam…®n gun m…®kemez…®, ia nan akam baraghan aghua. Puvat…®. Ia asebar marvir guabar ingara, na gamima, k…® an…®ngaghe. Ez…® arazir kam bang…®n, ia paza uarira uarigh ami. 
\p  
\v 8 ‚ÄúKamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, k…® ghaze, ia nan akam baraghan aghua.  
\v 9 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia oragh! K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® not…®n amadaghan itir ik…®zibar diagh…®va, egh uaghan Babilon…®n Atrivim Nebukatnesar, an diagham, a nan ingangarir gumazim…®n m…®n ami. Egh k…® me inigh iz…®t…®, me nguazir kam ko an borogh…®n itir kantriba dagh as…®ghas…®gham. Eght…® me ikuvigh mamagh…®ra ikiam. Eght…® gumazamizir igharaziba men ganigh, ak…®rim ragh me gas…® d…®bovir akabar me m…®k…®m…®va, egh d…®gavir kuram damuva, egh puv…®ram atiatingam. Eght…® nguazir kam…®n gumazamiziba aghums…®zim ik…® mamagh…®ra ikiam.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 25:10 \xt Aisaia 24:7; Jeremaia 7:34; 16:9; Esekiel 26:13; Hosea 2:11; Akar Mogomem 18:22-23\x*Egh k…® men navir aghuim…®n agoroger arazim ko, bar akongezir arazim ko, gumaziba amuibar ikiamin arazim, k…® bar ada g…®vagham. Eght…® wit…®n ov…®ziba m…®rm…®ramin gumaziba puvat…®gham, kamagh…®n wit m…®rm…®ramin dag…®aba ua t…®ngaghan kogham. Eght…® lam…®n angazangariba ua danganir kam…®n puvat…®gham.  
\v 11 \x - \xo 25:11 \xt 2 Eghaghaniba 36:21; Jeremaia 29:10; Daniel 9:2\x*Eght…® nguazir kam bar ikuvigh danganir k…®nim otogham. Eght…® 70plan azenibar, nan gumazamizir kaba, Babilon…®n atrivim…®n ingangarir gumazir k…®nibar ikiam. 
\p  
\v 12 ‚ÄúEght…® 70plan azeniba g…®vaght…®ma, k…® Babilon…®n atrivim ko an gumazamiziba, k…® men arazir kurar me amiba ikarvagh puv me damigham. Egh Babilon…®n kantri gas…®ghasigham, an ziar mam Kaldia. Eght…® Babilon…®n nguazim pura ik…® mamagh…®ra ikiam.  
\v 13 K…® Babilon gas…®ghas…®ghasa m…®kemezir biziba, Jeremaia bar adav keme. K…® bizir kaba bar dar amut…®, da otivigham. Jeremaia osirizir ak…®nafarir kam, k…® kantriba bar dagh as…®ghas…®ghasa m…®kemezir akaba bar an iti.  
\v 14 K…® ivezir kuram is…® Babilon…®n gumazamiziba, men arazir kurar me amiziba bagh me dan…®ngam. Eght…® kantrin igharazir av…®ribar atrivir gavgaviba me d…®kab…®n me damut…®, me pura ingangarir gumazamizir k…®nibar m…®n ingangarim damuam.‚Äù 
\s1 God gumazamiziba bar me gas…®ghas…®ghasa 
\p  
\v 15 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, a Israelian God, a kamagh…®n na m…®gei, ‚ÄúJeremaia, wain…®n kav…®n k…® suirazir kam, kar nan an…®ngagharim…®n ababanim. N…® kav…®n kam inight…®, k…® n…® amadaght…®, n…® gumazamizir av…®riba bagh mang…®gh, me damight…®, me wain…®n kav…®n kam…®n itim am…®.  
\v 16 Eght…® k…® apaniba ameght…®, me, me m…®sogh…®va, me gas…®ghasigham, kamagh…®n me mati, me wain…®n d…®par kabar amegh g…®vagh, gumazir onganibar m…®n otivigh, bar paz…®v…®ra daruam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 17 Ez…® k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n dafarim…®n wain…®n kav…®n kam inigha, gumazamizir kaba bagha ghugha, me gamiz…®ma me aneme.\f + \fr 25:17 \ft Jeremaia kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, gumazamiziba amezir kav…®n d…®par kam…®n akar is…®n zuim kamak…®n: God men arazir kuraba ikarvagh ivezim kuram me dan…®ngam. N…® Jeremaia 46-51…®n uaghan an gan.\f* 
\v 18 K…® faragha ghua Jerusalem ko Judan nguibar igharaziba, ko atriviba, ko Judan gumazir dapaniba, k…® me gamiz…®, me wain…®n d…®par kam ame. Egha Judan atrivim ko gumazir dapaniba bar ikuviz…®, nguazir kam pura nguazir k…®nim…®n oto. Ez…® gumazamizir igharaziba Judan kantrin gara, ak…®rim ragha me gasa d…®bovir akabar me m…®g…®a, bar d…®gavir kuram gamua, puv…®ram atiati. Egha gumazamizir kaba akar kurabar uari uan apanibav k…®masa, kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa Judaba ikuviz…® mogh…®n ia ikuvigham.‚Äù Bizir kaba dat…®r…®gh…®n bar mogh…®ra otivigha g…®fa.  
\v 19 Ez…® k…® wain…®n kav…®n kam inigha ghua, Isip…®n atrivim ko, an ingangarir gumaziba ko, an gumazir dapaniba ko, an gumazamiziba ko,  
\v 20 gumazamizir igharazir Isip…®n tong…®n itiba sara bar me gan…®ngi. Egha k…® ghua Us…®n nguazim…®n atriviba ko, Filistian nguazim…®n atriviba sara, k…® bar me gan…®ngi. Filistia nguibar kaba iti: Askelon, Gasa ko, Ekron ko Asdot…®n nguibam…®n ikiav…®ra itir varazira.  
\v 21 Ez…® k…® wain…®n kav…®n kam inigha ghua, Idom…®n kantri ko, Moap…®n kantri ko, Amonia ko,  
\v 22 Tair…®n atriviba ko, Saidon…®n atriviba ko, ongarim…®n vong…®n itir nguibabar atriviba sara, k…® bar me gan…®ngi.  
\v 23 Egha k…® ghua Dedan…®n gumazamiziba ko, Teman gumazamiziba ko, Bus…®n gumazamiziba ko, gumazamizir uan dapanir m…®nedevir ar…®zibar p…®ra da oteviba, sara bar me gan…®ngi.  
\v 24 Egha k…® ghua Arebian atriviba ko, gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n itir ik…®zir igharagha gariba, men atrivibagh an…®ngi.  
\v 25 Egha ghua Simrin atriviba ko, Elam…®n kantrin atriviba ko, Midian kantrin atriviba ko,  
\v 26 nguazir not…®n amadaghan itibar atriviba, men marazi saghon itima, marazi rogh…®ra iti, k…® vaghvagha bar me gan…®ngi. K…® nguazir kam…®n kantriba bar dar atriviba, k…® bar me gan…®ngi, ez…® me aneme. Ez…® bar abuan Babilon…®n atrivim abuananam ame. 
\p  
\v 27 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n na m…®keme, ‚ÄúJeremaia, n…® akar kam gumazamizir kabav kemegh. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, Israelian God, k…® kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòK…® apaniba amadaght…®, me iz…® ia m…®sogh ia gas…®ghas…®gham, eght…® ia wain…®n d…®par kam am…® mang…®v…®ra ik…® wain…®n d…®par bar av…®ribar am…®va, ia bar onganigh, migh…®va nguazim giregh ua d…®kavan kogham.‚Äô  
\v 28 Jeremaia, me ti n…®n dafarim…®n kav…®n kam inian aghuaght…®, n…® kamagh…®n me m…®k…®m, ‚ÄòK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, k…® m…®keme, ia a inigh anerem…®!  
\v 29 Ia oragh! K…® nguazir kam…®n gumazamiziba bar paz…®v…®ra me damigham. K…® Jerusalem…®n bizir kam faragh a damuam, kar nan nguibamra, k…® uan ziam fasa a ginaba. Ez…® ia ti ghaze, k…® ia gitagham, a? Bar puvat…®. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, k…® m…®keme, k…® apaniba ateght…® me mang…® nguazir kam…®n gumazamiziba bar me m…®sogham.‚Äô 
\p  
\v 30 ‚ÄúJeremaia, k…® n…® gan…®ngizir akaba, n…® bar adar gun m…®kemegh. N…® gumazamizir kaba kamagh…®n me m…®kemegh: 
\b  
\q1 ‚Äú‚Äâ‚ÄòIkiav…®ra Itir God uan Nguibam…®n overiam…®n ik…®va, 
\q2 pamtem…®n tiarim akarigh uan gumazamizibav k…®mam. 
\q1 A pamtem…®n nguazir kam…®n uan gumazamizibar diagham, 
\q2 mati gumaziba wain…®n d…®paba otivasa wain…®n ov…®ziba d…®ka dei mogh…®n d…®mam. 
\q1  
\v 31 An d…®md…®ar kam…®n n…®g…®nim, bar nguazim avaragham. 
\q2 Ez…® d…®md…®ar kam…®n m…®ngarim kamak…®n. 
\q1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God nguazir kam…®n gumazamiziba bar me tuis…®gham. 
\q2 A kantriba bar dar gumazamiziba isi kot dar…®gham. 
\q1 Egh ana apaniba ameght…® me mang…®va, 
\q2 gumazamizir arazir kurabagh amibav soght…®, me ar…®m…®ghiram. 
\q3 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, a kamagh…®n m…®keme. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 32 ‚Äú‚Äâ‚ÄòIkiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, kamagh…®n m…®keme: 
\q2 Ia oragh. Kantriba bar ikuvigham. 
\q1 Bizir kam, faragh kantrin tam…®n otogham, 
\q2 egh mang…® bar kantribar otivam. 
\q1 Ez…® as…®ghas…®zir kam, mati am…®nir ekiam bar saghon d…®kavigha iva iza 
\q2 nguazim bar a garui.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù 
\b  
\p  
\v 33 Eght…® dughiar kam…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God gumazamizibav m…®soght…® me ar…®ghir…®t…®, men kuaba tintinibar nguibaba bar dar ikiam. Eght…® men apangkuv aziva, men kuaba akuva, me afamin gumaziba puvat…®gham. Men kuaba afiar buaribar m…®n tintinibar nguazim…®n ir…®v ikiam. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 34 Ia gumazamizibar gumazir dapaniba ko me geghuva men gariba, 
\q2 mati sipsipbar garir gumaziba uan sipsipbagh eghufi, ia bar puv…®rama azi. 
\q1 Apaniba iz…® ia m…®soght…® ia ar…®m…®ghiramin dughiam otogha g…®fa. 
\q2 Eght…® g…®n me gumazamizir ikiav…®ra itiba batuegham. 
\q1 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia nguazim giregh a g…®poghpogh. 
\q2 Ia nguazir m…®ner aghuim ir…®gha b…®aghirez…® mogh…®n, ia iregh bar ikuvigham. 
\q1  
\v 35 Sipsipbagh eghuvir gumaziba, 
\q2 ia ar…® mang…® bizir kurar kam gitaghamin mogomer danganiba puvat…®. 
\q1  
\v 36 Ikiav…®ra Itir God danganir men sipsipba apir grazibagh as…®ghas…®ki. 
\q2 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia oragh! 
\q3 Dat…®r…®gh…®n sipsipbagh eghuvir gumaziba bar puv aziava arai. 
\q1  
\v 37 Ikiav…®ra Itir God bar puv…®ram ian an…®ngaghe. 
\q2 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a mati sipsipba avughsa n…®m…®ra itir danganir grazir aghuiba itibagh as…®ghas…®ki. 
\q1  
\v 38 Ikiav…®ra Itir God d…®kavigha, laion…®n m…®n uan danganir mogomem ataki. 
\q2 Ikiav…®ra Itir God bar an…®ngaghegha apaniba amangiz…®, me iza Judabav sosi. 
\q3 Ez…® men nguazim bar ikuvigha, danganir k…®nim gava. 
\c 26  
\ms1 Gumazir dapaniba ko gumazamiziba Jeremaian akam batoke 
\mr (Sapta 26--36) 
\s1 Gumazamiziba Jeremaia m…®sueght…® an aremeghasa 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 26:1 \xt 2 Atriviba 23:36--24:6; 2 Eghaghaniba 36:5-7\x*Josaian otarim Jehoiakim, a Judan atrivim…®n otivir dughiam…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, kamagh…®n Jeremaia m…®gei,  
\v 2 ‚ÄúK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® kamagh…®n m…®gei: N…® mang…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim av…®nizir d…®vazim…®n aven mang…®, me uari akuvir Danganim…®n tugh…®v ik…®va, Judan itir nguibabar gumazamiziba akam bar me m…®k…®m. Kar gumazamizir nan D…®penim…®n aven iza nan ziam feba. Eght…® akar k…® n…® gan…®ngiziba, n…® me m…®kemegh. N…® akatam atagh…®raghan mark…®.  
\v 3 Egh dughiar n…® nan akaba bar ada akunam, eght…® gumazamiziba n…®n akam baragh, egh navibagh iragh, egh arazir kurar me amiba ategham. Eght…® k…® n…®ghn…®zim giragh, bizir kurar k…® me damuasa m…®kemezibar amuan kogham.  
\v 4 N…® akar kam…®n me m…®kemegh, ‚ÄòIkiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n ia m…®k…®masa: Ia nan akam baragh, k…® ia gan…®ngizir Arazibar g…®n mang…®.  
\v 5 Egh nan akam inigha izir gumaziba, me nan ingangarir gumaziba, me ia gan…®ngizir akaba, ia bar dar g…®n mang…®. Dughiar av…®ribar k…® akam inigha izir gumaziba amadima, me iza akam ia m…®k…®ri, ez…® ia men akabar g…®n zuir puvat…®.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 26:6 \xt Josua 18:1; Onger Akaba 78:60; Jeremaia 7:12-14\x*Egh ia nan akam batueght…®, k…® D…®penir kam gas…®ghasigham. Mati k…® fom…®ra uan d…®penim Silon nguibam…®n a gamiz…® mok…®n. Eght…® nguibar igharazibar gumazamiziba g…®n uan apaniba akar kurabar me m…®k…®ms…®, me kamagh…®n me m…®k…®mam, ‚ÄúIa Jerusalemia ikuviz…® mogh…®n ia ikuvigham.‚Äù ‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù 
\p  
\v 7-8 Ez…® Jeremaia d…®kavigha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n ghugha, Ikiav…®ra Itir God a m…®kemezir akar kaba bar dar gun gumazamiziba bar me m…®keme. Ez…® ofa gamir gumaziba ko, akam inigha izir gumaziba ko, gumazamiziba bar akam baraki. Ez…® Jeremaia m…®kemegha g…®vaz…®ma, ofa gamir gumaziba ko, akam inigha izir gumaziba ko, gumazamiziba bar an suigha ghaze, ‚ÄúNa aremegh.  
\v 9 Manmaghsua n…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam…®n, akar kurar kam akuri? N…® kamagh…®n m…®k…®man mark…®, D…®penir kam Silo ikuviz…® mogh…®n a ikuvigham. Egh n…® kamagh…®n m…®k…®man mark…®, nguibar kam ikuvigham, eght…® gumazamiziba uam an ikian kogham.‚Äù Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim av…®nizir d…®vazim…®n aven itir gumazamiziba, me bar iza Jeremaia ek…®aru. 
\p  
\v 10 Ez…® dughiar kam…®n Judan gumazir dapaniba atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n ikia, egha bizir kabar akaba barasi. Egha me d…®kavigha ghuavanaga, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim av…®nizir tiar akam…®n otifi. Egha me uan dabirabibagh apia. Men dabirabiba Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n av…®nizir d…®vazim…®n aven mangamin tiar akam borogh…®n iti, tiar akar me kamagh…®n d…®borim, Tiarakar Igiam.  
\v 11 Ez…® ofa gamir gumaziba ko, akam inigha izir gumaziba ko, gumazir dapaniba ko, gumazamiziba bar mogh…®ra me m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazir kam kamagh…®n m…®keme, nguibar ekiar kam ikuvigham. Ia uari an akar kam baraki. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, bizir kam bang…®n, an aremegham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 12 Ez…® gumazir dapaniba ko, gumazamiziba bar mogh…®ra, Jeremaia kamagh…®n men akaba ikara, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God uab…® na amadaz…®, k…® akam inigha izir gumazim…®n akar ia oraghizir kam, an gun m…®keme. A uab…® ghaze, D…®penir kam ko nguibar ekiar kam ikuvigham.  
\v 13 \x - \xo 26:13 \xt Jeremaia 7:3; 26:3; 26:19\x*Eght…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ia uan daroriba ko arazibar k…®righ. Egh ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God…®n akam…®n g…®n mang…®. Egh ia kamagh…®n damight…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God uan n…®ghn…®zim giragh…®va, bizir a ia gas…®ghas…®ghasa m…®kemezibar amighan kogham.  
\v 14 Ez…® ko, k…® ian agharim…®n iti. Ia bizitam…®n na damus…®, egh ia a g…®n…®ghn…®gh suam, ian arazir kam deragh vorogh…®ra mang…®t…®, ia a damu.  
\v 15 Ez…® k…® kamaghsua, ia deraghav…®ra kamagh…®n fogh. Bar guizbang…®ra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God uab…® na amadaz…®, k…® iza akar k…® ia m…®kemezir kabav gei. Eght…® ia na m…®sueght…® k…® aremegham, ia kamagh…®n fogh, ia gumazir arazir kuratam gamizir puvat…®zim puram a m…®sueght…® an aremeght…®, ia an os…®mt…®zim iniam. Eght…® os…®mt…®zir kam a nguibar ekiar kam…®n ik…®va, uaghan bar mogh…®ra nguibar kam…®n gumazamiziba sara ikiam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 16 Jeremaia m…®kemegha g…®vaz…®ma, gumazir dapaniba ko gumazamiziba bar mogh…®ra d…®kavigha ofa gamir gumaziba ko, akam inigha izir gumazibav g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazir kam, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God, an ziam…®n akam akuri. An os…®mt…®ziba puvat…®, kamagh…®n amiz…®, e a m…®sueght…® ana aremeghan kogham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 17 Ez…® Judan gumazir aruar maba d…®kavigha kamagh…®n uari akuvagha itir gumazamizibav gei,  
\v 18 \x - \xo 26:18 \xt Maika 3:12\x*‚ÄúFom…®ra, Hesekia Judan atrivim…®n itir dughiam…®n, Moreset…®n nguibam…®n itir God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Maika, akam Judabav k…®ra ghaze, ‚ÄòIkiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim ghaze, Jerusalem…®n biziba bar ikuvigham, egh m…®nezir pozim…®n otogham. Egh Saion nguazir k…®nim…®n m…®n ik…®t…®, gumazamiziba an dagher azenibar ingaram. Eght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim iti nagh…®n m…®ghs…®ar kam, ruarim a batogham.‚Äô  
\v 19 Maika kamagh…®n m…®gei, Hesekia ko Judaba bar mogh…®ra ti a m…®soghez…® an areme, a? Bar puvat…®. Hesekia Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n apengan ikia, egha uan gumazamiziba bagha an azangs…®si. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God n…®ghn…®zim giragha, bizir kurar a me damuasa m…®kemezibagh amizir puvat…®. Ez…® erara, arazir e Jeremaia damuasa m…®kemezim, an os…®mt…®zir ekiam inigh iz…® e dat…®gham!‚Äù 
\p  
\v 20 (Ez…® g…®n gumazir mam, an ziam Uria, a God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir mam, a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam…®n akam akuri. Uria a Semaian otarim, egha Kiriat Jearim…®n nguibam…®n gumazim. A Jeremaia m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, Jerusalem…®n nguibar ekiam ko Judan nguazim ikuvighasa a m…®keme.  
\v 21 Ez…® Atrivim Jehoiakim uan gumazir dapaniba ko, m…®dorozir gumaziba ko, me Urian akar kam baraki. Egha atrivim a m…®soghasa amima, Uria atiatigha ara Isip…®n ghu.  
\v 22 Egha Atrivim Jehoiakim, Akbor…®n otarim Elnatan amadaz…® a gumazir maba ko me Isip…®n ghue.  
\v 23 Me ghua Uria inigha atrivim bagha ize. Ez…® atrivim gumazibav kemez…® me m…®dorozir sababar a m…®soghez…® an aremez…®, me an kuam isa gumazir k…®nibar matmatiam m…®k…®ni.) 
\p  
\v 24 Ez…® gumaziba iza Jeremaia m…®sueght…® an aremeghasa amima, Safan…®n otarim Ahikam Jeremaian akuraz…®, me paza a gamizir puvat…®. 
\c 27  
\s1 Kantriba bar, Atrivim Nebukatnesar…®n apengan ikiam 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 27:1 \xt 2 Atriviba 24:18-20; 2 Eghaghaniba 36:11-13\x*Josaian otarim Sedekaia, Judan atrivim…®n itir dughiam…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n Jeremaia m…®keme,  
\v 2 ‚ÄúN…® ter ararir ruarir taba inigh, benir ruarir dar afamiba inigh, mati gumazim ingangarim damuasa bizir kamning isa bulmakaun tuem gar…®zi mogh…®n, da is…® uan tuem dat…®gh.  
\v 3 Egh n…® tuebagh ar…®zir ter araribar ingarigh, vaghvagh Idom…®n atrivim ko, Moap…®n atrivim ko, Amon…®n atrivim ko, Tair…®n atrivim ko, Saidon…®n atrivim, me bagh ada amadagh. N…® fo, atrivir kabar gumazir dapaniba, en atrivim Sedekaia ko m…®k…®masa Jerusalem…®n ize. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® tuebagh ar…®zir ter ararir kaba is…® me dan…®ngigh, eght…® me da inigh uan atriviba bagh mang…®.  
\v 4 N…® kamagh…®n men atrivibav m…®k…®ms…® gumazir kabav kemegh: K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, Israelian God, k…® kamagh…®n akam ian atrivibar iti:  
\v 5 K…® uab…® uan gavgavir ekiam…®n nguazir kam…®n ingari, egha k…® uaghan gumazamiziba ko, as…®zibar ingariz…® da nguazir kam…®n iti. K…® uab…® uan ifongiam…®n g…®n ghua, nguaziba ab…®gha gumazamizibagh an…®di.  
\v 6 K…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ian kantriba isa, Babilon…®n Atrivim Nebukatnesar gan…®di, a nan ingangarir gumazim. Egha uaghan k…® as…®zir atiaba isa bar a gan…®ngi, eght…® g…®n me an apengan ikiam.  
\v 7 Kantriba bar an apengan ik…®, egh uaghan an otarim ko, an igiav otarir g…®n otivamim sara men apengan ikiam. Me Babilon…®n apengan ik…® mang…®, k…® Babilon gas…®ghas…®ghamin dughiar k…® m…®sevezim…®n tugham. Dughiar kam…®n, kantrin av…®riba ko atrivir gavgaviba Babilon…®n d…®kab…®ragh, me damut…® me pura men ingangarir gumazir k…®nibar otivigham. 
\p  
\v 8 ‚ÄúEgh kantrin igharaz tam…®n gumazamiziba Atrivim Nebukatnesar ateght…®, a me gativagh men ganan aghuagham, mati gumazim ingangarim damuasa ter ararim isa bulmakaubar tuebagh ar…®ki, eght…® k…® kantrin kam paz…®va a damigham. Egh k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® apaniba amadaght…® me iz…® me m…®sogham. Eght…® me dagheba otevegh ar…®mariar kuraba iniam. Eght…® arazir kabar, k…® Atrivim Nebukatnesar ateght…®, a kantrin kam…®n gumazamiziba bar me ag…®vagham.  
\v 9 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia atriviba, ian akam inigha izir gumaziba ko, ian kukunir gumaziba ko, ian irebabar m…®ngaribar gun m…®geiba ko, ian imezibagh amir gumaziba ko, ian akavsiabagh amir gumaziba, ia kuaribar arigh me baraghan mark…®. Gumazir kaba ghaze, ia Babilon…®n atrivim…®n apengan ikian kogham.  
\v 10 Me ia gifari. Ia men akaba n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim…®n dar ik…®t…®, k…® ia batueght…® ia uan nguaziba ategh saghon mangegham. Egh ia bar ikuvigham.  
\v 11 Eght…® kantrin tam…®n gumazamiziba Babilon…®n atrivim ateght…®, a me gativagh men ganam, kar mati bulmakau pura uab…® isa gumazim…®n taghiz…® a ter ararim isa an tuem gat…®gha, egha ingarasa a getui. Eght…® k…® gumazamizir kaba ateght…®, me deraghv…®ra uan nguazim…®n ik…®va, uari bagh dagher azenibar ingaram. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® m…®kemegha g…®fa.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 12 Ez…® k…® Jeremaia, k…® akar kamra Judan Atrivim Sedekaia gan…®ngi. K…® kamagh…®n a m…®keme, ‚ÄúIa Judaba, ia uan tueba is…® Nebukatnesar…®n ter araribar apengan ada amangigh, aneteght…® a uan gumazamiziba ko, me ia gativagh ian ganam. Ia kamagh…®n damu, ia deraghv…®ra ikiam.  
\v 13 Ikiav…®ra Itir God m…®kemegha g…®fa: N…® uan gumazamiziba ko Babilon…®n apengan ikian aghuaght…®, apaniba ian taraziv sueght…® me ar…®m…®ghiregham, eght…® tarazi dagheba puvat…®gh ar…®m…®ghiregham, eght…® tarazi ar…®mariar kuram inigh ar…®m…®ghiregham. N…® uan gumazamiziba ko, onganigh akaba batoght…®, bizir kaba ia gas…®ghasigham.  
\v 14 Ia fo, akam inigha izir ifavarir gumaziba ghaze, ia Babilon…®n atrivim…®n apengan ikian kogham. Puvat…®, me pura ia gifari. Ia men akaba baraghan mark…®.  
\v 15 K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® guizbang…®ra m…®gei, k…® me amadazir puvat…®. Me nan ziam…®n akar ifavarim akuri. Ia men akaba n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim…®n dar ik…®t…®, k…® ia batueght…®, ia uan nguibam ategh bar ikuvigham. Ez…® akam inigha izir ifavarir gumazir akaba ia m…®k…®riba, me uaghan bar ikuvigham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 16 K…® ofa gamir gumaziba ko, gumazamiziba bar me bagha kamagh…®n akam akura ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® guizbang…®ra m…®gei, ia akam inigha izir gumazir ifavarir kabar akaba baraghan mark…®. Me ghaze, ‚ÄòMe k…®ran oveghang…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n aven ingangarim damuamin bizir Babilon…®n itiba, me bar ada inigh ua Jerusalem…®n izam.‚Äô God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir ifavarir kaba pura ia gifari.  
\v 17 Ia men akam baraghan mark…®. Ia Babilon…®n atrivim…®n apengan ik…®, deraghv…®ra ikiam. Puvat…®ght…®ma, nguibar kaba ikuvigham.  
\v 18 Gumazir kaba, me guizbang…®ra akam inigha izir gumaziba, egh me guizbang…®ra Ikiav…®ra Itir God, dama akam inigh iz…®s…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim…®n azaraght…®, an apaniba ateght…® me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n aven ingangarim damuamin biziba, ko atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n itir bizir aghuiba ko, Jerusalem…®n danganir igharaziba bar mogh…®ra, dar itir bizir naba inigh Babilon…®n mangan kogham. 
\p  
\v 19-21 ‚ÄúAtrivim Nebukatnesar Jerusalem…®n izegha, Judan Atrivim Jehoiakin ini, a Jehoiakim…®n otarim. Egha uaghan Juda ko Jerusalemian gumazir dapaniba ini. Egha men akua kalabus bagha Babilon…®n ghu. Egha a bizir aghuir maba ataghiz…® da Jerusalem…®n iti. A bras…®n d…®penir ak…®niba ko, teng…®n ekiar me bras…®n ingarizim ko, me bras…®n ingarizir bizir me teng…®n doziba is…®n afamiba, me bizir kaba inizir puvat…®. Egha uaghan ingarizir bizir aghuir nan D…®penim…®n itir maba ko, atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n itiba ko, bizir igharazir Jerusalem…®n itir maba inizir puvat…®. Ez…® k…® God, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, Israelian God, k…® kamagh…®n ia m…®gei,  
\v 22 ‚ÄòApaniba bizir kaba bar ada inigh Babilon…®n mangam. Eght…® bizir kaba Babilon…®n ik…® mang…® dughiar k…® inabazim…®n, k…® uam adagh in…®r…®gham. Eght…® dughiar kam…®n k…® ua me inight…®, me ua Jerusalem…®n ikiam.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù 
\c 28  
\s1 Hanania gumazamizibagh ifari 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 28:1 \xt 2 Atriviba 24:18-20; 2 Eghaghaniba 36:11-13\x*Azenir kam…®n, Sedekaia Judan atrivim igiamra an otogha atrivim…®n ikia zuima an namba 4…®n azenim. Egha azenir kam…®n namba 5…®n iak…®nim…®n, Gibeon…®n nguibam…®n gumazir mam, a God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Hanania, Asur…®n otarim, a iza Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n aven iza ofa gamir gumaziba ko gumazamiziba bar mogh…®ra, men damazim…®n akar mam Jeremaia gan…®di. A kamagh…®n m…®gei,  
\v 2 ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, a Israelian God, a kamagh…®n m…®keme, ‚ÄòBabilon…®n atrivim ia gativagha, mati gumazim ter ararim isa bulmakaun tuem gat…®gha a gatifa. Ez…® k…® ter ararir ian tuebagh at…®ziba, k…® dar p…®righa g…®fa, ez…® da ua ia gativagh ian ganan kogham.  
\v 3 Azenir pumuning ik…®v…®ra ik…®t…®, k…® ua Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n aven ingangarim damuamin bizir kaba bar ada inigham, kar bizir Nebukatnesar inigha Babilon…®n ghuziba, ez…® k…® ua da inigh Jerusalem…®n izam.  
\v 4 Egh k…® uaghan Judan Atrivim Jehoiakin, a Jehoiakim…®n otarim, a inigh egh Babilon…®n kalabus…®n itir marazi sara ua men aku Judan nguazim…®n izam. Guizbang…®ra, k…® Babilon…®n atrivim ian tuebagh ar…®ghizir ter arariba, k…® kaba ap…®righam. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® m…®kemegha g…®fa.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù 
\p  
\v 5 Ez…® God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Jeremaia dat…®r…®gh…®n d…®kavigha ofa gamir gumaziba ko, gumazamizir Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n borogh…®n tuivighav itibar damazim…®n, God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Hananian akam ikarvasi.  
\v 6 Jeremaia kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúBar guizbang…®ra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, n…® m…®kemez…® mogh…®n damuasa k…® ifonge. Ikiav…®ra Itir God n…®n akam inigha izir gumazim…®n akar kabar amut…®, da guizbang…®ram otivigham. Egh a uan D…®penim…®n biziba uam ada iniam. Egh Babilon…®n itir gumazamizir kaba, a ua me inigh Jerusalem…®n izam.  
\v 7 Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n gumazamiziba ko ia bar mogh…®ra oraght…®, k…® akar igharazim m…®k…®masa.  
\v 8 Bar fom…®ra iza dat…®r…®k…®n, God…®n akam inigha izir gumaziba en faragha otifi. Me kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, M…®dorozir ekiaba ko, m…®tiriar ekiaba ko, ar…®mariar kuraba, da kantrin av…®riba bativ, uaghan nguibar ekiabar otivam.  
\v 9 Eght…® akam inigha izir gumazibar tav kamagh…®n m…®k…®m suam, Gumazamiziba dabirabir aghuim ikiam, e foghan kogham, akar kam a guizbang…®ra, o puvat…®. Eght…® g…®n, akam guizbang…®ram otoght…®, e dat…®r…®gh…®n fogham, Bar guizbang…®ra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God akar kam isa, akam inigha izir gumazim gan…®ngigha anemadaz…® a ize.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 10 Jeremaia akar kam m…®kemegha g…®vaz…®, Hanania ter ararim Jeremaia uab…® uan tuem gat…®zir kam ini. Egha Hanania ter ararir kam bar anep…®raghar…®ki.  
\v 11 Egha a gumazamizibar damazim…®n tugha ghaze, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n m…®keme. Ez…® arazir kamra, k…® ter ararir Nebukatnesar tintinibar kantribar gumazamizibar tuebagh ar…®ziba ap…®rarigham. Azenir pumuning g…®vaghan koght…®ma, k…® kamagh…®n damigham.‚Äù Jeremaia akar kam baregha ghu. 
\p  
\v 12 God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Hanania, a God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Jeremaian f…®rim…®n itir ter ararir kam ap…®riaghat…®, ez…® dughiar maba g…®vaz…®ma, g…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n Jeremaia m…®g…®a ghaze,  
\v 13 ‚ÄúN…® mang…® akar kam…®n gun Hanania m…®kemegh. Me temem…®n ingarizir ter ararir kam n…® anep…®righa g…®fa. Ez…® n…® ain…®n igiatam…®n ingarigh, egh ter ararir n…® d…®p…®rizir kam…®n danganim dat…®gh.  
\v 14 K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, Israelian God, k…® kamagh…®n m…®keme: K…® uab…® ain…®n me ingarizim inigha Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba bar mogh…®ra men tuebagh ar…®ki, ez…® me pura Babilon…®n Atrivim Nebukatnesar…®n ingangarir gumazamizibar iti. Egha k…® as…®zir atiaba sara a gan…®ngiz…®, da uaghan an apengan iti.‚Äù  
\v 15 Jeremaia akar kam m…®kemegha g…®vagha, ua kamagh…®n Hanania m…®gei, ‚ÄúHanania, n…® oragh. Ikiav…®ra Itir God n…® amadaz…® n…® izezir puvat…®. Ez…® n…® gumazamizibagh ifaraz…®, me n…®n akar ifavariba n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim…®n dar iti.  
\v 16 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n m…®gei: N…®n akaba gumazamizibagh ekuiz…®, me nan akaba barazir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n, k…® nguazir kam…®n n…® ag…®vagham. N…® azenir kamnagh…®ram aremegham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 17 Ez…® azenir kamra an namba 7…®n iak…®nim ikiav…®ra itima, God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Hanania aremegha g…®fa. 
\c 29  
\s1 Jeremaia Judan Babilon…®n itiba bagha ak…®nafarim osiri 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 29:1-2 \xt 2 Atriviba 24:12-16; 2 Eghaghaniba 36:10\x*Jeremaia Jerusalem…®n ikiava, ak…®nafarim osirigha gumazamizir kaba bagha anemada: Gumazir dapanir ikiav…®ra itiba ko, ofa gamir gumaziba ko, God…®n akam inigha izir gumaziba ko, Judan gumazamizir Babilon…®n itiba. Gumazamizir kaba bar mogh…®ra, Atrivim Nebukatnesar faragha Jerusalem…®n me inigha, Babilon…®n kalabus dar…®ghasa men akua ghue.  
\v 2 Babilonia faragha iza Jerusalem…®n izegha, Atrivim Jehoiakin ko gumazamizir av…®rim inigha men akua Babilon…®n ghuegha g…®fa, ez…® g…®n Jeremaia ak…®nafarir kam osiri. Me atrivim ko an amebam, ko atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n ingarir gumazir ekiaba ko, Judaba ko Jerusalemian gumazir dapaniba ko, fofozir gumazir bizir aghuibar ingariba ko, ain…®n bizibar ingarir gumaziba, me bar mogh…®ra ghue.  
\v 3 Dughiar kam…®n Judabar Atrivim Sedekaia, a Safan…®n otarim Elasa ko, Hilkian otarim Gemaria, aning amadaz…® aning Babilonian Atrivim Nebukatnesar bagha zui. Ez…® Jeremaia Judan Babilon…®n itiba bagha ak…®nafarir kam isa aning gan…®ngiz…® aning a inigha zui. Ak…®nafarir kam kamagh…®n m…®keme,  
\v 4 ‚ÄúK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, Israelian God, k…® kamagh…®n m…®keme. Ia Judaba, ia oragh. K…® Jerusalem…®n ia batuegha ia amadaz…® ia Babilon…®n ghue.  
\v 5 Egh ia uari bagh d…®penibar ingar…®va, dagher azeniba opar…®va, azenir kabar dagheba ini.  
\v 6 Egh ia gumaziba amuibar ik…®va boriba bat…®. Eght…® ian otariba g…®n amuibar ik…®va uari, uari bagh boriba bat…®. Egh ia ik…®zir av…®rir ekiam ikiam. Ia uari uari damut…®, ian d…®bobonim mag…®ran mark…®.  
\v 7 K…® ian akua nguibar ekiar ia dat…®r…®gh…®n itir kam…®n ghu. Eght…® ia nguibar ekiar kam bagh pamten ingar deragh a damut…® an am…®ragh…®r…®gh deraghv…®ra ikiam. Eght…® ia a bagh Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko m…®k…®mt…®, a nguibar ekiar kam deraghv…®ram a damuam. Guizbang…®ra, nguibar kam am…®ragh…®r…®gh deraghv…®ra ik…®t…®, ia uaghan am…®ragh…®r…®gh deraghv…®ra ikiam.  
\v 8 K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, Israelian God, k…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, ia akam inigha izir ifavarir gumaziba ko kukunir gumaziba, ia me ateght…® me ia gifaran mark…®. Egha ia garir irebar aghuiba, gumazir dar m…®ngariba ab…®gha ia m…®geiba, ia me baraghan mark…®.  
