\v 8 \x - \xo 31:8 \xt God…®n Araziba 30:4; Aisaia 42:16; Esekiel 34:16; Maika 4:6\x*Bar guizbang…®ra, k…® not…®n amadaghan itir nguibar kam ko nguazir oteviba bar uan gumazamiziba inigh, 
