\q2 A navir am…®rizim inian aghua.\f + \fr 31:15 \ft Resel a Jekop…®n amuim, ez…® Israelia kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, a men inaghamir amebam. Me fo, Resel…®n kuam afazir mozim Raman nguibam…®n iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, gumazamizir kaba kamagh…®n m…®gei, Resel Raman nguibam…®n ikia uan ovavir borir oveaghuezibagh n…®ghn…®gha aziav…®ra ikia iti.\f* 
