\p  
\v 23 Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, Israelian God, a kamagh…®n m…®keme: 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄúK…® g…®n Judan nguazim damight…®, a deraghv…®ra ikiam. 
