\v 26 Ez…® k…® osegha d…®kavigha tintinibar gari, egha ghaze, k…® deragha akui.\f + \fr 31:26 \ft Akar kam…®n m…®ngarim deragha otozir puvat…®, egha uaghan kamagh…®n deragha otozir puvat…®, tina akar kam akuni. A ti Jeremaia, o ti gumazir igharazim? E foghan kogham.\f* 
