\v 27 ‚ÄúK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® ghaze, K…® dughiar mam am…®sefe, egh k…® gumazamiziba ko as…®zibar amight…®, da Judaba ko Israelian nguazim…®n otiv bar av…®rasemegham. Mati gumazim dagher azenim…®n ingarigha, dagher av…®ribagh amiz…® da otifi.  
\v 28 \x - \xo 31:28 \xt Jeremaia 1:10; 44:27; Daniel 9:14\x*K…® fom…®ra da asiasa dar gara, da abigha, egha dagh as…®ghas…®gha paza dagh ami. Egha dat…®r…®gh…®n, k…® dar gan…®va, dar ingar…®va da opart…® da deraghv…®ra ikiam. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® kamagh…®n m…®keme.  
\v 29 \x - \xo 31:29 \xt Esekiel 18:2\x*Eght…® dughiar kam…®n gumazamiziba ua kamagh…®n akar is…®n zuir kam…®n m…®k…®man kogham: Afeziaba ko amebaba wain…®n ov…®zir angamt…®ziba api. Ez…® wain…®n ov…®zir kaba is…®ngt…®ziba puvat…®gha boribar akabav sozi men atariba me giri.  
\v 30 \x - \xo 31:30 \xt God…®n Araziba 24:16; Aisaia 3:11; Esekiel 18:4; 18:20\x*Puvat…®. Dughiar kam…®n, gumazitam arazir kuratam damigham, a uab…® aremegham. Mati gumazim wain…®n ov…®zir anizir puvat…®ziba amez…®, da an akam m…®sozi an atariba a giri.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 31 \x - \xo 31:31 \xt Matyu 26:28; Mak 14:24; Luk 22:20; 1 Korin 11:25; 2 Korin 3:6\x*\x - \xo 31:31-34 \xt Hibru 8:8-12\x*Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God m…®g…®a ghua kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúDughiam a iz…®t…®, k…® Israelia ko Judaba, me ko Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir Igiam damuam.  
\v 32 K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® ghaze, Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir Igiam, k…® fom…®ra men ovavir afeziaba ko amizir Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim, an an m…®n mangan kogham. Fom…®ra itir dughiam, k…® uan dafarim…®n men suigha me inigha Isip…®n kantri ategha azenan ize, egha k…® men pam…®n m…®n itima me nan amuim…®n m…®n iti. Egha me Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir Ghurir kam ab…®ki.  
\v 33 \x - \xo 31:33 \xt Jeremaia 24:7; 32:40; Hibru 10:16\x*K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® kamagh…®n ia m…®gei, G…®n izamin dughiam otoght…®, k…® Israel ko Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim damight…®, a kamagh…®n mangam: K…® uan araziba men n…®ghn…®zibar ar…®gh, egh da is…®va men navir averiabar da osiram. Egh k…® men God…®n ik…®t…®ma me nan gumazamizibar ikiam.  
\v 34 \x - \xo 31:34 \xt Aisaia 11:9; Maika 7:18; Habakuk 2:14; 1 Tesalonika 4:9; Hibru 10:17\x*K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® guizbang…®ra m…®gei, dughiar kam…®n gumazamiziba vaghvagh uan namakaba ko uan adarazir sure damuan kogh suam, ‚ÄòIa Ikiav…®ra Itir God g…®fogh.‚Äô Puvat…®. Me bar mogh…®ra na g…®fogham, gumazamizir k…®niba ko ziaba itir gumazamiziba. Eght…® k…® men arazir kuraba g…®n amadagh…®va ua dagh n…®ghn…®ghan kogham.‚Äù 
\b  
\q1  
\v 35 Ikiav…®ra Itir God angazangarim an…®ngasa aruem…®n ingari, 
\q2 egha a iak…®nim ko m…®koveziba d…®magaribar angazangarim an…®ngasa 
\q3 dar ingarigha, dar danganibar da ar…®ki. 
\q1 Egha an ongarim fez…®, ongarir ekiaba d…®kava pamtem…®n d…®p…®raghira t…®ngazi. 
