\q3 K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® m…®kemegha g…®fa.‚Äù 
\b  
\p  
\v 38 Ikiav…®ra Itir God ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® dughiar mam am…®sefe, eght…® me ua Jerusalem…®n ingaram, nan nguibar ekiar kam. Jerusalem…®n d…®vazir not…®n amadaghan ghuzim…®n ababanim, an Hananel…®n Tauan ikegh mang…® d…®vazim…®n M…®kebam…®n Tiar Akam…®n tugham.  
\v 39 Eght…® an m…®taghniam mang…® Garep…®n m…®ghs…®ar dozim…®n, aruem ghuaghiri nagh…®n tugham, egh ua ragh mang…® Goan nguibam…®n tugham.  
\v 40 Egh nguibam…®n m…®taghniam…®n mang…® saut…®n amadaghan mang…® Kidron…®n danganir zarim…®n m…®riam gighuigham. Nguibam…®n m…®taghniam…®n aven nguazir kam, matmatiam ko danganir avereniba akurim iti. Eght…® aruem anadi nagh…®n nguazir zarim…®n ruaghatevibar itir danganir kaba, bar mogh…®ra uaghan nguibar kam…®n m…®taghniam…®n aven ikiam. Eght…® m…®taghniam aruem anadi nagh…®n mang…® Hoziaba Zuir Tiar Akam…®n tugham. Eght…® nguazir nguibar ekiar kam…®n aven itiba, kar bar nan nguibabara, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God. Eght…® apaniba iz…® nguibar kam gas…®ghas…®gh, uam an biziba akararighan kogham. Puvat…®gham. Nguibar kam a deraghv…®ra ik…® mamagh…®ra ikiam.‚Äù 
\c 32  
\s1 Jeremaia nguazir otevir mam givese 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 32:1 \xt 2 Atriviba 25:1-7\x*Ez…® namba 10…®n azenim…®n Sedekaia Judan atrivim…®n itir dughiam…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God akam isa Jeremaia gan…®ngi. Kar Atrivim Nebukatnesar Babilon…®n atrivim…®n iti a namba 18…®n azenim. 
\p  
\v 2 Ez…® dughiar kam…®n Babilon…®n atrivim…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba, Jerusalem…®n nguibam…®n d…®vazim azui, ez…® God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Jeremaia Judan atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n borogh…®n itir danganim…®n kalabus…®n aven iti. 
\p  
\v 3-5 Jeremaia faragha kamagh…®n God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim…®n m…®n akam akuri, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n m…®keme: Bar guizbang…®ra, k…® Babilon…®n atrivim ateght…® a nguibar ekiar kam iniam. Eght…® Sedekaia Babilonian ar…®mang…®ghan kogham, kar Kaldiaba. Puvat…®. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® Babilon…®n atrivim ateght…® an an suiragham, eght…® Sedekaia, Nebukatnesar…®n guam…®n tugh, gua uaghara uaning…®n gan, egh n…® an azangs…®ziba deraghv…®ram ada ikarvagham. Nebukatnesar Sedekaia inigh Babilon…®n mang…®ght…®, a nguibar ekiar kam…®n ik…® mang…® dughiar k…® uam a g…®n…®ghn…®ghamim…®n tugham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia Babilonia m…®soghs…® damuva, ia me d…®kab…®raghan kogham. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® m…®kemegha g…®fa.‚Äù Ez…® Atrivim Sedekaia akar kam baregha, kamagh…®n Jeremaian atara ghaze, ‚ÄúTinara n…® m…®kemez…®, n…® God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim…®n m…®n akar kam akuri?‚Äù Egha Sedekaia magh…®ra Jeremaia inigha kalabus gat…®. 
\p  
\v 6 Kar Jeremaian akamra. K…® Jeremaia, k…® kalabus…®n itir dughiam…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n na m…®keme: 
\p  
\v 7 ‚ÄúN…® oragh. N…®n aveghbuam, Hanamel, a n…®n afeziar dozim Salum…®n otarim, a n…® bagh izam. Egh a nguazir Anatot…®n itim gives…® n…®n azangam. N…® fo, n…® an aveghbuar bar an borogh…®ra itim, ez…® n…® nguazir kam givezamin faragh mangamin gumazim.‚Äù\f + \fr 32:7 \ft Ofa Gami 25:25…®n itir akam…®n gan.\f* 
\p  
\v 8 Ez…® Hanamel g…®n iza danganir m…®dorozir gumaziba iti nagh…®n kalabus…®n nan gani, Ikiav…®ra Itir God m…®kemez…® mok…®n. Ez…® Hanamel kamagh…®n na m…®keme, ‚ÄúN…® Anatot…®n nan nguazim givesegh, a Benjamin…®n anabam…®n nguazibar nguazir otevir mam. N…® fo, n…® nan aveghbuar rogh…®ra itim, n…® nguazir kam…®n faragh mang…® a givezamin gumazim. N…® ua bagh a givezeght…®, nguazir kam n…®n nguazimra ikiam.‚Äù Egha Hanamel uab…® m…®kemegha g…®vaz…®, k…® fo, kar Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akamra, eght…® k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God ifongez…® mogh…®ra damuam. 
\p  
\v 9-10 Egha k…® nguazir kam givese. K…® nguazim givezasa akam ak…®righa an osirigha, gumazir mabar damazibar, uan ababanim a gat…®. Egha k…® nguazir otevim…®n ivezim bagha 200 silvan dag…®aba mengegha, da isa Hanamel gan…®ngi. 
\p  
\v 11 Egha k…® nguazim givezasa akar d…®k…®r…®zir ak…®nafarir pumuning osiri, ez…® ak…®nafarir kamning bizir ga damuasa akam ak…®rizir akaba aning…®n iti. Ez…® ak…®nafarir mam k…® a dukua, ez…® igharazim k…® a dukuazir puvat…®.  
\v 12 Egha k…® ak…®nafarir otevir kamning inigha Baruk gan…®ngi, a Nerian otarim, egha Masean igiavotarim. Ez…® gumazir av…®riba nan garima, k…® nguazim givezasa bizir kabagh ami. Nan aveghbuam Hanamel ko, gumazir ak…®nafarim…®n men ziaba osiriziba, ko Judan gumazir danganir kam…®n aperaghav itiba, me bar mogh…®ra bizir kabar garima, k…® dagh ami.  
\v 13 Gumazir kaba garav…®ra itima, k…® kamagh…®n Baruk m…®gei,  
\v 14 ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, Israelian God, a kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòBaruk, n…® akar d…®k…®r…®zim…®n ak…®nafarir kamning inigh, dukuazir puvat…®zim ko dukuazim. Egh aning is…® nguazir m…®netam darugh, eght…® aning deraghv…®ra dughiar ruarim…®n ikiam.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù 
\p  
\v 15 Guizbang…®ra, arazir kam…®n m…®ngarim kamak…®n: Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar itim, Israelian God, a ghaze, G…®n gumazamiziba ua d…®peniba ko, nguaziba ko, wain…®n azeniba nguibar kam…®n a dagh ivezam. 
\s1 Jeremaia Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko m…®gei 
\p  
\v 16 Nerian otarim Baruk, akar d…®k…®r…®zir gavgavim itir ak…®nafarim inigha g…®vaz…®, k…® kamagh…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko m…®gei,  
\v 17 \x - \xo 32:17 \xt Jenesis 18:14; 2 Atriviba 19:15; Luk 1:37\x*‚ÄúO Ikiav…®ra Itir God, nan Ekiam, n…®n gavgavir ekiam…®n, n…® overiam ko nguazim…®n ingari. N…® bizitam damus…® iburaghan kogham.  
\v 18 N…® zurara tausen…®n gumazamizir av…®ribar apangkufi. Eght…® gumazitam arazir kuratam damigham, n…® ivezir kuram a dan…®ng…®va, uaghan an boriba ko an arazir kuraba ikarvagham. God n…® bar gavgafi, ez…® n…®n gavgavim bar en gavgavim gafira. Ez…® n…®n ziam kamak…®n: Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar itim.  
\v 19 \x - \xo 32:19 \xt Jop 34:21; Onger Akaba 33:13; Aisaia 28:29\x*N…® bizir aghuibar amuasa n…®ghn…®si. N…® gavgavim ikia, egha n…® ingangarir ekiabagh ami. N…® gumazamiziba amir biziba n…® bar adar gari. Egha n…® vaghvagha gumazamiziba amir araziba tuis…®gha, arazir me amibar ivezimra ikarvagh me gan…®di. 
\p  
\v 20 ‚ÄúN…® fom…®ra Isip…®n kantrin mirakel…®n ekiabagh ami. Egha n…® Israelia ko gumazamizir igharaziba bar, men tong…®n arazir kamagh garibagh amuav…®ra iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, gumazamiziba bar ziar ekiam n…® gan…®di.  
\v 21 N…®n gavgavir ekiam…®n, n…® mirakel bagh amua, egha bizir ekiar igharagha garir av…®ribagh ami, egh Isipia damut…® me bar atiatigham. Ez…® arazir kam…®n n…® uan gumazamiziba Israelia, ua Isip…®n me inigha azenan ize.  
\v 22 Egha n…® men ovaviba ko akam ak…®riz…® mogh…®n, n…® nguazir kam me gan…®ngi. Nguazir kam bar dera, ez…® dagheba an ikia bar deraghav…®ram aghui.  
\v 23 Me nguazir kam inigha an ikia, egha n…®n akaba ko Arazir N…® Me Gan…®ngiziba, me dar g…®n zuir puvat…®. Me n…®n akam batuegha n…®n Arazibar ikiavk…®ni. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® bizir kurar kabagh amiz…®, da me batifi. 
\p  
\v 24 ‚ÄúN…® gan. Dat…®r…®gh…®n Babilonia me m…®soghasava amua, Jerusalem ek…®arugha g…®fa. Me nguibar ekiam…®n d…®vazim borogh…®ra m…®tivigh m…®soghasa nguazim akuvagha d…®vazim borogh…®ra dar pozir ekiabav k…®ni, egha nguibam iniasa. Apanir kaba me m…®sozima, me dagheba puvat…®gha, ar…®mariar kuraba me batifi. Kamagh…®n Kaldiaba Jerusalem iniam. Bizir n…® m…®kemeziba, da otivigha g…®fa, ez…® n…® dat…®r…®gh…®n dar gari.  
\v 25 Bar guizbang…®ra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, nan Ekiam, n…® uab…® nguazir kam givezasa kamagh…®n na m…®keme, ‚ÄòN…® gumazamiziba inigh iz…®t…®, me uan ziaba ak…®nafarir d…®k…®r…®zir kam…®n ada osiram.‚Äô Ez…® Kaldiaba me nguibar ekiar kam iniasava ami.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 26 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n Jeremaia m…®gei,  
\v 27 \x - \xo 32:27 \xt D…®boboniba 16:22; Jeremaia 32:17\x*‚ÄúN…® gan! K…® uab…® k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® nguazir kam…®n gumazamiziba bar mogh…®ra men God. K…® bizitam damuan iburaghan kogham.  
\v 28 \x - \xo 32:28 \xt 2 Atriviba 25:1-11; 2 Eghaghaniba 36:17-21\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® Babilon…®n Atrivim Nebukatnesar ko Kaldiabar m…®dorozir gumaziba, k…® me ateght…® me nguibar ekiam iniam. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® kamagh…®n m…®keme.  
\v 29 Me iz…® nguibar ekiar kam daboroght…® a isigham. Eght…® avir kam d…®peniba bar dar isigham, d…®penir kaba gumazamiziba faragha dagh is…®n ghuavanaga, ofan m…®gharir mughuriar aghuim zuiba aser Bal bagha dagh amua, wain…®n ofaba aser igharaziba bagha da inge. Ez…® gumazamiziba amir arazir kaba na gamima k…® bar an…®ngaghe. 
\p  
\v 30 ‚ÄúIsraelia ko Judaba, me igiamra ikia iza dat…®r…®k…®n, me nan damazim…®n arazir kurabaram ami. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® guizbang…®ra m…®gei, Me arazir kurar kam…®n na gamima, k…® an…®ngaghe.  
\v 31 Me Jerusalem…®n ingarir dughiam…®n ikegha iza dat…®r…®k…®n, Jerusalemia na gamima k…® bar an…®ngaghe. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® nguibar ekiar kam uam an ganan aghuagha a gas…®ghas…®ghasa.  
\v 32 Israelia ko Judaba na damut…® k…® bar men an…®ngagh…®v…®ra ikiasa, me arazir kurar igharagha garibagh amuav…®ra iti. Gumazamizir k…®niba ko, atriviba ko, gumazir dapaniba ko, ofa gamir gumaziba ko, akam inigha izir gumaziba ko, Judan gumazamiziba ko, Jerusalem…®n itir gumazamiziba, me bar mogh…®ra arazir kurabagh ami.  
\v 33 \x - \xo 32:33 \xt Jeremaia 2:27; 7:13; 7:24\x*Me ak…®rim ragha na gasaragha, nan borogh…®n izir puvat…®. K…® dughiar av…®ribar men arazir kuraba bagha men sure gami, ez…® me nan akam baraghan aghua, egha dar g…®n zuir puvat…®.  
\v 34 \x - \xo 32:34 \xt 2 Atriviba 23:10; Jeremaia 7:30-31; 19:1-6\x*K…® uan ziam fasa inabazir d…®penir kam, me asebar marvir guaba aven da asez…®, da bar kuri. Egha arazir kam…®n me d…®penim gamima, a nan damazim…®n bar m…®ze.  
\v 35 \x - \xo 32:35 \xt Ofa Gami 18:21; 2 Atriviba 23:10; Jeremaia 7:31\x*Egha me Hinom…®n danganir zarim…®n asem Bal…®n ziam fasa danganim ak…®ri. Egha me uari uan boriba is…® asem Molek…®n ofa damuasa. K…® kamagh…®n damuasa me m…®kemezir puvat…®. Ez…® k…® uaghan arazir kam me dan…®ngasa n…®ghn…®zir pu. Bar puvat…®. Me arazir bar kurar kurizir kam damuan k…® ifongezir puvat…®. Me kamagh…®ram amua Judabar naviba fez…®, me arazir kurar kam…®n os…®mt…®zim iti.‚Äù 
\s1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God uan gumazamiziba deragh me damuam 
\p  
\v 36 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, a Israelian God, a kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazamiziba kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòApaniba e m…®sozima, e dagheba puvat…®z…®, ar…®mariar kuram e gas…®ghas…®si. Eght…® arazir kam…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Babilon…®n atrivim ateght…® a en nguibar ekiar kam iniam.‚Äô Ez…® k…® nguibar ekiar kam g…®n…®ghn…®gha, egha akar igharazim iti.  
\v 37 \x - \xo 32:37 \xt God…®n Araziba 30:3; Jeremaia 23:6; Esekiel 37:21\x*Bar guizbang…®ra, k…® an…®ngaghegha atara gumazamiziba batoghez…® me ghuezir kantriba, k…® kantrin kaba da ua me iniam. Egh men aku ua nguazir kam…®n izeght…®, me deraghv…®ra ikiam.  
\v 38 \x - \xo 32:38 \xt Jeremaia 30:22; 31:33\x*Egh me nan gumazamizibar ik…®t…®, k…® men God…®n ikiam.  
\v 39 K…® men navir averiabar aven navir vam…®ra me danight…®, me tuavir vam…®ran g…®n mangam. Egh me zurara nan atiating nan apengan ik…®t…®, k…® me ko men boriba sara deraghv…®ra me damuam.  
\v 40 \x - \xo 32:40 \xt Aisaia 55:3; Jeremaia 31:31-33\x*Egh k…® me ko Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir Igiam damuam. Eght…® Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir kam ik…® mamagh…®ra ikiam. K…® kamagh…®n akam ak…®righ suam, K…® deragh me damuamin arazim ateghan kogham. Egh k…® n…®ghn…®zir aghuim me dan…®ngam, eght…® me nan atiating nan apengan ikiam, egh me ua na ateghan kogham.  
\v 41 Egh k…® uaghan uan navir averiam…®n aven n…®ghn…®zir vam…®ra ikiam, kar k…® me gakuegh deraghv…®ra me damuam, egh me ateght…® me deraghv…®ra nguazir kam…®n ikiam. 
\p  
\v 42 ‚ÄúK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, K…® faragha bizir kurar mabagh amiz…® da otiva, me gas…®ghas…®ki. Ez…®, kamagh…®ra, k…® me bagh akam ak…®riz…® mogh…®ra, k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n bizir aghuir av…®rim damut…® da me bativt…®, me dabirabir aghuim ikiam,  
\v 43 Gumazamiziba ghaze, ‚ÄòIkiav…®ra Itir God nguazir kam isa Kaldiaba gan…®ngi. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, nguazir kam a ikuvigha g…®fa, ez…® gumazamiziba ko as…®ziba an itir puvat…®.‚Äô Ez…® k…®rara, k…® ghaze, g…®n Judaba ua uan nguazim dapiagh, egh me nguazim uam a givezegh anemangam. 
\p  
\v 44 ‚ÄúGumazamiziba nguazim gives…® akar d…®k…®r…®zibar ak…®nafariba da osiram. Egh men damazibar gumazamizir maba me akar d…®k…®r…®zim damuva, uan ababanibar arigh…®va ak…®nafarir kabar kumam. Da nguazir otevir kaba: Benjamin…®n anabam…®n nguaziba ko, Jerusalem…®n borogh…®n itir danganiba ko, Judan nguibar ekiar igharaziba ko, m…®ghs…®ar dozir aruem uaghiri nagh…®n itiba ko, m…®ghs…®aba itir danganir igharaziba ko, saut…®n amadaghan Negev…®n danganim sara. Eght…® dughiar kam…®n, k…® Judan kantri damight…®, a ua deraghv…®ra ikiam. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® m…®kemegha g…®fa.‚Äù 
\c 33  
\s1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God uan akar d…®k…®r…®zim damut…® a guizbang…®ra otogham 
\p  
\v 1 Jeremaia, atrivim…®n d…®vazim…®n aven itir m…®dorozir gumazibar danganim…®n kalabus…®n ikiav…®ra itima, Ikiav…®ra Itir God akar igharazim a gan…®ga ghaze,  
\v 2 ‚ÄúK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® bizitam damus…® a g…®n…®ghn…®gh…®va, k…® bizir kam damight…® an otogham. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, kar nan ziamra. Ez…® k…® kamagh…®n m…®gei:  
\v 3 \x - \xo 33:3 \xt Aisaia 48:6; 55:6-7; Jeremaia 29:12; 32:17\x*N…® nan d…®mt…®, k…® n…®n d…®mdiam ikaragham. Egh bizir ekiar modogha itir n…® fozir puvat…®ziba, k…® dar gun n…® m…®k…®mam. 
\p  
\v 4 ‚ÄúK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Israelian God, k…® Jerusalem…®n d…®peniba ko, Judan atrivim…®n d…®penibagh n…®ghn…®si. Apaniba iza Jerusalem av…®nigha, an d…®vazim borogh…®ra m…®tivigh m…®soghasa nguazim akuvagha, d…®vazim borogh…®ra dar pozir ekiabav k…®ni, egha nguibar ekiam iniasava ami. Ez…® Jerusalemia uari uan d…®peniba ap…®righa, d…®vazim gavgavim a dan…®ngasa dag…®aba ko, ter ararir oteviba inigha ghua d…®vazim…®n borogh…®ra da ar…®ki.  
\v 5 Egha me d…®kavigha Kaldiabav soghasava ami. Ez…® k…® Jerusalemian arazir kuraba bagha atarav…®ra ikia, bar puv…®ram me an…®ngaghegha, men akuraghan aghua. Kamagh…®n, apaniba me m…®soght…® me ar…®ghiram, eght…® men kuaba men nguibar ekiam…®n d…®penibagh iz…®vagham. 
\p  
\v 6 ‚ÄúEght…® k…® g…®n nguibar ekiar kam…®n akuragham, eght…® nguibam ko an gumazamiziba ua deragh otivigham. Eght…® k…® dughiar bar aghuim me danight…®, me deragh dapiaght…®, apaniba me m…®soghan kogham.  
\v 7 K…® dughiar kam…®n Judaba ko Israelia damight…® me ua deraghv…®ra ikiam. Egh me damight…® me uan gumazamizir fom…®ra ikeziba, ikez…® mogh…®n gavgavigh ikiam.  
\v 8 Me na batuegha, arazir kuram gami. Ez…® k…® men arazir kuraba g…®namadagham, egh men arazir kurabar os…®mt…®zim ag…®vagh me damight…®, me nan damazim…®n zuegham.  
\v 9 Eght…® nguazir kam…®n gumazamiziba bar bizir av…®rir aghuir k…® Jerusalemia gamizibar ganigham. Egh gumazamizir kaba bar akuegh navir am…®rizim nan ik…®va, ziar ekiam na dan…®ngam. Egh gumazamizir kaba Jerusalemian dabirabir aghuim…®n gan…®va, bizir aghuir k…® Jerusalem gan…®ngizibar gan…®va, atiating n…®gh…®va akong d…®gavir kuram damigham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 10 Egha g…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúDat…®r…®gh…®n gumazamiziba ghaze, ‚ÄòNguibar ekiar kam ikuvigha g…®fa, ez…® gumazamiziba ko as…®ziba an tir puvat…®. Judan nguibaba ko Jerusalem…®n tuaviba pura iti, ez…® gumazamiziba ko as…®ziba dagh aruir puvat…®.‚Äô Ez…® k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® ghaze: Gumazamiziba g…®n ua nguibar ekiar kam…®n ikiam.  
\v 11 \x - \xo 33:11 \xt 1 Eghaghaniba 16:34; 2 Eghaghaniba 5:13; 7:3; Esra 3:11; Onger Akaba 100:5; 106:1; 107:1; 118:1; 136:1\x*Egh me navir aghuim…®n ik…®va, bar akuegh poroghamiba uarir ikiamin isabar amuam. Egh gumazamiziba na m…®nabir ofaba inigh Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n izam. Egh me ofaba inigh iz…®, kamagh…®n ighiaba bangam: 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim 
\q2 bar derav…®ra e gami. 
\q3 A zurara bar en apangkufi. 
\q2 Kamagh…®n, e a m…®namam. 
\b  
\m ‚ÄúDughiar kam…®n, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® nguazir kam damight…® a fom…®ra ikez…® mogh…®n ua derav…®ram otogham. 
\p  
\v 12 ‚ÄúK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, k…® kamagh…®n m…®keme: Dat…®r…®gh…®n nguazir kam ko an itir nguibaba ikuvigha iti, ez…® gumazamiziba ko as…®ziba dar itir puvat…®. Ez…® g…®n, gumazamiziba ua nguibar kabar ikiam. Eght…® grazir aghuiba dar aghungam, eght…® sipsipbagh eghuvir gumaziba kantrin kam…®n nguazir oteviba bar, ua uan ingangarim damuam. Me graziba itir danganir aghuibar sipsipbar aku mang…®t…® me aghuvsam.  
\v 13 Egh me uan sipsipba mengam. Ingangarir kam, me uan m…®ghs…®ar dozir aruem uaghiri nagh…®n itiba ko, m…®ghs…®aba itir danganir igharaziba ko, Negev…®n saut…®n amadaghan iti nagh…®n ko, Benjamin…®n anabam…®n nguazim ko, Jerusalem…®n borogh…®n itir nguibaba ko, Judan nguibar ekiaba bar, me ingangarir kam damuam. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® kamagh…®n m…®keme.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 14 \x - \xo 33:14-16 \xt Jeremaia 23:5-6\x*Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God ghaze: Dughiar k…® m…®sevezim iz…®t…®, k…® faragha Israelia ko Judaba, me ko d…®k…®r…®zir akam, a guizbang…®ram otivam.  
\v 15 K…® dughiar kam…®n, Devit…®n adarazir aven gumazir bar aghuitam a damight…® an otogham, mati Temer Ghuzir Igiam temer aguam…®n otogham. Gumazir kam atrivim…®n ik…® arazir aghuim…®n g…®n mang…®, guiz…®n arazim…®n nguazir kam…®n itir gumazamizibagh ativagh men ganam.  
\v 16 Eght…® dughiar kam…®n Jerusalem…®n nguibar ekiam…®n itir darasi, me dabirabir aghuim ko navir am…®rizim…®n ikiam. Eght…® Judaba, God men akurvaght…®, me uam os…®mt…®ziba puvat…®gh derav…®ra ikiam. Eght…® me Jerusalem ziar kam a dar…®gh a d…®ponam, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God, A Guiz…®n Arazir Aghuim…®n M…®ngarim.‚Äù  
\v 17 \x - \xo 33:17 \xt 2 Samuel 7:12-16; 1 Atriviba 2:4; 1 Eghaghaniba 17:11-14\x*K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® kamagh…®n m…®gei: Devit…®n ik…®zim…®n, Israelia zurara atrivibar otiv ikiam.  
\v 18 \x - \xo 33:18 \xt D…®boboniba 3:5-10\x*Eght…® uaghan Livain anabam…®n ik…®ziba, me ofa gamir gumazibar ikiam, egh me zurara nan damazim…®n na bagh ofan igharagha garibar amuam, kar ofan bar isia m…®gh…®riziba ko, wit…®n ofaba ko, ofan igharaziba. 
\p  
\v 19 Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n Jeremaia m…®keme,  
\v 20 ‚ÄúK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® guizbang…®ra m…®gei: K…® aruem ko, d…®magarim ko, akam ak…®righa g…®fa, eght…® aning zurara dughiar k…® aning bagha inabazim…®n otivam. Ez…® gumazitam nan akar d…®k…®r…®zir gavgavir kam giraghan kogham.  
\v 21 Ez…® kamagh…®ra, gumazitam nan Akar Gavgavir k…® Devit ko d…®k…®r…®zir kam ab…®ghan kogham, Devit nan ingangarir gumazim. Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir kam kamagh…®n ghaze, Devit…®n ik…®zim…®n, atriviba zurara otiv…®ra ikiam. Ez…® uaghan, k…® Livain anabam…®n ofa gamir gumaziba ko, Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim gamua ghaze, Livain ofa gamir gumaziba, me zurara nan ingangarir gumazibar ikiam. Eght…® gumazitam Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir kam abighan kogham.  
\v 22 Gumaziba m…®koveziba ko, ongarim…®n gigiba meng…®va avegham. Eght…® kamagh…®ra k…® uan ingangarir gumazim Devit ko, nan ingangarir gumaziba, Livaiba, me damight…®, men ovavir boriba bar av…®rasemeght…®, gumazamiziba me mengan iburagham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 23 Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n Jeremaian m…®gei,  
\v 24 ‚ÄúGumazamiziba ghaze: ‚ÄòFom…®ra Ikiav…®ra Itir God Israelia ko Judaba me am…®sevez…®, me a baghav…®ra ik…®zir pumuning…®n iti. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n an ak…®rim ragha me gasaragha g…®fa.‚Äô Gumazamizir kaba akar kamagh garibav g…®a, egha me nan gumazamizibagh ifongezir puvat…®gha, ghaze, men ganganim…®n, nan gumazamizibar kantri ovegha g…®fa.  
\v 25 Ez…® k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® guizbang…®ra m…®gei: K…® aruem ko, d…®magarim ko Akar Gavgavim ak…®righa, overiam ko nguazim bagha bizir k…® damuasa m…®kemeziba bar da ar…®ki,  
\v 26 ez…® bar guizbang…®ra, k…® Jekop…®n ovavir boriba ko nan ingangarir gumazim Devit…®n ik…®zim, ak…®rim ragh me gasaraghan kogham. Puvat…®. K…® Abraham ko, Aisak ko, Jekop…®n ovavir boriba gativs…®, Devit…®n ovavir boribar tong…®n atrivibar amut…® me otivam. Guizbang…®ra, k…® kuarkuvim men ik…® me damut…®, me ua deraghv…®ra ikiam.‚Äù 
\c 34  
\s1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, m…®g…®r…®g…®am Atrivim Sedekaian iti 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 34:1 \xt 2 Atriviba 25:1-11; 2 Eghaghaniba 36:17-21\x*Babilon…®n Atrivim Nebukatnesar uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko, iza Jerusalemia ko, Judan nguibar ekiaba ko m…®sozir dughiam…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God akam isa Jeremaia gan…®ngi. Nebukatnesar…®n apengan itir kantriba bar dar ik…®zibar m…®dorozir gumaziba, me bar Nebukatnesar…®n g…®n ghua Jerusalem m…®sosi. Dughiar kam, Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n Jeremaia m…®gei,  
\v 2 ‚ÄúK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® Israelian God, k…® ghaze, n…® Judan Atrivim Sedekaia bagh mang…®gh kamagh…®n a m…®kemegh: K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® nguibar ekiar kam is…® Babilon…®n atrivim dan…®ngam, eght…® an a daboroght…® a isigham.  
\v 3 Sedekaia, n…® an ar…®mangan mark…®. Puvat…®. N…® ik…®t…® me n…®n suiragh n…® inigh a bagh mangam. N…® an guam…®n tugh, egh gua uaghara uaning…®n gan, egh n…® an azangs…®ziba deraghv…®ram ada ikarvagh. Eght…® me n…®n aku Babilon…®n mangam.  
\v 4 O Judan Atrivim Sedekaia, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® akar igharazir kam n…®n iti. N…® deraghv…®ra nan akar kam barakigh: Me n…® m…®sueght…® n…® aremeghan kogham.  
\v 5 Puvat…®. N…® deraghv…®ra ik…® mang…®, egh aremegham. Eght…® n…® aremeghamin dughiam…®n, me pauran mughuriar aghuim itim tuegh, ziar ekiam n…® dan…®ngam, mati me n…®n Judan atrivibar itir ovaviba bagha amiz…® mok…®n. Egh me azi m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòO noki, en gumazir aruam.‚Äô K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® akam ak…®righa egha m…®kemez…® mogh…®n bizir kam otivam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 6 Atrivim Sedekaia Jerusalem…®n itima, ez…® God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Jeremaia ghua akar kaba bar a m…®keme.  
\v 7 Ez…® dughiar kam…®n, Babilon…®n atrivim…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba Jerusalemia ko, Lakis…®n nguibam ko, Asekan nguibam ko m…®sosi. Apaniba faragha Judan nguibar d…®vazir gavgaviba itir maba bar ada ini, ez…® nguibar 3plan kabara ikiav…®ra iti. 
\s1 Judaba ingangarir gumazir k…®niba paza me gami 
\p  
\v 8 Atrivim Sedekaia ko Jerusalem…®n gumazamiziba ko, akar gavgavim ak…®righa ghaze, Men ingangarir gumazamizir k…®niba, me me damight…® me f…®righ…®regham. Ez…® dughiar kam…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God akam isa Jeremaia gan…®ngi.  
\v 9 Me kamagh…®n akam m…®soke. Israelian gumazitam o amizitam, namakar tam…®n ingangarir gumazir k…®nim…®n ik…®t…®, a gativazir gumazim aneteght…® a f…®righ…®r…®gh ik…®. Kamagh…®ra, Judaba namakabar suiraght…® me men ingangarir gumazamizir k…®nibar ikian kogham.  
\v 10 Gumazir dapanir av…®riba ko gumazamizir av…®rir maba akar d…®k…®r…®zir gavgavir kam gifonge, egha me bar akam m…®suegha ghaze, me pura men ingarir gumazamizir k…®nibar suighan kogham. Me akam m…®suegha g…®fa, egha me ingangarir gumaziba ko, ingangarir amiziba ataghiz…® me f…®riagh…®re.  
\v 11 Egha me g…®n n…®ghn…®zim giragha, egha gumazir kaba ko amizir kaba inigha, me gamiz…®ma me ua ingangarir gumazamizir k…®nibar otifi. 
\p  
\v 12 Kamagh…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God akam isa Jeremaia gan…®ngigha ghaze,  
\v 13 ‚ÄúK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Israelian God, k…® ian ovaviba ko Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim gami. Me Isip…®n ingangarir gumazamizir k…®nibar itima, k…® kalabuziar danganim…®n me inigha azenan ize. Egha g…®n k…® me ko Akar Gavgavim ak…®ri. Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir kam kamagh…®n m…®gei:  
\v 14 \x - \xo 34:14 \xt Ua Me Ini 21:2; God…®n Araziba 15:12\x*‚ÄòIa zurara azenir namba 7…®n vaghavagh, uan ingangarir gumazamizir k…®nibar amut…® me f…®righ…®regham. Ian namakaba me ian uari amang…®t…®, ia me inight…® me ian ingangarir gumazamizir k…®nibar otivigh, ian ingangaribar amuam. Egh me ingar mang…®v…®ra ik…® 6plan azeniba g…®vagham. Eght…® azenir an g…®rara irimra, ia me ateght…® me pura mang…®.‚Äô Ian ovaviba akar kam g…®fo, egha me nan akam barazir puvat…®gha, an g…®n zuir puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 15 ‚ÄúIa faragha akar kam bar an g…®n zuir puvat…®. Egha bar bogh…®mra, ia navibagh iragha guiz…®n araziba nan damazim…®n dagh ami. Ia vaghvagh namakar ingangarir gumazamizir k…®nibar m…®k…®mt…®, me ian ingangarir gumaziba ko ingangarir amizibar ikian mark…®. Egh uaghan ia nan D…®penim…®n tuivigh, Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim nan damazim…®n a damuva m…®k…®m suam, Ia uan namakaba ateght…®, me pura mang…®.  
\v 16 Egha dat…®r…®gh…®n ia ua n…®ghn…®zibagh iragh, gumazamizir ia me ataghiz…® me uan ifongiam…®n pura ghueziba, ia ua me inigha, me gamiz…® me ua ian ingangarir gumazamizir k…®nibar otifi. Ez…® arazir kam…®n ia nan ziar ekiam d…®kab…®ra. 
\p  
\v 17 ‚ÄúEz…® bizir kam bagha, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® kamagh…®n m…®keme: Ia nan akam…®n g…®n zuir puvat…®, egha ia aveghbuar kaba ko namakaba, ia ategh mangasa, ia me m…®kemezir puvat…®. Egh ia oragh. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® kamagh…®n m…®keme: k…® ia ateght…® ia uari pura mangam. Guizbang…®ra, ia pura mang…® aremegham. Apaniba ian taraziv sueght…® ia ar…®m…®ghiregham, eght…® tarazi ar…®mariar kuraba iniva ar…®ghiram, eght…® tarazi dagheba puvat…®gh ar…®ghiram. Ez…® Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba bizir k…® ia gamizibar akam baregh, atiating d…®gavir kuram damigham.  
\v 18 Ian ovaviba fom…®ra nan damazim…®n Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir kam gamua, akam ak…®ramin arazim…®n g…®n ghua, bulmakaun nguzim m…®suegha, akuar pumuning…®n aneb…®ki. Egha ia bulmakaun akuar kamning…®n t…®zimning…®n arui. Ez…® g…®n ian gumazamizir av…®riba Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir kam ab…®ki. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® ia damight…® ia bulmakaun nguzir ian ovaviba m…®soghezir kam…®n m…®raram otogham.  
\v 19 Gumazamizir bulmakaun akuamning…®n t…®zim…®n aruiziba, me akar d…®k…®r…®zim abight…®, k…® kamagh…®n bar mogh…®ra me damuam. Kar Judaba ko, Jerusalem…®n gumazir dapaniba ko, atrivim…®n gumazir dapanir ekiaba ko, ofa gamir gumaziba ko, gumazamizir igharaziba bar.  
\v 20 K…® me is…® apanibar dafarim dat…®ght…®, apaniba me m…®sueght…® me ar…®m…®ghiregham, eght…® kuaraziba ko as…®ziba iz…® men kuabar amam.  
\v 21 Egh uaghan, k…® Atrivim Sedekaia uan gumazir aruaba ko me is…® apanir me m…®soght…® me ar…®m…®ghir…®s…® damuamin kabar dafarim dat…®gham. Kar Babilon…®n atrivim…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba. Guizbang…®ra, Babilonia ia ategha ghue.\f + \fr 34:21 \ft Jeremaian ak…®nafarim…®n itir akaba, biziba otivizir dughiam…®n g…®n derav…®ra zuir puvat…®. Jeremaia saptan kam…®n aven akunizir akaba, da bizir otivizibar eghaghanim, Jeremaia 37:5 ko 37:11…®n iti.\f* 
\v 22 Eght…® k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® m…®kemeght…®, me ua iz…® Jerusalem ko m…®sogh egh nguibar ekiar kam iniam. Egh men nguibar ekiaba, avim…®n dar apongegham. Eght…® k…® Judan nguibaba bar dagh as…®ghasigham, eght…® nguibar k…®niba ik…®t…®, gumazamiziba dar puvat…®gham.‚Äù 
\c 35  
\s1 Rekapia derav…®ra uan ovavibar akabar g…®n zui 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 35:1 \xt 2 Atriviba 23:36--24:6; 2 Eghaghaniba 36:5-7\x*Josaian otarim Jehoiakim, Judan atrivim…®n itir dughiam…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n Jeremaia m…®gei,  
\v 2 ‚ÄúN…® mang…® Rekap…®n adarazir gumazamizibar gan…®va, egh me ko m…®k…®m…®va men aku nan Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n aven itir danganir mam bagh iz…®. Egh n…® wain is…® me danight…® me aneremam.‚Äù  
\v 3 Ikiav…®ra Itir God m…®kemegha g…®vaz…®, k…® ghua Rekapian mav ini, an ziam Jasania. A Jeremaian otarim, egha Habasinian igiavotarim. K…® an aveghbuaba ko, an otariba ko, Rekap…®n adarazir gumazir igharaziba bar me inigha,  
\v 4 men akua Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n ghu. Egha k…® men akua Ikdalian otarim Hanan…®n adarazir danganim…®n ghu. Hanan a God…®n akam…®n g…®n zuir gumazir mam. Danganir kam, a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n gumazir ekiabar danganim…®n borogh…®n iti. Egha a Masean danganim gis…®n iti, a Salum…®n otarim. Masea, a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n gumazir ekiar faragha itim, egha a D…®penibar Tiar Akabar gari gumazim. 
\p  
\v 5 Ez…® k…® wain…®n m…®ner iz…®v…®r…®zim ko kav…®n d…®paba apiba inigha Rekap…®n adarazi gan…®ga, kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúAria, ia dam…®.‚Äù  
\v 6 Ez…® me kamagh…®n akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúNoki, e wain…®n d…®pam aman kogham. En ovavim Jonadap, Rekap…®n otarim, a ikiangs…®zir mam e gan…®ga, e ko en ovavir boriba wain…®n d…®pabar aman en anogoroke. Bizir kam bang…®n, e wain…®n d…®paba apir puvat…®.  
\v 7 Jonadap uaghan e m…®g…®a ghaze: Ia d…®penibar ingaran mark…®, egh azeniba oparan mark…®, egh wain…®n azenibar ingaran kogh, uaghan wain…®n azenitam ikian mark…®. Puvat…®. E zurara averpenibar ikiam. Egh akar kabar g…®n mangam, egh e zuam…®ram oveghan kogham. E dughiar ruarim…®n nguazir kam…®n ikiam.  
\v 8 En ovavim, Rekap…®n otarim Jonadap, e gan…®ngizir akar kaba e zurara bar dar g…®n zui. E uan amuiba ko boriba sara wain…®n d…®paba apir puvat…®.  
\v 9 E d…®penibar ingarir puvat…®gha, egha e wain…®n azeniba ko azenir igharaziba puvat…®.  
\v 10 E purirpenibar iti, ez…® arazir kam…®n, e Jonadap e gan…®ngizir akaba bar adar g…®n zui.  
\v 11 Ez…® dughiar Babilon…®n Atrivim Nebukatnesar iza nguibar ekiar kam ko m…®sozima, e Kaldia ko Sirian m…®dorozir gumazibar atiatingi, egha e Jerusalem…®n ikiasa akam m…®soke. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, e dat…®r…®gh…®n Jerusalem…®n ikiav…®ra iti.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 12 Me m…®kemegha g…®vaz…®ma, ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n Jeremaia m…®gei,  
\v 13 ‚ÄúK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, Israelian God, k…® kamagh…®n m…®keme: N…® mang…® Judaba ko Jerusalemia kamagh…®n me m…®k…®m suam, K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ia nan akam…®n g…®n mangamin arazim…®n, k…® ian sure damuasa.  
\v 14 Fom…®ra Rekap…®n otarim Jonadap, uan adaraziv g…®a ghaze, me wain…®n d…®pabar aman kogham. Ez…® fom…®ra ikegha iza dat…®r…®gh…®n tugha zui, Rekapia uan ovavim…®n akaba derav…®ram dar g…®n ghua, egha wain…®n d…®paba apir puvat…®. Ez…® k…® dughiar av…®ribar akaba ia gan…®di, ez…® ia nan akam barazir puvat…®.  
\v 15 Nan akam inigha izir gumaziba, k…® dughiar av…®ribar me amadima, me ia bagha izi, me nan ingangarir gumaziba. Me kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze: Ia vaghvagh uan n…®ghn…®zibagh ira uan arazir kuraba ategh, uan araziba ak…®righ. Egh ia asebar g…®n mang…®va, dar ziaba fan mark…®. Ia nan akar kam…®n g…®n mang…®va, nguazir k…® ian ovaviba ko ia gan…®ngizir kam, deraghv…®ram an ikiam. Nan akam inigha izir gumaziba akar kam…®n gun ia m…®keme, ez…® ia nan akam barazir puvat…®gha, an g…®n zuir puvat…®.  
\v 16 Rekap…®n otarim, Jonadap…®n adarasi, derav…®ra uan ovavim…®n akabar g…®n zui. Ez…® ia gumazamiziba nan akam…®n g…®n zuir puvat…®.  
\v 17 Kamagh…®n, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, Israelian God, k…® kamagh…®n m…®keme: Ia Judaba ko Jerusalemia, ia oragh! K…® fom…®ra akam ia m…®k…®ni, ez…® ia kuariba arigha akar kam barazir puvat…®. K…® ian diaz…®, ia nan d…®mdiam ikarazir puvat…®. Bizir kam bang…®n, k…® damuasa m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, k…® bizir kuraba bar adar amut…® da ia bativam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 18 Egha g…®n, Jeremaia kamagh…®n Rekapia m…®gei, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, a Israelian God, a ghaze: Ia uan ovavim Jonadap…®n akaba baragha, egh an akaba bar dar g…®n ghua, a damuasa ia m…®kemezir biziba ia bar adagh ami.  
\v 19 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar itim, Israelian God, k…® ian m…®gei, ia Rekap…®n otarim Jonadap…®n adarasi, ian ovavir boriba zurara nan ingangarim damuamin gumazamizibar ikiam.‚Äù 
\c 36  
\s1 Jeremaia, God…®n akam gumazamiziba bagh a d…®ponasa Baruk m…®gei 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 36:1 \xt 2 Atriviba 24:1; 2 Eghaghaniba 36:5-7; Daniel 1:1-2\x*Ez…® azenir namba 4, Josaian otarim Jehoiakim, Judan atrivim…®n itir dughiam…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God akam isa Jeremaia gan…®ga ghaze,  
\v 2 ‚ÄúN…® ak…®nafarir tam inigh bizir Israel ko, Juda ko, kantrin igharazibar otivamin akaba bar ada osirigh. N…® akar kaba bar ada osirigh, k…® Atrivim Josaian dughiam…®n faragha n…® gan…®ngizir akabar ikegh iz…®, dat…®r…®gh…®n otoziba sara, n…® bar ada osirigh.  
\v 3 Eght…® Judaba bizir kurar k…® me damuamibar akar kaba baregh, uan n…®ghn…®zibagh ira uan arazir kuraba ateght…®, k…® men arazir kuraba ko os…®mt…®ziba g…®n amadagham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 4 Ez…® Jeremaia d…®kavigha Nerian otarim, Baruk…®n diaz…®, a ize. Ez…® Jeremaia akar Ikiav…®ra Itir God a gan…®ngiziba bar dar gun a m…®keme, ez…® Baruk akar kaba ak…®nafarir mam…®n bar ada osiri.  
\v 5 Ez…® g…®n Jeremaia kamagh…®n Baruk m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® uab…® k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n aven mang…®ghan kogham.\f + \fr 36:5 \ft E fozir puvat…®, manmagh…®n amiz…® Jeremaia Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n mangan aghua. A ti kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si: an aven mang…®t…® me paz…® a damigham o, an aven mangan atiatingiz o, a ti ar…®mariar tam iti o, gumazir aruaba ti aven mangan an anogoroke.\f* 
\v 6 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® osirasa n…® m…®kemezir ak…®nafarir kam, n…® a iniasa k…® ifonge. N…® dagheba atagh…®razir dughiar ekiatam bagh Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n aven mang…®va, God…®n akar kaba Judan nguibabar gumazamiziba bagh adar pon. Dughiar kam…®n me bar mogh…®ra uari akuvagh, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n aven ik…®va, uaghan akar kam baragham.  
\v 7 Ikiav…®ra Itir God atara bar gumazamizir kaba bar men an…®ngaghe, egha bizir kuratam…®n me damuasa m…®gei. Eght…® gumazamiziba ti uan arazir kurar me amiba ategh, Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko m…®k…®mt…®, a men d…®mdiam baragham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 8-9 Ez…® namba 5…®n azenim…®n, an namba 9…®n iak…®nim…®n, Jehoiakim Judan atrivim…®n itir dughiam…®n, gumazamiziba uarir akurvaghasa, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n azangs…®ghasa, dagheba atagh…®raghasa dughiar mam am…®sefe. Ez…® Jerusalem…®n itir gumazamiziba ko Judan nguibabar gumazamiziba bar iza Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n uari akufa. Ez…® dughiar kam…®n Baruk bizir Jeremaia a m…®kemeziba bar adagh ami. A Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akaba itir ak…®nafarim inigha, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n ghu.  
\v 10 Egha a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n d…®vazim…®n aven tughav ikia, Jeremaian akar ak…®nafarir kam…®n itiba bar ada d…®pone, ez…® gumazamiziba bar da baraki. Baruk danganir mam…®n tiar akam…®n tughav ikia ak…®nafarir kam d…®bori. Danganir kam, a Safan…®n otarim Gemarian danganim. A fom…®ra Safan…®n atrivim…®n ak…®nafariba osirir gumazim…®n iti. Danganir kam, a danganir me uari akuvim…®n p…®n ikia, egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n tiar akam…®n borogh…®ra iti. Me ziam, Tiarakar Igiam a gar…®si. 
\s1 Baruk atrivim…®n gumazir dapaniba bagha ak…®nafarim d…®bori 
\p  
\v 11 Mikaia, a Gemarian otarim, egha Safan…®n igiavotarim. A Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n ikia, Baruk barazima, a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Akar Ak…®nafarir kam…®n itiba d…®bori.  
\v 12 Egha an atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n iraghu. Egha atrivim…®n ak…®nafariba osirir ingangarir gumazim…®n danganim…®n aven ghua garima, gumazir dapanir av…®riba apiaghav iti. Gumazir dapanir kabar ziabar kara: Ak…®nafariba osirir ingangarir gumazim Elisama ko, Semaian otarim Delaia, ko Akbor…®n otarim Elnatan, ko Safan…®n otarim Gemaria, ko Hananian otarim Sedekaia. Ez…® gumazir ekiar maba uaghan iti.  
\v 13 Baruk gumazamiziba bagha d…®ponezir akar akaba, Mikaia faragha da baregha, bar dar gun gumazir dapanir kaba me geghani. 
\p  
\v 14 Gumazir dapanir kaba, me Mikaian akam baregha, Baruk iniasa gumazir mam amada. Gumazir kam…®n ziam, Jehudi, a Netanian otarim, egha Selemian igiavotarim, ez…® Selemia, a Kusin otarim. Ez…® Jehudi ghua kamagh…®n Baruk m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® ak…®nafarir gumazamiziba bagha d…®ponezir kam inigh, egh n…® izi.‚Äù Ez…® Baruk ak…®nafarir kam inigha, gumazir dapaniba bagha ize.  
\v 15 An otogha g…®vaz…®ma, gumazir dapaniba a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® daperagh egh ak…®nafarir kam d…®pont…® e a baragham.‚Äù Ez…® Baruk ak…®nafarir kam me bagha a d…®bori.  
\v 16 Me ak…®nafarir kam…®n akaba bar ada baragha, atiatigha d…®gavir kuram gami, egha uarira uarir gari. Egha me kamagh…®n Baruk m…®gei, ‚ÄúBar guizbang…®ra, e mang…® bizir kabar gun atrivim m…®kemeka.‚Äù  
\v 17 Egha me kamagh…®n Baruk…®n azara, ‚ÄúN…® e m…®kemegh. N…® manmaghsua akar kaba osiri? Jeremaia ti m…®geima n…® da osiri, a?‚Äù  
\v 18 Ez…® Baruk me ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúBar guizbang…®ra. Jeremaia akar kaba bar na gan…®ngi, ez…® k…® f…®nf…®nim inigha, an akaba ak…®nafarir kam…®n bar ada osiri.‚Äù  
\v 19 Ez…® gumazir dapaniba kamagh…®n Baruk m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® mang…® Jeremaia inigh gua mang…® modogh. N…® gumazitam ateght…® a gua modir danganim g…®foghan mark…®.‚Äù 
\s1 Gumazir mam atrivim bagha ak…®nafarim d…®bori 
\p  
\v 20 Ez…® gumazir dapaniba Baruk…®n dafarim…®n da ak…®nafarim inigha, a isa Elisaman danganim…®n anet…®, an atrivim…®n ak…®nafariba osirir gumazim. Egha me d…®kavigha atrivim…®n ganasa uari akuvir danganim…®n ghugha, bizir otivizir kabar gun a m…®gei.  
\v 21 Atrivim akar kaba baregha, ak…®nafarir kam iniasa Jehudi amada. Ez…® Jehudi ghua Elisaman danganim…®n ak…®nafarim inigha atrivim bagha ize. Egha an atriviba ko gumazir ekiar atrivim…®n borogh…®ra tuivigha itiba, me bagha a d…®bori.  
\v 22 Kar bizir namba 9…®n iak…®nim…®n otiviziba, kar orangt…®zim…®n dughiam. Dughiar kam, atrivim uan d…®penir a zurara orangt…®zim…®n dughiam…®n itim…®n ikiava, avim…®n borogh…®ra aperaghav ikia, uan m…®karzim fefem a gan…®di.  
\v 23 Ez…® Jehudi ak…®nafarim d…®bora iti, egha osizirir mabar ponegha g…®vaz…®ma, atrivim afuar dozir mam inigha, Jehudi d…®ponezir akar otevir ak…®nafarim…®n itir kam atugha a isa avim m…®k…®ni. Jehudi ak…®nafarim d…®bora ghuav…®ra itima, atrivim kamagh…®ra amuav…®ra ghua, ak…®nafarir otevir maba bar da tue.  
\v 24 Atrivim uan gumazir dapaniba ko me bar akar kaba baraki. Egha me tong atiatia d…®gavir kuram gamizir puvat…®gha, uan arazir kurabagh n…®ghn…®gha, egha osemegha uan korotiaba ab…®ghizir puvat…®.  
\v 25 Ez…® Elnatan ko, Delaia ko, Gemaria, me atrivim ak…®nafarim tuan me bar aghuagha gavgavigha a gakaghori. Ez…® atrivim men akam baraghan aghua.  
\v 26 Egha atrivim uan otarim Jeramel ko, Asriel…®n otarim Seraia, ko Apdel…®n otarim Selemia, akar gavgavimra me gan…®ga ghaze, Ia mang…® God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Jeremaia ko ak…®nafariba osirir gumazim Baruk, aning…®n suiragh. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God aning modoz…®, me aning…®n apizir puvat…®. 
\s1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God ak…®nafarir igharazim osirasa Jeremaia m…®gei 
\p  
\v 27 Atrivim, Baruk osirizir ak…®nafarir kam tuaz…® a isiz…®, an g…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n Jeremaia m…®gei,  
\v 28 ‚ÄúN…® ak…®nafarir igharazim inigh, Atrivim Jehoiakim tuaz…® isizir ak…®nafarir kam…®n itir akabar m…®rarama ada osirigh.  
\v 29 Egh n…® uaghan, atrivim bagh kamagh…®n akam osir suam: 
\b  
\pm ‚ÄúK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® kamagh…®n m…®gei, Atrivim Jehoiakim, n…® ak…®nafarir kam tuagha kamagh…®n m…®keme, ‚ÄòTizim bagha Jeremaia akar kam osirigha ghaze, Babilon…®n atrivim iz…® nguazir kam gas…®ghasigh, gumazamiziba ko as…®ziba bar me m…®sueght…®, me ar…®ghiregham?‚Äô  
\v 30 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® Atrivim Jehoiakim g…®n…®ghn…®gha kamagh…®n m…®gei, an adarazir gumazitam atrivim…®n otogh, Devit…®n atrivir dabirabim daperaghan kogham. Eght…® Jehoiakim aremeghamin dughiam, me an kuam is…® nguazim…®n anekunight…®, aruem a dapongt…®, d…®magarim…®n ghuariam a giram.  
\v 31 Eght…® k…® an arazir kuraba ikarvaghs…®, a ko, an boriba ko, an ingangarir gumazir ekiaba sara bar paz…®v…®ra me damigham. Egh k…® damuasa m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, k…® bizir kurabar amut…® da Jerusalemia ko Judaba bativam. K…® akar kam me gan…®ngiz…®, me a baraghan aghua.‚Äù 
\b  
\p  
\v 32 Ez…® Jeremaia ak…®nafarir igiam inigha, egha ak…®nafariba osirir gumazim Nerian otarim, Baruk gan…®ngi. Egha Atrivim Jehoiakim tuaz…® akar ak…®nafarir kabar itiba, Jeremaia bar adar gun m…®keme. Egha uaghan kamagh…®ra ghuzir akar igiar maba sara m…®keme. Ez…® Baruk akar kaba bar da isa ak…®nafarir igiam…®n ada osiri.\f + \fr 36:32 \ft Fofozir gumazir av…®riba kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, ak…®nafarir igiar kam…®n itir akaba, da dat…®r…®gh…®n God…®n Akam Inigha Izir Gumazim Jeremaian Ak…®nafarir kam, an akar faragha zuir akabar aven iti, e da d…®bori. Egha e fozir puvat…®, m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kaba me managh ada osiri, egha me ti managh ikegha uam ada osira ghu.\f* 
\c 37  
\ms1 Jeremaia m…®kemez…® mogh…®n,  // God bar pazav…®ra Juda ko Jerusalem gami 
\mr (Sapta 37:1--40:6) 
\s1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God akam Sedekaian iti 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 37:1 \xt 2 Atriviba 24:17; 2 Eghaghaniba 36:10\x*Babilon…®n Atrivim Nebukatnesar, faragha Josaian otarim, Sedekaia am…®sevez…®, a Judan atrivim…®n oto. An Atrivim Jehoiakin…®n danganim ini. Jehoiakin, an ziar mam Konia, egha a Jehoiakim…®n otarim.  
\v 2 Dughiar kam…®n, Jeremaia Ikiav…®ra Itir God, a gan…®dir akabav gei, ez…® Sedekaia uan gumazir dapaniba ko gumazamiziba ko me bar mogh…®ra deragha kuariba arigha, akar kam barazir puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 3 Egha dughiar mam…®n, Sedekaia, Selemian otarim Jehukal ko, ofa gamir gumazim Sefanaia, a Masean otarim, aning amadaz…®, aning God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Jeremaia bagha ghua kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúAtrivim ghaze, N…® e bagh Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God, a ko m…®k…®m.‚Äù  
\v 4 Dughiar kam…®n Jeremaia t…®ghar kalabus…®n mangam. A zurara gumazamizibar tong…®n uan ifongiam…®n mang…® izegh gami.  
\v 5 Ez…® uaghan dughiar kam…®n, Kaldiabar m…®dorozir gumazir Jerusalem m…®soghasava amiba orazima, Isip…®n atrivim…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba, Isip ategha Jerusalem…®n izi. Kamagh…®n, Kaldiaba Jerusalem ataki. 
\p  
\v 6 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God akam isa uan akam inigha izir gumazim Jeremaia gan…®ngi, ez…® an akam isa Jehukal ko Sefanaia m…®k…®ri. Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam kamak…®n,  
\v 7 ‚ÄúK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Israelian God, k…® kamagh…®n m…®gei: Judan atrivim nan azangs…®gh na g…®foghasa gua amada, egh fogh suam, k…® ian akuragham, ti puvat…®gham? Eght…® n…® kamagh…®n atrivim m…®k…®m, Isip…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba ian akurvaghasa Isip ategha izi. Ez…® me iz…® ia batoghan kogham. Puvat…®. Me tuavim…®n uamategh ua uan kantrin mangam.  
\v 8 Eght…® Babilonia uamategh iz…® Jerusalemia m…®sogh…®va, nguibar ekiar kam iniam. Egh me nguibam daboroght…® a isigham.  
\v 9 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® guizbang…®ra Akar Gavgavim…®n ia m…®gei, Ia uarira uarigh ifar suam, ‚ÄòKaldiaba uamategh Jerusalem…®n izeghan kogham.‚Äô Akar kamagh…®n garim, a guiz…®n akam puvat…®. Me ua izam.  
\v 10 Ia ti Kaldiaba me m…®sogha, men m…®dorozir gumazir av…®riba bar me ab…®raz…® deraghai. Men m…®dorozir gumazir ik…®v…®ra ikiamin varazira ti duar ekiar av…®riba ko m…®dorozim…®n os…®mt…®ziba ik…® uan averpenibar ikegh, me guizbang…®ra ua d…®kavigh iz…® nguibar kam daboroght…® a isigham.‚Äù 
\s1 Me Jeremaia isa kalabus gat…® 
\p  
\v 11 Kaldiabar m…®dorozir gumaziba orazi, Isip…®n atrivim…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba Jerusalem bagha izi. Ez…® Kaldiaba Jerusalem ategha ghue.  
\v 12 Ez…® dughiar kam…®n Jeremaia Jerusalem ategha Benjamin…®n anabam…®n nguazim…®n mangasa, egh uan namakabar tong…®n men nguazir otevir mam iniasa.  
\v 13 A ghua Jerusalem…®n d…®vazim…®n tiar akar kam…®n oto, me kamagh…®n a d…®bori, Benjamin…®n Tiarakam. Ez…® m…®dorozir gumazibar gumazir dapanir mam, tiar akar kam…®n tugha gumazamizibagh eghuva, men gari me mang…® izegh gami. Gumazir dapanir kam…®n ziam, a Iriya, a Selemian otarim, egha Hananian igiavotarim. Ez…® Iriya Jeremaian suiragha ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® fo, n…® ar…® mang…® Kaldiaba ko ikiasava ami.‚Äù  
\v 14 Ez…® Jeremaia kamagh…®n an akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® ifari. K…® Kaldiaba bagha zuir puvat…®.‚Äù Ez…® Iriya n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim…®n Jeremaian akabar itir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n, a Jeremaian suiragha a inigha, gumazir dapaniba bagha ghu.  
\v 15 Gumazir dapaniba Iriyan akam baregha, puv…®ra Jeremaian atari. Egha me benim…®n a m…®suegha a isa atrivim…®n ak…®nafariba osirir gumazim Jonatan…®n d…®penim…®n kalabus gat…®. Me faragha Jonatan…®n d…®penim kalabus…®n m…®n a gami.  
\v 16 D…®penir kam, an kalabuziar danganim nguazim…®n aven iti. Me Jeremaia danganir kam…®n a kalabus gat…®, ez…® a dughiar ruarim…®n iti. 
\p  
\v 17 Ez…® g…®n, Sedekaia Jeremaian aku atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n izasa me m…®keme. Ez…® Sedekaia amizir bizir kam, gumazir igharaziba a g…®fozir puvat…®. Ez…® aning uaningra ikia egha Sedekaia kamagh…®n Jeremaian azara, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God akatam n…® gan…®ngi, o puvat…®?‚Äù 
\p Ez…® Jeremaia ghaze, ‚ÄúAre, Ikiav…®ra Itir God akar mam na gan…®ngi. Akar kam a kamak…®n. Me n…® is…® Babilon…®n atrivim dafarim dar…®gham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 18 Egha Jeremaia kamagh…®n Sedekaian azara, ‚ÄúK…® arazir kurar manam…®n n…® gami, o n…®n gumazir dapanitam, o n…®n gumazamizibagh amiz…®, ia na isa kalabus gat…®?  
\v 19 N…®n akam inigha izir gumazir maba kamagh…®n akam akunigha ghaze, ‚ÄòBabilon…®n atrivim iz…® n…® ko kantrin kam…®n m…®soghan kogham.‚Äô Egha dat…®r…®gh…®n akam inigha izir gumazir kaba managh iti.  
\v 20 Ez…® uaghan, ga uaning, gumazir ekiam, k…® bizir mam bagh n…®n azangs…®ghasa. N…® nan apangkuvigh, ua na amadaght…®, k…® ak…®nafariba osirir gumazim Jonatan…®n d…®penim…®n mangan mark…®. Puvat…®ght…®ma, k…® an d…®penim…®n ik…® mang…®va aremegham.‚Äù  
\v 21 Jeremaia m…®kemegha g…®vaz…®ma, Atrivim Sedekaia m…®geima, me Jeremaia isa atrivim…®n d…®vazim…®n aven m…®dorozir gumazibar danganir mam…®n, Jeremaia isa kalabus gat…®. Egha atrivim me m…®kemez…®, me dughiaba bar bretba tuer d…®penim…®n, bretba vaghvagha da isa iza Jeremaia gan…®di. Me arazir kam gamuav…®ra ikia, ghua nguibar ekiam…®n bretba bar g…®vazir dughiam otoz…®, me ua kamagh…®n amir puvat…®. Dughiar kabar, Jeremaia kamagh…®ra m…®dorozir gumazibar danganim…®n kalabus…®n ikiav…®ra iti. 
\c 38  
\s1 Me Jeremaia isa mozir mam gat…® 
\p  
\v 1-3 Jeremaia kamagh…®n akam gumazamizibav m…®k…®ri, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God ghaze: Gumazamizir nguibar ekiar kam…®n itiba, me ar…®ghiram. Apaniba taraziv sueght…® me ar…®m…®ghiregham, tarazi dagheba puvat…®gh ar…®ghiram, tarazi ar…®mariar kuram paz…® me damight…® me ar…®m…®ghiregham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me angam…®ra ik…®s…®, me nguibar ekiam ategh Babilon…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba bagh mang…®. Egh me Babilonia ateght…® me men suiraght…®, me ar…®m…®ghireghan kogham. Ikiav…®ra Itir God uaghan kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòK…® Babilon…®n atrivim…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba ateght…® me nguibar ekiar kam iniam.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù 
\p Ez…® atrivim…®n gumazir dapanir maba, Jeremaian akar kam baraki. Men ziabar kara: Matan otarim Sefatia ko, Pasur…®n otarim Gedalia ko, Selemian otarim Jehukal ko, Malkian otarim Pasur. 
\p  
\v 4 Ez…® gumazir dapanir kaba ghua kamagh…®n atrivim m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazir kam Jeremaia, a m…®geir akaba, nguibar ekiar kam…®n ikiav…®ra itir m…®dorozir gumaziba ko, gumazamizibar navir averiaba ko, n…®ghn…®ziba ko gavgavim d…®kab…®ri. Gumazir kam, men akuraght…® me deragh ikian aghua. Puvat…®. A me ikuvighasa a ifonge. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® a m…®sueght…®, an aremegh.‚Äù  
\v 5 Ez…® Atrivim Sedekaia kamagh…®n men akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúA ian dafarim…®n iti. K…® ian anogoreghan kogham.‚Äù  
\v 6 Ez…® gumazir kaba Jeremaia inigha mozir d…®par mam…®n ghu. Egha me benim…®n an agharimning ikegha, aghumra anetagh…®razima a mozim…®n uaghira, mozir kam…®n d…®k…®nim…®n tu. Mozir kam a d…®patam an itir puvat…®. Nguazir beghneazimra an iti. Ez…® Jeremaia mozir d…®k…®nim…®n tuz…® an suemning nguazir beghneazir kam giraghu. Kar atrivim…®n otarim Malkian mozim, a m…®dorozir gumazibar danganim…®n ikia atrivim…®n d…®penim av…®niz…® d…®vazim…®n aven iti. 
\p  
\v 7 Ebetmelek a Itiopian kantrin gumazir mam, an atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n gumazir dapanir mam, a kamagh…®n akam baraki, me Jeremaia isa mozir kam gat…®. Ez…® dughiar kam…®n, atrivim Benjamin…®n Tiarakam…®n borogh…®ram aperaghav ikia, gumazamizibar kotiam barasi.  
\v 8 Ez…® Ebetmelek atrivim…®n d…®penim ategha, atrivim bagha ghua, kamagh…®n a m…®g…®a ghaze,  
\v 9 ‚ÄúGa uaning, gumazir aruam, gumazir kaba arazir bar kuram…®n, akam inigha izir gumazim Jeremaia gami. Me a isa mozir mam m…®k…®ni. Eght…® a mozir kam…®n ik…®va, dagheba puvat…®gh aremegham. N…® fo, dagheba nguibar ekiar kam…®n bar puvat…®.‚Äù  
\v 10 Ez…® atrivim akar kam baregha, kamagh…®n Itiopian gumazim Ebetmelek m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® mang…®, na ko itir gumazibar tong…®n gumazir 30pla inigh, egh ia mang…® mozir kam…®n Jeremaia gekuigh anang. Eght…® an aremeghan kogham.‚Äù  
\v 11 Ez…® Ebetmelek gumazir kaba inigha atrivim…®n dag…®aba itir d…®penim…®n apengan itir danganir mam…®n ghu. Egha me inir ghuriba inigha Jeremaia itir mozir kam…®n ghu. Egha Ebetmelek inir ghurir kaba isa benir gavgavim gikegha, Jeremaia bagha da kuniz…® da ghuaghir…®.  
\v 12 Egha a kamagh…®n Jeremaia m…®gei, ‚ÄúInir kaba uan reziamning dat…®gh, egh benir gavgavim inigh iz…® dagh is…®n uab…® gikegh. Eght…® e n…® gekuamin dughiam…®n, benim n…® aghoran kogham.‚Äù Ez…® Jeremaia Ebetmelek m…®kemez…® mogh…®ram ami.  
\v 13 Ez…® me Jeremaia gekuiz…® a mozim…®n anabo. Egha me ua Jeremaia isa m…®dorozir gumazibar danganim gat…®z…® a ikiav…®ra iti. 
\s1 Sedekaia ua Jeremaia ko m…®gei 
\p  
\v 14 Ez…® g…®n, Atrivim Sedekaia gumaziba amangiz…®, me God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Jeremaia iniasa ghue, egha me an akua iza Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penir tiar akar namba 3…®n atrivim bato. Aning uaningra ikiava, atrivim kamagh…®n Jeremaia m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® bizitam bagh n…®n azangasa. Eght…® n…® deraghv…®ram a ikaragh. N…® akam nan mongan mark…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 15 Ez…® Jeremaia kamagh…®n an akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® akam…®n gun n…® m…®kemeght…®, bar guizbang…®ra, n…® na m…®sueght…® k…® aremegham. K…® ti n…®ghn…®zir aghuim n…® dan…®ngt…®, n…® nan akam baraghan kogham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 16 Ez…® Atrivim Sedekaia akar d…®k…®r…®zir mam Jeremaia bagha a gamigha ghaze, ‚ÄúBar guizbang…®ra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n bar p…®n itim, a God…®n ik…®r…®m…®rir angam…®ra itim isa gumazamizibagh an…®dim, k…® an ziam…®n n…® m…®gei, k…® n…® m…®sueght…® n…® aremeghan kogham. Egh k…® n…® is…® gumazir n…® gas…®ghas…®ghamibar dafarim dat…®ghan kogham. Bar puvat…®gham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 17 Ez…® Jeremaia kamagh…®n Sedekaia m…®gei, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, Israelian God, a ghaze, N…® m…®dorozim ategh, egh Babilon…®n atrivim…®n gumazir dapaniba ateght…® me n…® inigh, n…® m…®sueght…® n…® aremeghan koght…®, me nguibar kam daboroght…® a isighan kogham. Eght…® n…® uan amuiroghboriba ko ia deraghv…®ra ikiam.  
\v 18 Egh n…® Babilonia ateght…® me n…® inighan kogham, eght…® k…® me ateght…® me nguibar kam inigham, egh me a daboroght…® a isigham. Eght…® n…® uab…® men ar…®mang…®ghan kogham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 19 Ez…® Sedekaia kamagh…®n Jeremaia m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® Judan ara ghua Babilonia ko itir darazir marazir atiatingi. Kamagh…®n Babilonia ti na is…® Judan kabar dafarim dat…®ght…®, me paz…®v…®ra na damigham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 20 Ez…® Jeremaia ghaze, ‚ÄúMe n…® is…® Judabar dafarim dat…®ghan kogham. Puvat…®. N…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God nan akam garugha n…® gan…®ngizir akaba bar adar g…®n mang…®, egh n…® deraghv…®ra ik…®t…®, me n…® m…®sueght…® n…® aremeghan kogham.  
\v 21 Egh n…® Babilonia ateght…® me n…® inighan koght…®, bizir kurataba n…® bativigham. Ikiav…®ra Itir God irebam…®n m…®n garir bizir mam…®n aven, bizir kam nan aka.  
\v 22 Ez…® irebar kam…®n k…® Babilonian garima, me amizir n…®n d…®penim…®n ikiav…®ra itiba, me inigha men akua Babilon…®n atrivim…®n gumazir dapaniba bagha ghue. Ez…® k…® amizir kaba barazi me kamagh…®n m…®gei: 
\b  
\q1 ‚Äú‚Äâ‚ÄòO Atrivim Sedekaia, n…® namakabar akam baraki, 
\q2 me n…® gifaragha n…® d…®kab…®ra. 
\q1 Dat…®r…®gh…®n dughiar kuram n…® bato, 
\q2 mati n…®n dagarimning nguazir beghneazim giraghu. 
\q3 Ez…® namakaba anetaki.‚Äô 
\b  
\m  
\v 23 ‚ÄúK…® irebar kam…®n gani, egha k…® fo, bar guizbang…®ra, Babilonia n…®n amuiroghboriba iniam. Ez…® n…® uaghan men ar…®v avegham. Puvat…®. Babilon…®n atrivim n…®n suiragham. Egha n…® akam batoghezir arazim bang…®n, Babilonia nguibar ekiar kam daboroght…® a isigham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 24 Ez…® Sedekaia kamagh…®n Jeremaian akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúN…®, ga uan akam…®n gun gumazir igharazitam m…®k…®man mark…®. N…® m…®kemegh…®va, aremegham.  
\v 25 Gumazir dapaniba kamagh…®n oregh suam, ga uaning m…®keme, egh me ti iz…® kamagh…®n n…®n azangs…®gham, ‚ÄòN…® manmagh…®n atrivim m…®keme? Ez…® atrivim akar manam n…® m…®keme? N…® e m…®kemegh. N…® akar kam mongan mark…®. Puvat…®ght…®, e n…® m…®sueght…® n…® aremegham.‚Äô Me akar kamagh garitam n…® m…®kemeght…®,  
\v 26 n…® kamagh…®n men akam ikaragh, ‚ÄòPuvat…®. K…® atrivim ko m…®g…®a, egha an azangs…®si, a ua na amadaght…® k…® Jonatan…®n d…®penim…®n kalabus…®n ikian kogham. Puvat…®ght…®, k…® d…®penir kam…®n ik…® mang…® aremegham.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù 
\p  
\v 27 Egha g…®n gumazir dapanir kaba bar Jeremaia bagha izegha, an azangs…®si. Ez…® ana atrivim a m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, kamagh…®n men akaba ikara. Ez…® gumazitam atrivim ko Jeremaian akatam baraghizir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, gumazir dapaniba ua an azangs…®ghan iburagha, Jeremaia ategha ghu.  
\v 28 \x - \xo 38:28 \xt Esekiel 33:21\x*Ez…® Jeremaia m…®dorozir gumazibar danganim…®n ikiav…®ra ikia ghua, apaniba Jerusalem inizir dughiam…®n tu. 
\c 39  
\s1 Babilonia me Jerusalem ini 
\r (Jeremaia 52:1-11) 
\p  
\v 1 Egha namba 9…®n azenim…®n Sedekaia atrivim…®n ikia ghua, namba 10…®n iak…®nim…®n otogha ghua an namba 10…®n iak…®nir kam…®n aruem…®n oto. Ez…® Babilon…®n Atrivim Nebukatnesar uan m…®dorozir gumaziba bar me inigha iza, Jerusalem…®n nguibar ekiam korogha a iniasa m…®sosi.  
\v 2 Me m…®sogha ikiav…®ra itima iak…®nir 6pla g…®fa, ez…® Sedekaia atrivim…®n itir azenir namba 11 otoz…®, azenir kam…®n namba 4…®n iak…®nim oto, egha an namba 9…®n dughiam…®n, me d…®vazim…®n vuer mam akarigha, Jerusalem…®n aven ghue.  
\v 3 Egha dughiar kam, Babilon…®n atrivim…®n gumazir dapaniba bar nguibar ekiam…®n aven ghue. Gumazir dapanibar ziabar kara: Nergal Sareser ko, Samgar Nebo ko, gumazir ekiar faragha zuim Sarsekim ko, m…®dorozir gumazibar dapanim Nergal Sareser. Me ghua nguibar ekiam…®n d…®vazir kam…®n Ar…®ghan Itir Tiarakam…®n ghuegha, nguibar ekiam gativaghasa a gapiagha iti.\f + \fr 39:3 \ft Gumazir dapanir kabar ziaba ko men ingangariba me deragha da ab…®ghizir puvat…®.\f* 
\v 4 Judan Atrivim Sedekaia uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko me bar mogh…®ra garima, Babilonia izima, me are. Me d…®magarim…®n suebar ghuava atrivim…®n dagher azenim…®n otivigha ghua, danganir d…®vazir pumuning uaning isasuiragha itir tiar akar kam…®n ghua, nguibar ekiam…®n otivigha ghue. Egha me Jordan…®n Fanem…®n danganir zarim…®n ghua tuavim…®n zui.  
\v 5 Ez…® Babilon…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba men ag…®raz…®, me ghua Jerikon nguibar ekiam…®n borogh…®n itir danganir zarim…®n otoz…®, me Sedekaian suira. Egha me a inigha Atrivim Nebukatnesar bagha ghu. Ez…® dughiar kam…®n Atrivim Nebukatnesar Riplan nguibam…®n iti, Hamat…®n nguazim…®n aven itir nguibam. Ez…® Nebukatnesar uan kot…®n aven Sedekaian gara ghaze, Sedekaia uan arazir kurar an amizim…®n ivezim iniam. 
\p  
\v 6 Ez…® Babilonian atrivim Riplan nguibam…®n ikia Sedekaian otariba inigha, Sedekaian damazim…®n bar me m…®suaghar…®ki. Egha a uaghan Judan gumazir dapaniba me m…®suaghar…®ki.  
\v 7 Egha atrivim m…®kemez…®, me Sedekaian damazimning asi, egha an suemning ko dafarimning sen…®n ada ikegha, a inigha Babilon…®n ghu. 
\p  
\v 8 Ez…® Kaldiabar m…®dorozir gumaziba Jerusalem…®n ikia atrivim…®n d…®penim ko gumazamizibar d…®penibagh apongez…® da isi. Egha Jerusalem av…®nizir d…®vaziba bar da akaraghar…®ki.  
\v 9 Ez…® Nebusaradan, a Babilon…®n gumazir dapanibar faragha zuim, a Jerusalem…®n iti, a Jerusalem…®n gumazamizir ikiav…®ra itiba bar me inigha, men akua kalabus bagha Babilon…®n ghu. Egha uaghan Judan faragha Jerusalem ategha ara ghua, an gara a ko ikezibar akua, me inigha Babilon…®n kalabus bagha ghu.  
\v 10 Egha Nebusaradan, gumazamizir onganarazibagh amir maba ataghiz…®, merara Judan nguazim…®n ikiav…®ra iti. Gumazamizir kaba nguaziba ko biziba puvat…®. Ez…® a dughiar kam…®n wain…®n azeniba ko, azenir igharaziba sara me gan…®ngi. 
\s1 Atrivim m…®kemez…®, Jeremaia kalabus ataki 
\p  
\v 11 Atrivim Nebukatnesar Jeremaia g…®n…®ghn…®gha, egha Jerusalem…®n Nebusaradan bagha anemada, Babilon…®n gumazir dapanibar faragha zuim. Nebukatnesar…®n akam kamak…®n,  
\v 12 ‚ÄúN…® mang…® Jeremaia inigh deraghv…®ram an gan. N…® paz…® a damuan mark…®. N…® an ifongiam…®n g…®n mang…®va, bizir manam ana damuasa n…®n azai, n…® a damu.‚Äù  
\v 13 Ez…® Babilon…®n gumazir dapanibar faragha zuim Nebusaradan, a ko an gumazir ekiar an apengan ikia faragha itimning, Nebusasban ko Nergal Sareser, aning ko Babilon…®n gumazir ekiar igharaziba, me bar d…®kavigha,  
\v 14 gumaziba amangiz…®, me m…®dorozir gumaziba itir danganim…®n ghua Jeremaia ini. Egha me Jeremaia isa, Gedalian dafarim gat…®. Gedalia, a Ahikam…®n otarim, egha Safan…®n igiavotarim. Me, Jeremaia inigh an d…®penim…®n mangasa Gedalia m…®gei. Kamagh…®n, Jeremaia ua uan nguibam…®n ghua uan namakaba ko Judan nguazim…®n ikiav…®ra iti. 
\s1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God akam Ebetmelek gan…®ngi 
\p  
\v 15 Jeremaia faragha m…®dorozir gumazibar danganim…®n ikiav…®ra itima, Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n akam isa a gan…®ga ghaze,  
\v 16 ‚ÄúN…® Itiopian gumazim Ebetmelek bagh mang…®, kamagh…®n a m…®k…®m suam: Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, a Israelian God, a kamagh…®n m…®keme, K…® fom…®ra nguibar ekiar kam gas…®ghas…®ghasa, ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n nan akam…®n daghem otogham. K…® nguibar ekiar kam deraghv…®ra a damuan kogham. Ez…® n…® uab…® bizir k…® damuasa m…®kemezibar ganam.  
\v 17 K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® m…®kemes, K…® bizir kam damuamin dughiam, k…® n…®n akuraght…®, me n…® is…® gumazir n…® atiatibar dafaribar at…®ghan kogham.  
\v 18 K…® deraghv…®ra n…®n akurvagh n…®n ganam, eght…® me n…® m…®sueght…® n…® aremeghan kogham. N…® n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim nan iti, kamagh…®n n…® aremeghan kogham. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® m…®kemegha g…®fa.‚Äù 
\c 40  
\s1 Nebusaradan Jeremaia ko m…®gei 
\p  
\v 1 Nebusaradan Jeremaia ataghiz…® a f…®riagh…®r…®gha zuir dughiam…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God akam isa Jeremaia gan…®ngi. Babilonia Jeremaia ko, Judaba ko, Jerusalemia inigha senbar me ike, egh men aku kalabus bagh Babilon…®n mangam. Egha me Raman nguibam…®n otivir dughiam…®n, gumazir dapanir faragha zuim Nebusaradan, Jeremaian garima a me ko iti, ez…® a anetaghiz…® a f…®riagh…®r…®gha ghu.  
\v 2 Ez…® dughiar kam…®n Nebusaradan kamagh…®n Jeremaia m…®gei, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God, n…®n God, bizir kurar kantrin kam…®n otivamim…®n gun m…®keme.  
\v 3 Egha dat…®r…®gh…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God m…®kemez…® mogh…®n bizir kabagh amima da otifi, Ia Israelia Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akaba batuegha, an damazim…®n arazir kuram gami. Ez…® bizir m…®ngarir kam bagha, bizir kaba ia batifi.  
\v 4 N…® oragh. Dat…®r…®gh…®n k…® sen…®n n…®n dafarimning ikezir kam f…®ri, ez…® n…® dat…®r…®gh…®n f…®righ…®r…®gh ik…®. Egh n…® na ko Babilon…®n iz…®s…®, kamagh…®n n…® iz…®, eght…® k…® deraghv…®ra n…®n ganam. N…® aghuagh mark…®, a dera n…® ik…®. Ez…® kantrin kam…®n danganir manaba n…® dar mangasa ifonge, n…® pura mang…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 5 Jeremaia akar kam baregha, Nebusaradan ataghizir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Nebusaradan Jeremaia m…®g…®a ghua ghaze, ‚ÄúPuvat…®ght…®, n…® Gedalia bagh mang…®, an Ahikam…®n otarim, egha Safan…®n igiavotarim. Babilon…®n atrivim Judan nguibabagh ativagh dar ganasa anem…®sefe. A gumazamizir maba ko kagh ik…®t…®, n…® a ko ik…®. N…® aghuagh…®va, managh mangasa ifonge, n…® mang…®.‚Äù Egha Nebusaradan bizir aghuir mam ko dagher maba sara Jeremaia ganigha anetaghiz…®, a ghu.  
\v 6 Ez…® Jeremaia ghua Gedalia bagha nguibam Mispan ghu. Jeremaia a gumazamizir Judan nguazim…®n ikiav…®ra itibar tong…®n me ko iti. 
\ms1 Me Jeremaian akua Isip…®n zui 
\mr (Sapta 40:7--45:5) 
\s1 Gedalia Judan gavman…®n gumazir faragha zuim…®n iti 
\r (2 Atriviba 25:22-24) 
\p  
\v 7 \x - \xo 40:7-9 \xt 2 Atriviba 25:22-24\x*Judan m…®dorozir gumazir maba uan gumazir dapaniba ko, me kantrin danganir mabar ikiav…®ra iti. Me kamagh…®n akam baraki, Babilon…®n atrivim, Gedalia Judan nguazim…®n, gavman…®n gumazir dapanir faragha zuim…®n ikiasa anem…®sefe. Ez…® a onganarazibagh amir gumazamiziba ko borir Babilonia inigha Babilon…®n kalabus…®n ghuezir puvat…®zir kabar ganamin ingangarim iti.  
\v 8 Ez…® gumazir dapanir kaba uan m…®dorozir gumaziba inigha, me Gedalian ganasa Mispan ghue. Gumazir dapanir kabar ziabar kara: Netanian otarim Ismael ko, Karean otarimning Johanan ko Jonatan, ko Tanhumet…®n otarim Seraia ko, Netofan nguibam…®n gumazim Efain otariba ko, Makan nguazim…®n gumazim Jesania.  
\v 9 Ez…® Gedalia me ko akam ak…®ra ghaze, ‚ÄúBar guizbang…®ra, ia Babilonia men apengan ik…®va, men atiatingan mark…®. Puvat…®. Ia nguazir kam…®n ik…®va, Babilon…®n atrivim…®n apengan ik…® deraghv…®ra ikiam.  
\v 10 K…® uab…®, k…® Mispan kagh ikiam. Babilonia iz…® en ganamin dughiam, k…® Judaba e uan abuir gumazim…®n ikiam. Iarara, ia uamategh nguibar ia inizir kabar mang…®, wain…®n ikar…®zir ov…®ziba ko ov…®zir igharazir aghuiba inigh, wain ko borebar ingar, egh g…®n izamin dughiam bagh ada is…® m…®nebar ar…®gh.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 11 Ez…® dughiar kam…®n Judan marazi Moap ko, Amon ko, Idom ko kantrin igharazibar iti. Me kamagh…®n akam baraki, Babilon…®n atrivim gumazamizir varazira ataghiz…® me Judan nguazim…®n itima, ez…® atrivim me gativagh men ganasa, Gedalia am…®sefe, a Ahikam…®n otarim, egha Safan…®n igiavotarim.  
\v 12 Ez…® Judan gumazamizir apaniba me batoghez…® me ghuezir nguibar kaba, me da ategha uamategha Judan nguazim…®n ize. Egha me Gedalian ganasa Mispan ghue. Egha g…®n, wain…®n ikar…®zir ov…®ziba ko, ov…®zir igharazir aghuiba azenibar da isava, me wain…®n av…®riba ko dagher aghuiba iti. 
\s1 Ismael Gedalia m…®soghez…® an areme 
\r (2 Atriviba 25:25-26) 
\p  
\v 13 Ez…® dughiar mam…®n, Karean otarim Johanan ko, Judan m…®dorozir gumazibar, gumazir dapaniba, me kantrin danganir mabar ikegha Gedalia bagha Mispan ize.  
\v 14 Egha me kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúAmon…®n kantrin Atrivim Balis, n…® m…®sueght…® n…® aremeghasa, Netanian otarim Ismael amadaz…®, a ize. N…® bizir kam g…®fo, o puvat…®?‚Äù Ez…® Gedalia men akam n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an itir puvat…®.  
\v 15 Ez…® Johanan ko Gedalia uaningra itir dughiam…®n, Johanan n…®m…®ra kamagh…®n Gedalian m…®gei, ‚ÄúGa uaning. N…® na ateght…® k…® mang…® Ismael m…®sueght…® ana aremeka. Gumazitam bizir kam g…®foghan kogham. N…® aneteght…® a n…® m…®sueght…®, n…® aremeght…®, Judan dat…®r…®gh…®n iza n…® akuvagha itiba, me tintinibar mangegham. Eght…® en gumazamizir ikiav…®ra itir varazira, e bar ikuvigham.‚Äù  
\v 16 Ez…® Ahikam…®n otarim Gedalia kamagh…®n Karean otarim Johanan akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® arazir kam damuan mark…®. K…® fo, n…® Ismael…®n gun m…®geir akar kam, a guiz…®n akam puvat…®. N…® ifari.‚Äù 
\c 41  
\p  
\v 1-2 \x - \xo 41:1-3 \xt 2 Atriviba 25:25\x*Ismael a Netanian otarim, egha a Elisaman igiavotarim, egha a Judan atrivim…®n ik…®zir mam. An atrivim…®n gumazir dapanir faragha zuir mam…®n ike. Babilon…®n atrivim Judan gavman…®n faragha zuir gumazim…®n ikiasa Gedalia am…®sefe, ez…® azenir kam…®n, an namba 7…®n iak…®nim otoz…®, Ismael 10plan gumaziba inigha, Gedalian ganasa Mispan ize. Egha me Gedalia ko apiagha apir dughiam…®n, Ismael 10plan gumaziba ko me d…®kavigha, uan m…®dorozir sababa inigha Gedalia m…®soghez…® an areme.  
\v 3 Ez…® Ismael uaghan Judan Gedalia ko Mispan itiba sara m…®suegha, Kaldiabar m…®dorozir gumazir dughiar kam…®n Mispan itiba sara m…®soghez…®, me ariaghire. 
\p  
\v 4 Ez…® am…®mzaraghan, gumaziba fozir puvat…®, Gedalia aremegha g…®fa,  
\v 5 ez…® Sekem…®n nguibam ko, Silon nguibam ko, Samarian nguibam…®n gumazir 80pla arua iza Mispan borogh…®ra izi. Me wit ko pauran mughuriar aghuim zuim inigha, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim bagha Jerusalem…®n mang…® ofa damuasa zui. Gumazir kaba uan ghuamas…®zibagh isava, uan korotiaba ab…®gha, tintinibar uan m…®karzibar ghora uan apangkuvim ko os…®mt…®zim akakaghasa.  
\v 6 Dughiar kam, Netanian otarim Ismael men gari, me izima, a Mispa ategha, me gifara aziava me bagha tuavim…®n zui. A ghaze, an azirakam ti gumazibar amut…®, me suam, a me ko apangkuvir kam iti. Egha a ghua me batogha kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa iz…®, Ahikam…®n otarim Gedalia, ia an ganasa ai ifonge.‚Äù  
\v 7 Me nguibar ekiam…®n aven ghuez…®, Ismael uan adarazi ko me gumazir av…®rir kabav suegha, men kuaba akuniz…® me mozir d…®par ekiar mam giraghue.  
\v 8 Ez…® gumazir kabar tong…®n itir 10plan gumaziba kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® en m…®sueght…® e aremeghan mark…®. E tuzim…®n dagher bar av…®riba mongez…® da iti, witba ko, baliba ko, oliv…®n boreba ko, haniba. E da n…® dan…®ngam.‚Äù Ez…® Ismael men akam baregha, 10plan gumazir kabav soghez…® me ariaghirezir puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 9 Mozir d…®par kam, Judan Atrivim Asa, fom…®ra ghaze, Israelian Atrivim Basa iz…® Mispan m…®sogh…®va, nguibar ekiam av…®night…®, Mispan gumazamiziba d…®pam…®n oteveghan kogham. A Mispan gumazamiziba d…®pam…®n oteveghan aghuagha an a g…®kui. Mozir d…®par kamra, dat…®r…®gh…®n Ismael…®n adarazi me Gedalia m…®soghez…® an aremezir dughiam…®n, me gumazir kuar kaba inigha mozir kam gaghuiz…®, mozir kam iz…®fa. 
\p  
\v 10 Ez…® g…®n, Ismael Mispan itir gumazamizir igharaziba inigha, Mispa ategha, men akua Amon…®n kantrin zui. Babilon…®n m…®dorozir gumazibar dapanim Nebusaradan, a faragha gumazamizir kaba, Mispan nguibam…®n me ataghiz…® me itima, a men ganasa Gedalia am…®sefe. Ez…® Judan atrivim…®n guiviba uaghan men tong…®n iti. 
\p  
\v 11 Ez…® Karean otarim Johanan, ko Judan m…®dorozir gumazibar dapanir maba, me Netanian otarim Ismael amizir arazir kuraba bar da baraki.  
\v 12 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me d…®kavigha uan m…®dorozir gumaziba inigha, Ismael m…®soghasa an g…®nt…®gha zui. Me an g…®nt…®gha ghua Gibeon…®n nguibam…®n itir d…®par akarer ekiam…®n borogh…®ram a bato.  
\v 13 Ez…® Ismael Mispan inigha a ko izezir gumazamiziba, me Karean otarim Johanan ko gumazir dapanir mabar ganigha, bar akonge.  
\v 14 Egha me bar Ismael ategha, ivemara Karean otarim Johanan bagha ghue.  
\v 15 Ez…® Johanan adarazi Ismael…®n suighasa amima, a uan gumazir 8pla ko, me ara ghua Amon…®n kantrin ghue. 
\p  
\v 16 Ez…® Karean otarim Johanan, ko gumazir dapanir an g…®n zuiba, me Ismael…®n dafarim…®n ada ua Mispan gumazamiziba ini. M…®dorozir gumazir igharaziba ko, men amuiroghboriba, ko atrivim…®n ingangarir gumaziba, me ik…®zir kam…®n tong…®n iti. Gumazamizir kabara, Netanian otarim Ismael faragha Gedalia m…®suegha g…®vagha, egha kalabuziabar m…®n bar me inigha Mispa ategha Gibeon…®n ghu. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n me bar Gibeon ategha ghue.  
\v 17-18 Johanan men aku Isip…®n mangasava ami. Ez…® me fo, Ismael Gedalia m…®soghez…® an areme, gumazir kam Babilon…®n atrivim Judan nguazim gativagh an ganasa anem…®sefe. Egha me atiatia n…®ghn…®si, Kaldiaba ti men otivizir biziba baregham, egh iz…® me gas…®ghasigham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me Isip…®n mangasa ifonge. Egha me Betlehem…®n nguibam…®n borogh…®ra, Gerut Kimham…®n nguibam…®n otivigha iti. 
\c 42  
\s1 Gumazamiziba Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko m…®k…®masa Jeremaian azangs…®si 
\p  
\v 1 Egha g…®n, Karean otarim Johanan ko, Hosaian otarim Jesania ko, m…®dorozir gumazir maba ko, gumazamiziba bar, kar gumazir aruaba ko gumazir k…®niba, me bar d…®kavigha,  
\v 2 God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Jeremaia bagha ghue. Egha me kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúE uari, n…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, n…®n God, n…® a ko m…®k…®m, egh an azaraght…®, a en gumazamizir ikiav…®ra itir varazira an en akuragham. E fom…®ra av…®raseme, ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n n…® garima, e bar ik…®zir muziariba iti.  
\v 3 E kamaghsua, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, n…®n God, tuavir manam…®n e mangam, ko bizir tizir e damuamim, an e m…®kemegh.‚Äù  
\v 4 Ez…® God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Jeremaia kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúA dera. K…® ian akam…®n amamangat…®. Ez…® ia nan azaraz…® mogh…®n, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, a ko m…®k…®mam. Eght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God akar manam…®n na ikaraght…®, k…® an gun ia m…®k…®mam. K…® akatam ian modoghan kogham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 5 Ez…® gumazamiziba kamagh…®n Jeremaia m…®gei, ‚ÄúBar guizbang…®ra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, n…®n God, e an akaba bar adar g…®n mangam. Ikiav…®ra Itir God guiz…®n araziba ko, vorogh…®ra zuir araziba zurara adagh ami. Eght…® e an akar, an e bagha n…® gan…®ngizibar g…®n mangan koght…®, a uan kot…®n aven e tuis…®gham.  
\v 6 Ikiav…®ra Itir God e bagha en azangs…®ziba ikarvagha n…® gan…®dir akar kaba, da paz…® e damuam o, da deragh e damuam, e pura dar g…®n mangam. Bar guizbang…®ra, e Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akabar g…®n mangam, an en God, ez…® e deraghv…®ra ikiam.‚Äù 
\s1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God Jeremaian azangs…®zim ikara 
\p  
\v 7 Ez…® Jeremaia Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko m…®geima, 10plan dughiabar g…®n, an akam a gan…®ngi.  
\v 8 Ez…® Jeremaia d…®kavigha, Karean otarim Johanan ko m…®dorozir gumazibar dapanir a ko itiba ko, gumazamiziba bar, kar gumazir aruaba ko gumazir k…®niba, a men diaz…® me a bagha ize.  
\v 9 Ez…® a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko m…®k…®masa nan azangs…®ki. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Israelian God, kamagh…®n m…®gei:  
\v 10 \x - \xo 42:10 \xt Jeremaia 1:10\x*Ia Judan nguazim…®n kagh ik…®t…®, k…® gavgavim ia dan…®ngigh, egh ia d…®kab…®raghan kogham. Guizbang…®ra, bizir kurar k…® ia gamizir kam, a na gamima k…® bar oseme. Kamagh…®n k…® ia akaragh, ua ia asighan kogham.  
\v 11 Ia Babilon…®n atrivim…®n atiati, ez…® k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® guizbang…®ra m…®gei, K…® ia ko iti. Egh k…® ian akuragh an dafarim…®n ua ia inigham. Kamagh…®n, ia uam an atiatingan mark…®.  
\v 12 K…® ian apangkuvigh, egh a damut…®, a uaghan ian apangkuvigham. Egh ia ateght…®, ia uamategh uan nguazim…®n mangam. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® m…®kemegha g…®fa. 
\p  
\v 13 ‚ÄúEz…® ia nan akaba batoghan mark…®, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God. Egh ia kamagh…®n m…®k…®man mark…®, ‚ÄòE Judan nguzim…®n ikian aghua.  
\v 14 Puvat…®. E Isip…®n mangam. E Isipra ik…®t…®, apaniba e m…®sueghan kogham. Eght…® gumazamiziba m…®soghs…® s…®ghabagh iviva, en d…®man kogham. Eght…® e daghebar oteveghan kogham. E pura Isip…®n ikiam.‚Äô  
\v 15 O Judan ikiav…®ra itir varazira, ia oragh! Ia akar kamagh…®n amizim m…®kemeght…®, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® akam ian ikiam. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, Israelian God, k…® ia m…®gei, Ia ti gavgavigh mang…® Isip…®n ik…®t…®,  
\v 16 bizir ia atiatiba, da Isip…®n ia bativam. Apaniba ia m…®soght…® ia ar…®ghiram, egh ia dagheba puvat…®gh ar…®ghiram.  
\v 17 Gumazamizir otuegh gavgavigh, mang…® Isip…®n ikiamiba, me bar ar…®ghiregham. Apaniba taraziv sueght…® me ar…®ghiram, eght…® tarazi dagheba puvat…®gh ar…®m…®ghiregham, eght…® tarazi ar…®mariar kuram iniva ar…®m…®ghiram. K…® bizir kurar kabar amut…®, da me bativt…®, men adarazi bar g…®vaght…®, men ikiav…®ra itir varazira, ua ikian kogham. 
\p  
\v 18 ‚ÄúK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, Israelian God, k…® guizbang…®ra m…®gei: K…® faragha puv…®ra Jerusalemian an…®ngagha, bar pazav…®ra me gas…®ghas…®ki. Eght…® kamagh…®ra, ia Isip…®n mang…®ght…®, k…® bar puv…®ra ian an…®ngaghegh, bar paz…®v…®ra ia gas…®ghasigham. Eght…® Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba, bizir k…® ia gamiziba baregh…®va, atiating, d…®gavir kuram damigham. Egh me paz…® ia damuva, egh d…®bovir akabar ia m…®k…®mam. Egh me uari akar kurabar uan apaniba m…®k…®ms…®, me kamagh…®n m…®k…®mam, ‚ÄòIa Judaba ikuviz…® mogh…®n, ia ikuvigham.‚Äô Egh ia ua uan nguazir kam…®n ganighan kogham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 19 Jeremaia Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam akunigha g…®vagha, kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúO ia Judan gumazamizir ikiav…®ra itir varazira, ia oragh! Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Isip…®n mangan ian anogoregha m…®keme. Ez…® ia akar ikiangs…®zir k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ia gan…®ngizir kam deraghv…®ram a g…®n…®ghn…®gh.  
\v 20 Ia, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, a ko m…®k…®masa nan azangs…®gha, kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòJeremaia, n…® mang…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God, n…® a ko m…®k…®m, egh an azaraght…®, an akam e dan…®ngigh. Eght…® akar manam a n…® danight…®, n…® e m…®kemeght…®, e an g…®n mangam.‚Äô Ez…® ia dat…®r…®gh…®n arazir igharazim damuasava ami. Ian arazir kam, a bar derazir puvat…®. A ia damut…®, ia ikuvigham.  
\v 21 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, a ia dan…®ngasa na gan…®ngizir akam, k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ia gan…®ngi. Ez…® ia akar kam…®n g…®n zuir puvat…®.  
\v 22 Kamagh…®n, ia deraghv…®ra fogh, danganir ia mang…® ikiasa amir kam, apaniba ian taraziv sueght…® me ar…®m…®ghiregham, eght…® tarazi dagheba puvat…®gh ar…®m…®ghiregham, eght…® tarazi ar…®mariar kuram iniva ar…®m…®ghiregham.‚Äù 
\c 43  
\s1 Me Jeremaia inigha, gumazamizir ikiav…®ra itir varazira sara Isip…®n ghue 
\p  
\v 1 Akar Ikiav…®ra Itir God, men God, gumazamizibav k…®masa Jeremaia m…®kemeziba, Jeremaia dar gun gumazamizibav kemegha g…®vaz…®ma,  
\v 2 Hosaian otarim Asaria, ko Karean otarim Johanan, ko gumazir akaba batozir maba, me kamagh…®n Jeremaia m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® ifari. Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God, e mang…® Isip…®n ikiasa en anogorogha, e m…®k…®masa n…® amadazir puvat…®. Bar puvat…®.  
\v 3 Kar Nerian otarim Baruk, anar…®ra e d…®kab…®nasa n…®n n…®ghn…®zim…®n fe. N…® Kaldiaba e inigh e m…®sueght…® e aremeghasa, o en aku kalabus bagh Babilon…®n mangasa n…® ifonge.‚Äù  
\v 4 Egha me akar kam m…®kemez…®, ez…® Karean otarim Johanan ko gumazir dapanir maba, ko gumazamiziba bar mogh…®ra Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam batogha, Judan nguazim…®n ikian aghua.  
\v 5-6 \x - \xo 43:5-7 \xt 2 Atriviba 25:26\x*Karean otarim Johanan uan gumazir dapaniba ko, me d…®kavigha, Judan gumazamizir ikiav…®ra itir varazira, bar mogh…®ra me inigha zui. Gumazir kaba, ko amiziba ko boriba, apaniba fom…®ra me batoghez…® me kantrin igharazibar ghueziba, me fom…®ra uamategha Judan nguazim…®n ize. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n Johanan uaghan, Judan atrivim…®n guiviba ko gumazamizir igharaziba ini. Kar Nebusaradan, Babilon…®n m…®dorozir gumazibar gumazir faragha zuim, me gativagh men ganasa Gedalia am…®sefe. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n Johanan ko gumazir dapaniba, Judan gumazamizir kaba ko, God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Jeremaia ko Nerian otarim Baruk, bar me inigha zui.  
\v 7 Egha me men akua bar Isip…®n ghu. Egha arazir kam…®n me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam batoke. Egha me ghua nguibam Tapanes…®n otifi, kar Isip…®n kantrin nguibar mam. 
\p  
\v 8 Me Tapanes…®n itima, Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n Jeremaia m…®keme,  
\v 9 ‚ÄúN…® mang…® dag…®ar ekiar taba inigh mang…® Isip…®n atrivim…®n d…®penir nguibar kam…®n itim…®n tiar akam…®n apengan, nguazim g…®kuigh an aven dar afegh. Judan marazi nguibar kam…®n iti, me n…®n gant…®, n…® a damu.\f + \fr 43:9 \ft Hibrun akam deragha m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®.\f* 
\v 10 Egh Judan kaba kamagh…®n me m…®kemegh: Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, Israelian God, a kamagh…®n m…®keme: K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® uan ingangarir gumazim Babilon…®n Atrivim Nebukatnesar…®n diagham. Eght…® a danganir kam…®n izam. Egh dag…®ar k…® mozim g…®kuigha dafezir kabagh is…®n, uan atrivir dabirabim afagham. Egh a uaghan uan purirpenim asaragh, nguazir otevir dag…®ar kaba itir kam avaragham.  
\v 11 A iz…® Isip…®n kantri gas…®ghasigham. K…® gumazir maba me ar…®mariar kuram inigh ar…®ghirasa me am…®sefe, eght…® dughiar kam…®n me ar…®mariar kuram iniam. Ez…® gumazir maba me mang…® kantrin igharazim…®n kalabus…®n ikiasa, k…® me am…®sefe, eght…® dughiar kam…®n me kalabus…®n mangam. Ez…® k…® gumazir maba me mang…® m…®sogh ar…®ghirasa, me am…®sefe, eght…® dughiar kam…®n me mang…® m…®sogh…®va ar…®ghiram.  
\v 12 Egh k…® Isip…®n asebar ziaba fer d…®penibar apongegham. D…®penir kaba, da Isip…®n asebar marvir guaba dar iti. Eght…® Nebukatnesar marvir guar katabar apong…®va, taba inigh uan kantrin mangam. Egh a Isip…®n kantrin biziba bar ada batuegham, mati sipsipbagh eghuvir gumazim, uan korotiam…®n piba batosi. A Isipba bar me gafiragham. Egh a kantrin kam ategh deraghv…®ra mangam.  
\v 13 A Isip…®n ikiamin dughiam…®n, a dag…®ar d…®penir ak…®nir ruarir d…®penir kam…®n itiba ap…®righam, gumazamiziba zurara d…®penim…®n ghua, aruem…®n ziam fe, mati men asem. Egh a bar Isipian asebar ziaba fer d…®peniba, bar dar apongt…® da isigham.‚Äù 
\c 44  
\s1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God akam isa Judan Isip…®n itibagh an…®di 
\p  
\v 1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God akam isa Judan Isip…®n itir daraziv k…®nasa Jeremaia gan…®ngi. Me Mikdol…®n nguibam ko Tapanes…®n nguibam ko, Memfis…®n nguibam ko, Isip…®n saut…®n amadaghan itiba. Ez…® Jeremaia kamagh…®n me m…®gei,  
\v 2 ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, a Israelian God, a kamagh…®n m…®gei: K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® Jerusalem ko Judan nguibar ekiabagh amizir bizir kuraba, ia bar a dar gani. Ia gan, da dat…®r…®gh…®n bar ikuvigha iti. Ez…® gumazamiziba uam adar itir puvat…®.  
\v 3 Judan kaba me arazir kurar av…®ribagh ami, ez…® bizir kam na gamima k…® men an…®ngaghe. Me asebar ziaba fe, egha ofan m…®gharir mughuriar aghuim zuiba me gan…®di. Me fom…®ra aser kabagh fozir puvat…®. Ez…® ia Judan kagh itiba, ko ian inazir afeziaba uaghan, ia bar mogh…®ra aser kabagh fozir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® Judan gumazamizibagh as…®ghas…®ki.  
\v 4 K…® faragha dughiar av…®ribar uan ingangarir gumaziba amangi, me God…®n akam inigha izir gumaziba, me Judaba ia bagha ize. Egha me kamagh…®n nan akam akura ia gakaghori, ‚ÄòIa arazir kurir k…® aghuazir kabar amuan mark…®.‚Äô  
\v 5 Ez…® Judan kaba kuariba arigha akar kam barazir puvat…®, egha an g…®n zuir puvat…®. Me uan arazir kuram ataghizir puvat…®, egha me asebar ofa gamir arazim ataghizir puvat…®.  
\v 6 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® bar men an…®ngaghegha, Judan nguibaba ko Jerusalem…®n tuaviba bar pazav…®ra dagh amua dagh as…®ghas…®ki. Ez…® me ikuvigha kamagh…®ra iti. 
\p  
\v 7 ‚ÄúK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar itim, Israel…®n God, k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n kamagh…®n m…®gei: Ia manmaghsua uarira uari gas…®ghas…®ghasava ami? Ia arazir kam damut…®, ian Judabar tong…®n itir gumaziba ko amiziba ko boriba, bar mogh…®ra ikuvigham. Egh ian ikiav…®ra itir varazira ua ikian kogham.  
\v 8 Ia dat…®r…®gh…®n Isip…®n ikia, egha ia uan dafaribar asebar marvir guabar ingara, ofan m…®gharir mughuriar aghuim zuiba, aser igharagha garibagh an…®di. Ez…® ian arazir kam na gamima, k…® bar puv…®ram an…®ngaghe. Eght…® kamagh…®n ia ikuvigham. Eght…® Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba bar ia d…®pova, akar asuir kurabar ia m…®k…®mam. Egh me uan apaniba akar kurabar me m…®k…®ms…®, me kamagh…®n m…®k…®mam, ‚ÄòIa Judaba ikuviz…® mogh…®n ia ikuvigham.‚Äô  
\v 9 Ian inazir afeziaba ko atriviba, ko atrivibar amuiba, arazir kuram gami. Egha ia uaghan uan amuiba ko arazir kuram gami. Ia bar mogh…®ra arazir kam Judan nguibaba ko Jerusalem…®n tuavibar arazir kam gami. Ia ti bizir kurar kaba g…®namadagha g…®fa, a?  
\v 10 Fom…®ra ikegha iza dat…®r…®gh…®n, ia arazir kurar kabar aghums…®zir puvat…®. Egha ia nan atiatia nan apengan itir puvat…®gha, nan Araziba ko arazir k…® ifongeziba, k…® da isa ia ko ian ovavibagh an…®ngi, ia dar g…®n zuir puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 11 ‚ÄúKamagh…®n k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, Israelian God, k…® m…®keme: Ia Judaba, k…® ia gas…®ghas…®ghasa n…®ghnigha g…®fa. Ez…® ian tav ikian kogham.  
\v 12 Ia Judan ikiav…®ra itir varazira, ia iz…® Isip…®n ikiasa gavgafi. Iarara, k…® bar ia gevegham. Egh ia Isip…®n ikiamin dughiam…®n, ia ar…®ghiram. Apaniba iz…® ian taraziv soght…® ia ar…®ghiram, ian tarazi dagheba puvat…®gh…®va ar…®ghiram, gumazir aruaba ko gumazir k…®niba sara. Eght…® Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba bizir k…® ia gamizir kaba baregh, me atiating, d…®gavir bar kuram damigham. Egh me ia d…®pov, ia gas…®ghas…®gh akar kurar asuibar ia m…®k…®mam. Egh me uari akar kurabar uan apanibav m…®k…®ms…®, me kamagh…®n m…®k…®mam, ‚ÄòIa Judaba ikuviz…® mogh…®n ia ikuvigham.‚Äô  
\v 13 Ia Isip…®n itir darasi, k…® Jerusalem…®n amizir arazir kamra, k…® ia damigham. Apaniba taraziv sueght…® me ar…®ghiregham, eght…® tarazi dagheba puvat…®gh ar…®ghiram, eght…® tarazi ar…®mariar kuram iniva ar…®ghiram.  
\v 14 Ia Judan dat…®r…®gh…®n Isip…®n ikiav…®ra itir varazira, ia Judan nguazim…®n mangasa bar ifonge. Ez…® ian tav as…®ghas…®zir kam gitaghan kogham, egh uamategh uan nguazim…®n mang…®ghan kogham. Ia bar mogh…®ra ikuvigham. Eght…® gumazir bar vaghvazibara uamategh ar…® mang…® uan nguazim…®n mangam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 15 Dughiar kam…®n, Judan av…®rir ekiam iza uari akuvagha itima, Jeremaia akar kam akuri. Judan Isip…®n saut…®n amadaghan itiba, me uaghan iti. Gumaziba bar uari akuvagha ikia, kamagh…®n fo, men amuiba ofan mughuriar aghuim zuiba aseba bagha dagh ami. Egha gumazir kaba uan amuiba ko kamagh…®n Jeremaian akam ikaragha ghaze,  
\v 16 ‚ÄúN…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam…®n akaba e m…®k…®ri. Ez…® e akar kam bareghan kogham. Puvat…®. E aghua.  
\v 17 E bizir e damuasa akam ak…®riziba, e dar amuam. E ofan mughuriar aghuim zuiba, aser amizir kam bagh dar amuam, me kamagh…®n a d…®bori Overiam…®n Kwin. Egh e wain…®n ofaba a gingam. Mati e fom…®ra, en ovaviba ko atriviba, ko en gumazir dapaniba, e bar mogh…®ra Overiam…®n Kwin bagha ofan kabagh amiz…® mogh…®n dagh ami. E ofan kaba Judan nguibaba ko Jerusalem…®n tuavibar dagh ami. E dagh amir dughiabar, e dagher av…®riba ikia deraghav…®ra iti, ez…® bizir kuratam e batozir puvat…®.  
\v 18 E fom…®ra ikegha iza dat…®r…®gh…®n Overiam…®n Kwin baghava wain…®n ofaba ko, ofan igharazir av…®rir amir kaba ategha, e biziba bar puvat…®. Apaniba iza en marazi m…®soghez…® me ariaghire, ez…® marazi dagheba puvat…®gha ariaghire.‚Äù  
\v 19 Ez…® amiziba ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúE guizbang…®ra, Overiam…®n Kwin bagha ofan kabagh amua, bisketba tua dagh amima da an nedazim m…®n otifi. Egha e wain…®n ofaba a ginge. Ez…® n…® ti ghaze, en paba ti arazir kam…®n aghua, a? Puvat…®, me arazir kaba bar dagh fogha, da bagha bar akonge.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 20 Jeremaia akar kam baregha, egha gumaziba ko amiziba v…®rara, kamagh…®n men akam ikaragha ghaze,  
\v 21 ‚ÄúFom…®ra ia ko, ian ovaviba, ko atriviba, ko gumazir dapaniba, ko gumazamizir igharaziba bar, ia Judan nguibaba ko Jerusalem…®n tuavibar ikia, aseba bagha ofan m…®gharir mughuriar aghuim zuibagh ami. Ez…® ia ti ghaze, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ti ian arazir kabagh n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®, a? Puvat…®. A deraghv…®ram dagh fogha dagh n…®ghn…®si.  
\v 22 \x - \xo 44:22 \xt Jeremaia 25:11; 25:18; 25:38\x*Ia arazir bar kuribagh ami, ez…® g…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God ian arazir kurar kam bar a giporpore. Bizir kam bang…®n, a ian nguazim gamiz…®, a ikuvigha nguazir k…®nim…®n oto. Ez…® gumazitam an itir puvat…®gha iza dat…®r…®gh…®n tu. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba akar kurabar uan apanibav k…®masa kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòIa Juda ikuviz…® mogh…®n, ia ikuvigham.‚Äô  
\v 23 Ia aseba bagha ofan m…®gharir mughuriar aghuim zuibagh amua, egha arazir kuraba, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n dagh ami. Egha ia an Araziba ko an arazir a ifongeziba batuegha, an akabar g…®n zuir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, dughiar kurar ia batozim ikiav…®ra iti.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 24 Egha Jeremaia uam akar maba bar Judabav keme. An akam amizibagh asa, kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa bar Judan Isip…®n itiba, deragh kuaribar arigh, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam baragh.  
\v 25 Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, Israelian God, a ghaze: Ia uan amuiba ko, uan akar d…®k…®r…®zim…®n bizibar amut…® da otivasa. Ia kamagh…®n akam ak…®righa m…®keme, ‚ÄòE ofan m…®gharir mughuriar aghuim zuim tuegh, Overiam…®n Kwin bagh wain…®n ofaba ingasa akam ak…®ri. Ez…® bar guizbang…®ra, e akar d…®k…®r…®zir kam damut…® an otivam.‚Äô Aria, ia bizir ia damuasa akam ak…®riziba, ia mang…® dar amut…® da otiv. 
\p  
\v 26 ‚ÄúIa Judan Isip…®n iti darazi bar, ia deraghv…®ra kuariba arigh Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam baragh. Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n m…®gei: K…® uan ziar ekiam bagha p…®n ar…®gha guizbang…®ra m…®gei: Ia Judan tav Isip…®n kantrin ik…®v…®ra ik…®va, akar d…®k…®r…®zir tam uan ziam…®n a damighan kogham. Ia ua kamagh…®n m…®kemeghan kogham, ‚ÄòBar guizbang…®ra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n p…®n ikiav…®ra itim…®n ziam, e uan akam gavgavim a gan…®ga m…®gei.‚Äô Bar puvat…®.  
\v 27 K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® guizbang…®ra m…®gei, K…® deraghv…®ra ia damuan kogham. Puvat…®. K…® paza ia damuasa ian gari. Ia Judan Isip…®n iti darasi, k…® apaniba amadaght…®, me iz…® ian taraziv sogh…®rarigham. Eght…® tarazi dagheba puvat…®gh ar…®m…®ghiregham. Egh ia bar gevegham.  
\v 28 Ian vaghvazibara m…®dorozim…®n ikuvighan kogh…®va, Isip ategh ua Judan nguazim…®n mangam. Ia Judan ikiav…®ra ikia iza Isip…®n ikezir varazira, ia dughiar kam…®n deraghv…®ra fogham, tinan akam bar gavgafi, nan akam, o ian akam? 
\p  
\v 29 ‚ÄúK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® guizbang…®ra m…®gei, K…® ian akakaghs…® bizitam kamagh…®n a damigham. Ia kantrin kam…®n ikiamin dughiam…®n, k…® ia gas…®ghasigham. Ia bizir kam…®n ganigh, egh ia fogham, nan akam pura mang…®ghan kogham. Puvat…®.  
\v 30 \x - \xo 44:30 \xt 2 Atriviba 25:1-7\x*Bizir k…® ia damuamim a kamak…®n, Isip…®n Atrivim Hofra, k…® a is…® apanir a m…®sueght…® ana aremeghamim…®n dafarim dar…®gham. Arazir kamra, k…® faragha Judan Atrivim Sedekaia gami. Babilon…®n Atrivim Nebukatnesar Sedekaian apanim gami, egh a m…®sueght…® an aremeghasa, k…® a isa Nebukatnesar gan…®ngi.‚Äù\f + \fr 44:30 \ft Jeremaian eghaghanim, a sapta 44…®n g…®fa. Dughiar kam…®n, Jeremaia Isip…®n kantrin ikia egha ghurigha g…®fa. Ez…® fofozir gumaziba ghaze Jeremaia Isip…®n kantrin ikia ghua areme.\f* 
\c 45  
\s1 Jeremaia Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam isa Baruk gan…®di 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 45:1 \xt 2 Atriviba 24:1; 2 Eghaghaniba 36:5-7; Daniel 1:1-2\x*Namba 4…®n azenim…®n, Josaian otarim Jehoiakim, Judan atrivim…®n itir dughiam…®n, God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Jeremaia akam isa Nerian otarim Baruk gan…®ngi. Jeremaia Ikiav…®ra Itir God a gan…®ngizir akaba, bar adar gun m…®keme. Ez…® Baruk ak…®nafarir mam…®n ada osiri. Egha aning ingangarir kam gamir dughiam…®n, Jeremaia kamagh…®n Baruk m…®keme,  
\v 2-4 \x - \xo 45:2-4 \xt Jeremaia 1:10\x*‚ÄúBaruk, n…® oragh. N…® kamagh…®n m…®keme, ‚ÄòAio! K…® os…®mt…®zir av…®riba ko m…®zazir av…®riba iti, ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God ua nan os…®mt…®zibagh is…®vagha ghu. K…® ikiav…®ra ikia, ghua bar iporpore. Nan os…®mt…®ziba da gevir puvat…®. Da kamagh…®ra itima, k…® bar am…®ragha avughsaziba puvat…®.‚Äô Ez…® Baruk, n…® oragh. Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Israelian God, n…® m…®k…®masa kamagh…®n na m…®keme, ‚ÄòK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® guizbang…®ra m…®gei. K…® dat…®r…®gh…®n bizir k…® ingariziba ab…®si. Ez…® k…® oparizir biziba, k…® da asiam. Bizir k…® b…®gh…®va asiamin kaba, da bar nguazir kam…®n gumazamiziba bar me bativam.  
\v 5 Ez…® manmagh…®n amiz…®, bizir aghuibara n…® bativasa n…® ifonge? N…® n…®ghn…®zir kam atakigh. Guizbang…®ra, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® nguazir kam…®n gumazamiziba bar pazav…®ra me damigham. Egh k…® n…®n akuragham, eght…® n…® danganir manam…®n mangam, me n…® m…®sueght…® n…® aremeghan kogham.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù 
\c 46  
\ms1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God kantrin maba m…®g…®r…®g…®am dar iti\f + \fr 46:0 \ft Jeremaia Jerusalem…®n God…®n akam akuri dughiam…®n, God dughiar mabar kantrin igharazir tintinibar itiba bagha akaba isa a gan…®di. Akar kaba me bar ada isafuragha God…®n Akam Inigha Izir Gumazim Jeremaian Ak…®nafarim…®n aven bar abuan ada ar…®ki.\f* 
\mr (Sapta 46--51) 
\s1 Isipia m…®dorozim…®n ire 
\p  
\v 1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, kantrin maba bagha akam ikia, egha akar kam isa Jeremaia gan…®ngi. 
\p  
\v 2 \x - \xo 46:2-26 \xt Aisaia 19:1-25; Esekiel 29:1--32:32\x*Akar mam, Isipia bagha ghu. Akar kam, a Isip…®n atrivim Nekon m…®dorozir gumaziba bagha ghu. M…®dorozir gumazir kaba Yufretis…®n Fanem…®n borogh…®n, Karkemis…®n nguibam…®n otifi. Ez…® namba 4…®n azenim…®n, Josaian otarim Jehoiakim, Judan atrivim…®n itima, Babilon…®n Atrivim Nebukatnesar uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko, iza Isipia m…®sogha me d…®kab…®ra. Dughiar kam…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God Babilonia g…®n…®ghn…®gha akar kam isa Isipia gan…®ga ghaze: 
\b  
\q1  
\v 3 ‚ÄúIa Isipia, ia oraba inigh, 
\q2 mang…® m…®soghs…® uari ar…®gh gan ik…®. 
\q1  
\v 4 Ia hoziabar k…®r. 
\q2 Eght…® ia m…®dorozir gumazir hoziabagh apiaghira m…®soziba, 
\q3 ia uan hoziabar apiagh. 
\q1 Ia uan m…®dorozir dapanir asuabar aghuigh, tuivigh m…®soghs…® gan ik…®. 
\q2 Ia uan afuziba ak…®r…®va, egh ia vaghvagh uan m…®dorozir korotiabar aghuigh. 
\q1  
\v 5 Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n manmagh…®n ami? 
\q2 K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® Isipian garima, 
\q3 me bar puv…®ram atiatigha ara uamategha ize. 
\q1 Apaniba men m…®dorozir gumazir gavgaviba d…®kab…®ra, ez…® Isipia m…®dorozim ategha zuam…®ra ua ize. 
\q2 Me atiatir biziba da tintinibar iti. 
\q3 Kamagh…®n me ua ik…®gha g…®rak…®rang…®n garir puvat…®. 
\q1  
\v 6 Egha gumazir puv ivemariba ko m…®sozir gumazir gavgaviba, 
\q2 me apanibar ar…®v avegham. Puvat…®. 
\q1 Me not…®n amadaghan ikia, 
\q2 tintinibar onganigha Yufretis…®n Fanem…®n borogh…®ra ire. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 7 ‚ÄúIk…®zir manaba, Isip…®n kantrin itir Nail…®n Fanem…®n m…®n ekefe? 
\q2 Me gavgavigha, mati faner ekiam aperiar gavgavim an otogha zui. 
\q1  
\v 8 Kar Isip…®n adarazira. 
\q2 Me Nail…®n Fanem…®n m…®n ekevegha otivigha, mati faner ekiam aperiam an oto. 
\q1 Isip…®n gumazamiziba kamagh…®n m…®keme: 
\q2 ‚ÄòK…® bar ekevegh otogh nguazim…®n danganiba bar ada avaragham. 
\q1 Egh k…® nguibabagh as…®ghas…®gh…®va, 
\q2 dar itir gumazamiziba saram as…®ghasigham. 
\q1  
\v 9 Ia nan hoziaba, ia ivemar mang…®. 
\q2 Ia nan karisba, ia bar puv…®ra ivemar. 
\q1 Ia nan m…®dorozir gumazir gavgaviba, ia Itiopia ko Libian kantrining, ia aning…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba, 
\q2 ia oraba suizir gumaziba, ia Lidian kantrin pibar asir gumaziba, 
\q3 ia bar mogh…®ra mang…® m…®sogh.‚Äô 
\b  
\q1  
\v 10 ‚ÄúIsipia kamagh…®n m…®kemegha g…®fa. 
\q2 Ez…® m…®dorozir kam, kar God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim…®n bizim. 
\q3 A en Ekiam. 
\q2 Egha dughiar kam…®n a uan apaniba ivezir kuram me ikarvasi. 
\q1 M…®dorozim bar gavgaviz…®, gumaziba pura tintinibar ariaghiri. 
\q2 Mati m…®dorozir sabam m…®tiriam puv an azima, 
\q3 a gumazibar m…®karziba ko ghuziba apava, bar iz…®fa. 
\q1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, gumazamizir kabav soghez…® me ariaghire. 
\q2 Egha mati, a uab…® not…®n amadaghan, 
\q3 Yufretis…®n Fanem…®n borogh…®n ofa gami.‚Äù 
\b  
\q1  
\v 11 Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n m…®gei, 
\q1 ‚ÄúKantri Isip, n…® mati guivir igiar mam duaba n…®n m…®karzim…®n otifi. 
\q2 N…® Gileat…®n mang…®gh danganir kam…®n marasin…®n aghuiba buri. 
\q1 Egh n…® marasin…®n igharagha gariba bagh, bar puv…®ra ingar da inighan kogham. 
\q2 Marasin…®n tam n…®n duabar amut…®, da akumighan kogham. 
\q1  
\v 12 N…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba tintinibar are, 
\q2 egha me uarira uarigh ivezegha, uari inigha ire. 
\q1 N…® m…®dorozim…®n ir…®gha bar aghums…®ki, 
\q2 ez…® kantrin igharaziba n…®n aghums…®zir akam baraki. 
\q3 N…®n ararem bar nguazir kam…®n danganiba bar adagh iz…®fa.‚Äù 
\s1 Atrivim Nebukatnesar iza Isipia m…®sosi 
\p  
\v 13 \x - \xo 46:13 \xt Jeremaia 43:10-13\x*Babilon…®n Atrivim Nebukatnesar iz…® Isip…®n kantri ko m…®soghamin dughiam…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God akar mam isa uan akam inigha izir gumazim Jeremaia gan…®ngi. Akar kam kamak…®n: 
\b  
\q1  
\v 14 ‚ÄúIa Mikdol ko Memfis, ko Tapanes ko, Isip…®n itir nguibar maba sara akam akun. 
\q2 Egh kamagh…®n me m…®k…®m, ‚ÄòApaniba otivigh puv ia m…®sogh…®rarigh, 
\q3 egh ian kantrin aven bizir av…®ribagh as…®ghasigham. 
\q1 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia Isipia, uan m…®dorozir biziba ak…®righ 
\q2 tuivigh m…®soghs…® ik…®. 
\q1  
\v 15 Manmaghsua Apis, an aser ia bulmakaun apurir ingarizim, 
\q2 an arav ghu, egha tugha gavgavizir puvat…®? 
\q1 An m…®ngarim kamak…®n, 
\q2 Ikiav…®ra Itir God uab…® anekuniz…® a iraghu. 
\q1  
\v 16 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Isipian av…®rim gamiz…®, ia tintinibar ire. 
\q2 Ez…® Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba uariv g…®a ghaze: 
\q1 Aria, e ti Isip ategh uamategh uan gumazamiziba bagh mangam. 
\q2 Apaniba kantrin kam gas…®ghas…®si, 
\q3 kamagh…®n amiz…®, e uamategh uan nguibamra mangam.‚Äô 
\q1  
\v 17 Ia ziar igiam kamagh…®n Isip…®n atrivim dan…®ngigh, 
\q2 Gumazim Puram Akam Arava Tintinibar Ifaghata Uan Dughiam…®n Atam Ghuz…® A G…®fa.‚Äù 
\b  
\q1  
\v 18 Ez…® atrivim…®n ziar bar guizbang…®ram atrivim…®n itim, a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim. 
\q2 A kamagh…®n m…®keme, 
\q1 ‚ÄúK…® zurara angam…®ra iti, k…® guizbang…®ra m…®gei: 
\q2 Gumazitam izam. 
\q1 Eght…® an gavgavim bar gumazir igharazibar gavgavim gafiragham, 
\q2 mati Tabor…®n M…®ghs…®am bar ruaragha, m…®ghs…®ar mabagh afira. 
\q2 Egha mati Karmel…®n M…®ghs…®am ongarir dadarim…®n ikia, 
\q3 bar p…®n mar iti. 
\q1  
\v 19 Ia Isipia, ia mang…® kantrin igharazibar kalabus…®n ikiam, 
\q2 kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia uan bizibar k…®r. 
\q1 Apaniba Memfis gas…®ghas…®gham, 
\q2 eght…® nguibar kam pura ikiam, eght…® gumazamiziba ua an ikian kogham.‚Äù 
\b  
\q1  
\v 20 Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n m…®gei, 
\q2 ‚ÄúIsip…®n kantri, mati bulmakaun amebar igiar bar dirim. 
\q3 Ez…® d…®fuar bar kurar mam not…®n amadaghan ikegha iza a givi. 
\q1  
\v 21 Ez…® igharaz darazir gumaziba, Isipia uan m…®dorozir gumazibar ikiasa 
\q2 me givese. 
\q1 Egha Isipia bar deraghav…®ra men gari, ez…® me bar deraghav…®ra iti, 
\q2 mati bulmakaun m…®karzim saram aghungiziba. 
\q1 Egha apaniba otivizir dughiam…®n, gumazir kaba m…®dorozim ategha are. 
\q2 Ez…® Isip…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba uaghan kamagh…®n ami. 
\q1 Ez…® m…®dorozim…®n aven, dughiar bar kuram me batoz…®, me bar ikufi. 
\q2 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me m…®dorozim bagha tuivigha gavgavizir puvat…®. 
\q1 Ez…® dughiar kam…®n me arazir kurar me amiziba bagha 
\q2 ivezir kuram isi. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 22 ‚ÄúApaniba b…®zir ekiam…®n arua izima, 
\q2 Isipia bar atiatigha n…®m…®ra kuruzim…®n m…®n uari am…®k…®r…®vegha are, 
\q3 egha me n…®g…®nir tam gamizir puvat…®. 
\q1 Apaniba sobiabar me m…®soghasa izi, 
\q2 mati gumazim sobiam suiragha temeba okasa izi.\f + \fr 46:22 \ft Hibrun akam deragha m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®.\f* 
\q1  
\v 23 Isipia me av…®raseme, egha me bar gavgavigha, 
\q2 mati ruarir ekiam…®n temeba bar uari an…®ghaf…®ri, 
\q3 ez…® gumaziba aven mangan asaghasaki. 
\q1 Ez…® apanibar m…®dorozir gumazibar d…®bobonim bar ghuavanabo, 
\q2 egha odezibar d…®bobonim gafira, 
\q3 eght…® gumazitam men d…®bobonim mengan iburagham. 
\q1 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® ghaze, 
\q2 apaniba bar Isipia ag…®vagham, 
\q3 mati gumaziba ruarir ekiam…®n temeba bar ada oke. 
\q1  
\v 24 K…® Isipia isa not…®n amadaghan itir gumazibar dafarim gat…®z…®, 
\q2 me bar aghums…®ki.‚Äù 
\b  
\p  
\v 25 Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, Israelian God, kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa oragh. Tebes…®n nguibam…®n asem Emon, ko Isip…®n atrivim ko, men aser igharaziba ko, Isip…®n kantrin aven itir biziba bar ko, an atrivim ko, gavman…®n gumazir dapaniba ko, gumazamizir n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim uan atrivim…®n itiba, me bar mogh…®ra, k…® ivezir kuram is…® me dan…®ngam.  
\v 26 Atrivim Nebukatnesar uan gumazir dapaniba ko Isipia m…®sueght…® me arighireghasa. K…® Isipia is…® Babilonian dafarim dar…®gham. Eght…® g…®n, gumazamiziba fom…®ra Isip…®n apiagha ikez…® mogh…®n, gumazamiziba ua Isip…®n nguazim…®n ikiam. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® m…®kemegha g…®fa.‚Äù 
\s1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God ua uan gumazamiziba iniam 
\p  
\v 27 \x - \xo 46:27 \xt Aisaia 41:13-14; 44:2\x*\x - \xo 46:27-28 \xt Jeremaia 30:10-11\x*Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n m…®keme: 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄúIa Israelia, ia Jekop…®n ovavir boriba, ia nan ingangarir gumazamiziba, 
\q2 ia atiating…®va d…®gavir kuram damuan mark…®. 
\q1 Bar guizbang…®ra, ia kantrin saghon itir kam…®n kalabus…®n iti. 
\q2 Eght…® k…® ua ia inight…®, 
\q1 ia ua uan nguazimra izegh, deraghv…®ra dapiagham. 
\q2 Eght…® tarazi ua ia damut…® ia atiatingan kogham. 
\q1  
\v 28 \x - \xo 46:28 \xt Jeremaia 10:24; 30:11\x*K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® kamagh…®n m…®gei: K…® ia ko ik…® ian akurvagham. 
\q2 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Ia Israelia, ia nan adarasi, ia nan ingangarir gumazamiziba, ia atiatingan mark…®. 
\q1 K…® ia batoghez…®, ia ghua kantrin igharazibar tong…®n iti. 
\q2 Eght…® k…® kantrin kaba bar me agevegham. 
\q1 Egh k…® ia ag…®vaghan kogham. 
\q2 Guizbang…®ra, k…® puv ia damigham, 
\q3 k…® arazir vorogh…®ra itim g…®n…®ghn…®gha ia ak…®ri.‚Äù 
\c 47  
\s1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God akam Filistian adarazir iti 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 47:1-7 \xt Aisaia 14:29-31; Esekiel 25:15-17; Joel 3:4-8; Amos 1:6-8; Sefanaia 2:4-7; Sekaraia 9:5-7\x*Ikiav…®ra Itir God akam Filistian kantrin adarazir iti. Dughiar kam…®n Isipian atrivim t…®ghar Gasa m…®sogham, kar Filistian nguibar ekiar mam. Ez…® God akam isa an akam inigha izir gumazim Jeremaia gan…®ngi.  
\v 2 Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n m…®keme: 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄúIa gan! 
\q2 Apaniba not…®n ikia uari akuvasava ami, 
\q3 mati not…®n amadaghan itir d…®paba bar ekefe. 
\q1 Egha da bar puv…®ra ivemara, 
\q2 dar aperiaba bar gavgafi. 
\q1 Apaniba nguazir kam avaragham, 
\q2 mati aperiam nguazim ko an itir biziba bar ada avegham. 
\q3 A nguibaba ko dar itir gumazamiziba saram avaragham. 
\q1 Kamagh…®n nguibar kabar gumazamiziba bar atiating…®va, 
\q2 pamtem…®n d…®m…®va, bar puv…®ram arangam. 
\q1  
\v 3 Eght…® hoziaba ivemar iz…®t…®, 
\q2 dar suer puziba puv…®ra nguazim m…®sogh t…®ngagh…®t…®, me da baragham. 
\q1 Eght…® me karisbar n…®g…®nim baraght…® 
\q2 da puv…®ra ivemart…®, dar wilba pamtem…®n t…®ngagham. 
\q1 Eght…® gumazamiziba bar puv…®ram atiating…®va, aregham. 
\q2 Eght…® ameboghfeziaba onganigh 
\q3 uan boribagh n…®ghn…®ghan kogh…®va, me m…®zuamighan kogham. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 4 ‚ÄúFilistiaba gas…®ghas…®ghamin dughiam a izegha g…®fa. 
\q2 K…® men tuavim ap…®righam, eght…® me ua Tair ko Saidon…®n akuraghan kogham. 
\q1 Fom…®ra Filistian ovaviba Krit…®n Arighat…®zim ategha iza Filistian nguibar ekiabar iti. 
\q2 Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, 
\q3 k…® nguibar ekiam…®n itir Filistian varazira gas…®ghas…®ghasava ami. 
\q1  
\v 5 Gasaba, men naviba bar oseme, ez…® me uan dapanir ar…®ziba ap…®ri. 
\q2 Ez…® Askelon…®n nguibam bar ikufi. 
\q1 Ia danganir zarir kam…®n ikiav…®ra itir varazira, ian apangkuvim manad…®zogh…®n g…®vaght…®, 
\q2 ia tintinibar uan inivaf…®ziba aghorir arazim ategham? 
\q1  
\v 6 Ia kamagh…®n d…®a ghaze, 
\q2 ‚ÄòO Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n m…®dorozir sabam, n…® manad…®zogh…®n e gas…®ghas…®zir ingangarir kam ategham? 
\q1 O m…®dorozir sabam, n…® uamategh uan asuam…®n aven mag…®r…®. 
\q2 N…® ingangarir kam ategh avughs…®.‚Äô 
\q1  
\v 7 Ez…® k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® ingangarir kam isa uan m…®dorozir sabam gan…®ngi. 
\q2 K…® Askelonia ko ongarir dadarim…®n itir gumazamizir igharaziba sara m…®soghasa m…®dorozir sabar kam amada. 
\q3 Kamagh…®n, a n…®m…®ra ik…® avughsan kogham.‚Äù 
\c 48  
\s1 Moap…®n kantri ikuvigham 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 48:1-47 \xt Aisaia 15:1--16:14; Aisaia 25:10-12; Esekiel 25:8-11; Amos 2:1-3; Sefanaia 2:8-11\x*Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, Israelian God, a Moap…®n kantri g…®n…®ghn…®gha kamagh…®n m…®keme: 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄúIavzika, Nguibar ekiam Nebon gumazamiziba. 
\q2 Apaniba Nebo bar a gas…®ghasigham. 
\q3 Me Kiriataim d…®kab…®ragham, a nguibar d…®vazir gavgavim itim. 
\q1 Me a gas…®ghas…®gham. 
\q2 Eght…® nguibar kam…®n gumazamiziba bar aghumsigham. 
\q1  
\v 2 Moap…®n ziar ekiam a iraghugha g…®fa. 
\q2 Apaniba Hesbon…®n nguibam…®n otifi, 
\q3 egha me Moapia gas…®ghas…®ghamin arazim…®n akam m…®sosi. 
\q1 Me kamagh…®n m…®gei, 
\q2 ‚ÄòAria, e mang…® gumazamizir kaba bar me ag…®vaka, 
\q3 eght…® Moap…®n kantri ua ikian kogham.‚Äô 
\q1 Ia Matmenia, apaniba bar ia gas…®ghas…®ght…®, 
\q2 ia matmat…®n mangam. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 3 ‚ÄúIa d…®md…®ar ararer ekiar Horonaim…®n nguibam…®n otozim baragh. 
\q2 Me kamagh…®n dei: 
\q3 Biziba bar ikufi. 
\q1  
\v 4 Moap ikuvigham, 
\q2 eght…® men boribar ararem bar ekevegham. 
\q1  
\v 5 Moapia, me aregham. 
\q2 Me bar puv arava, Luhit…®n tuavim…®n ghuavanaga, Horonaim…®n nguibam…®n ghuaghiri. 
\q3 Ez…® men ararem ghuav…®ra ikiava bar ekefe. 
\q1  
\v 6 Me kamagh…®n m…®gei: Ia zuam…®ram aregh. 
\q2 Puvat…®ght…® ia ikuvigham. 
\q3 Ia as…®zir atiabar m…®n mang…® gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n mongegh.\f + \fr 48:6 \ft Hibrun akam deragha m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®.\f* 
\b  
\q1  
\v 7 \x - \xo 48:7 \xt D…®boboniba 21:29; Aisaia 46:1-2; Jeremaia 43:12; 49:3\x*‚ÄúMoap, n…® ingarizir biziba ko, dag…®aba bagha pamtem…®n n…®ghn…®gha ghaze: 
\q2 Bizir kaba n…®n akuraght…® n…® deraghv…®ra ikiam. 
\q3 Ez…® n…®n n…®ghn…®zir kam derazir puvat…®. 
\q1 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…®n apaniba m…®dorozim…®n n…® d…®kab…®ragham. 
\q2 Egh me n…®n aser kam Kemos inigh mang…® kantrin igharazim…®n kalabus dat…®gham. 
\q3 Egh me uaghan Kemos…®n ofa gamir gumaziba ko, an ingangarir gumazibar dapaniba sara iniam. 
\q1  
\v 8 Apaniba iz…® nguibaba bar dagh as…®ghasigham, 
\q2 eght…® nguibatam deragh ikian kogham. 
\q1 K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, 
\q2 me danganir zariba ko, danganir m…®ghs…®abar itibagh as…®ghasigham. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 9 ‚ÄúMoap, k…® amangs…®zim n…®n nguazim dat…®gham. 
\q2 Eght…® n…®n nguibaba bar ikuvigh pura ikiam. 
\q3 Eght…® gumazitaba dar ikeghan kogham.‚Äù\f + \fr 48:9 \ft Hibrun akam deragha m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®.\f* 
\b  
\p  
\v 10 Gumazamiziba Ikiav…®ra Itir God me gan…®ngizir ingangarim damuan aghuaght…®, a me gas…®ghasigham. Egh a gumazir igharaziba m…®dorozir sabam…®n me m…®sueght…® me ar…®m…®ghir…®s…® gumazitam m…®kemeght…®, gumazim a damighan koght…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God a gas…®ghasigham. 
\s1 Moap…®n nguibaba bar ikuvigham 
\p  
\v 11 Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n m…®gei: 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄúMoap…®n kantri fom…®ra igiamra ikegha iza dat…®r…®gh…®n dughiar kam…®n tu, 
\q2 apanitam iza a gas…®ghas…®ghizir puvat…®, 
\q3 egha gumazamiziba inigha ghua kantrin igharazim…®n me isa kalabus gat…®zir puvat…®. 
\q1 Moap mati wain…®n aghuim, gumaziba an ingarigha, anetaghiz…® a iti. 
\q2 Me d…®par m…®sevir tabar a ruizir puvat…®. 
\q3 Ez…® an is…®ngt…®zim kamagh…®ra ikia, egha an mughuriam dera. 
\q1  
\v 12 Ez…® k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® guizbang…®ra m…®gei: 
\q2 K…® dughiar mam am…®sefe, ez…® dughiar kam…®n k…® gumazitaba amadaght…® 
