\v 18 ‚ÄúGumazir Moap gas…®ghas…®ghamin ingangarim itim, 
\q2 a ia batogh ian d…®vazir gavgavibagh as…®ghasigham. 
\q1 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia Dibon…®n nguibar ekiam…®n gumazamiziba, 
\q2 ia mati atrivim…®n guivir dirim uan ziam fe, 
\q1 egh ia uan ziar ekiaba g…®n amadagh, 
\q2 gumazir k…®nibar m…®n nguazir m…®diarim dapiagh. 
