\v 26 Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n m…®gei: 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄúMoap na batoke, kamagh…®n amiz…®, apaniba a d…®kab…®nasa k…® ifonge. 
\q2 Egh a damight…® a mati gumazim d…®par onganim amez…® mogh…®n otogham. 
